MV viewing mode can be played by clearing each song once on any difficulty level of your choice. You will be released.
mlHelp_Body.97:
By using Prism Jewel or Gacha tickets, you can obtain P-idol or S characters.

For Gacha notes, be sure to read the Gacha Details posted on each Gacha screen. please confirm.
mlHelp_Body.99:
By using Prism Jewel, you can get P-idol or S characters.

Limited to once a day, you can use Paid Prism Jewel at a lower price than usual to get a Gacha. You can draw.
*The reset of the number of times will be done at 0:00 AM every day.

Please be sure to check the Gacha Details posted on each Gacha screen for precautions regarding Gacha.
mlHelp_Body.100:
You can increase the [Prism Gauge] by pulling some gachas.

If you increase the target's [Prism Gauge] and reach the specified value, you will receive a Prism Gauge reward item. You can earn it.
mlHelp_Body.101:
[Exchange points] will be given when you pull some gachas.

By acquiring the required number of target [exchange points], you can exchange them with the target P-idol or S character. 

[Exchange points] held at the end of the event period will be automatically converted to [Star Shards].
[Star Shards] can be exchanged with various items at the exchange. You can exchange it.
mlHelp_Body.102:
On Twesta, you can check the posts of Idols.
This occurs depending on various conditions such as obtaining the Idol and the Idol's No. of fans.

Set Favorite for each post can do.
mlHelp_Body.103:
In CHAIN, you can enjoy conversations between idols in chat format.
It occurs due to various conditions such as the rise of the idol's bond and when Events are held or ended.

In CHAIN There are the following types.

■Idol 
In the talk room for each idol, you can enjoy one-on-one conversation between the idol and Producer.

■Unit
In the talk room for each unit. You can mainly enjoy conversations between unit members.

Unread talks will have a badge displayed to the right of the idol name/unit name and will be displayed at the top of the list.
mlHelp_Body.104:
On the phone, you will receive calls from idols.
This will occur during the idol's final training or when Bond rises.
mlHelp_Body.105:
You can earn rewards by achieving specific conditions.

Divided into [Daily missions], [Main missions], [Limited missions], and [Season missions].
mlHelp_Body.106:
This is a mission that can be challenged every day.

Achievement status will be reset at 0:00 AM and you can challenge again.
mlHelp_Body.107:
This is a mission that can be challenged at any time.

Once a mission has been cleared, it cannot be challenged again.
mlHelp_Body.108:
This is a mission that can be challenged in Limited mode.

Once a mission has been cleared, it cannot be challenged again.
mlHelp_Body.109:
Some rewards will be sent to the [Gift Box] and can be received from the [Gift Box] button on the home page.

Also, some gifts have a Receiving Due Date. 
Gifts that have passed the Receiving due date will be automatically deleted.

You can receive up to 100 Gifts at a time using the [Receive All] button.

[Receiving History] will display the most recent one. You can check up to 500 gifts received within the past week.
mlHelp_Body.110:
You can check the items you have by selecting [item] in the menu.
You can check the item's description by selecting each item.

■Consumables
STRecoveryitem・LBRecoveryitem, Money ,This item is used for production and live performances.

■Awakening
This item is necessary for the awakening of Produce Idol.

■Special training
This item is necessary for special training of Produce Idol.

■Idol Skill LvUp
Items required for Idol Skill LvUp of Produce Idol.

■Training
Items required for training Support Characters.

■Master Training
Items required for master training of Support Characters .

■Gacha Ticket
This is Gacha Ticket.

■Other
Items that do not fit into the above categories will go here.
mlHelp_Body.111:
At [Shop], you can purchase various products.
Some products have a limit on the number of purchases, and some products have a fixed purchase period.

■Prism Jewel
Paid Prism You can purchase Jewel.

■item
You can purchase various items and products.

■Clothes
You can purchase's costumes.

■Login Bonus Pass
Login Bonus Pass You can purchase.

■Season Pass
You can purchase Season Pass.
mlHelp_Body.112:
Here you can purchase Paid Prism Jewel.
To purchase, you will need to log into your account on the platform you are using and register your date of birth.

Also, the amount that can be purchased per month is in the following format for each age group.

・Under 16 years old: up to 5,000 yen per month
・16 to 17 years old: 20,000 yen per month Up to Yen
・Over 18 years old: No limit
mlHelp_Body.113:
At [Exchange Office], you can exchange various items.
There are some items and products that have a limit on the number of times they can be exchanged, or a fixed period of exchange.

■ Money 
You can exchange Money for various items.

■Produce Idol pieces
Rainbow Rocks can be exchanged for each Produce Idol's Piece.
The exchange rate of Rainbow Rocks will never be reset. 

■Support Characters Pieces
Rainbow Rocks can be exchanged for each Support Characters' Piece.

■Star Shards
Star Shards can be exchanged for various items.

■Season Medals
Season Medals can be exchanged for various items.

■Selection Tickets
You can use Selection Tickets to exchange for any object.

■Costume Tickets
You can exchange Medals for any object using's costume Tickets. You can exchange it.
mlHelp_Body.114:
If you uninstall the app from your device, all data will be deleted.

In order to continue playing with the same game data after reinstalling, you must complete Account Link. there is.
mlHelp_Body.115:
[Account Link] is to link your game account and
Bandai Namco ID.
You can do this from [Account Link] in the menu.

If you have completed [Account Link] By doing so, you can share game data and play on multiple devices by performing [data link] from other devices.
Also, if you change to a new device, lose your device, or accidentally change your device from one device to another, Even if you delete the app
, you can resume playing from where you left off with the game data using [Data Linkage].

*Paid Prism Jewel cannot be linked to different platforms. No. It can only be used on the purchased platform. For details, please check the notes displayed when [Account Link]/[Data linkage].

When performing [Data linkage] When starting the app for the first time
Select [Data Linkage] in [Game Start] and enter the Account Linked Bandai Namco ID.

Go to a device that already has playing data. [Data linkage] is not possible, so please use User Data Deletion in the title menu or delete the app before trying.
mlHelp_Body.116:
Play live If you spend money while playing, the rewards you can get will increase.
Decreased LB will be recovered once every 30 minutes, and can be recovered with Prism Jewel or LBRecoveryitem.

※ The LB consumed in one live can be set to 0 or 1 to 5 times.
*The amount of rewards and Idol status EXP that can be earned will increase when set to 2 times or more.
*Set to 0 and the amount of rewards The amount will decrease, but you can play the live as many times as you like.
*LB consumption cannot be reduced to 0 except for the smartphone version.
mlHelp_Body.117:
Here you can purchase Paid Prism Jewel.
To purchase, you will need to log into your account on the platform you are using and register your date of birth.

Also, the amount that can be purchased per month is in the following format for each age.

・Under 16 years old: up to 5,000 DMM points per month
・16 to 17 years old: 20,000 per month Up to DMMpoint
・Over 18 years old: No restrictions
mlHelp_Body.118:
In Lesson ・Special Lesson ・Audition,
You can use it by dragging and dropping the Produce Card displayed in your hand onto it.
mlHelp_Body.119:
This is a rhythm game mode where you can enjoy the live performance of idols.
 Tap the flowing notes at the right time to lead the live to success.

Various rewards depending on the live performance You will receive.

*For versions other than the smartphone version, it will be auto live or Skip live.Please enjoy manual play on the smartphone version.
*For rewards that require manual play, please use the smartphone with data linking. You can earn it by playing on a version device.
mlHelp_Body.120:
Each song has a difficulty level and song level.
The 4 difficulty levels from EASY to EXPERT can be played immediately without Unlock Condition.

■Difficulty level
EASY/NORMAL/HARD ／EXPERT／MASTER

■Song Level
This is an indicator that shows the difficulty level of the live performance.
mlHelp_Body.121:
The conditions are different between the smartphone version and the PC version (other than the smartphone version).

■Smartphone version
MASTER difficulty level is unlocked by clearing EXPERT once in manual play.
 To clear the game, you must complete the remaining LIFE in the rhythm game with a score of 1 or higher.

■PC version
Manual play is not supported, so it cannot be released on the PC version.
On the smartphone device that has linked the data If you clear EXPERT manually and unlock it, it will also be unlocked on the PC version.
mlHelp_Body.122:
You will receive a reward when you achieve the goal in manual play.
There are High Score rank rewards and combo rank rewards for each song/difficulty level.
The target value, reward details, and achievement status of each are as follows. You can check from [Rewards] in song selection.

In addition, High Score and combo number results are not recorded in auto live and Skip live, so you will need to play live manually.

■ About the PC version
The PC version has auto live and Skip live, so you can earn it by playing manually on the smartphone version with data linkage.
mlHelp_Body.123:
Once you complete production, you will become Fes Idol (abbreviated as F-Idol) and will be able to perform live.

F-Idol has a high status and has one Live Skill.
 
F-Idol's Fes Idol rank is displayed at the top right of the icon.
mlHelp_Body.124:
If live performance feels slow in 3DMV mode, please try the following.

■Menu > System Settings > Quality Settings
Select [Performance Priority] or [Custom] to adjust 3D resolution and shadow quality. ,Please try changing the anti-aliasing and power saving mode settings.

■ Live Settings > 3DMV Effect
The default during live is [Weak].Set it to [None] to lighten the operation. You can.

*Please note that the effect may vary depending on the play environment such as the device specs and storage/memory usage status.

Reducing the 3D processing load in the game and We will continue to work on improving the playing environment.If you have any concerns about any parts or situations while playing, please feel free to contact us or let us know.
mlHelp_Body.125:
Except for some 's songs, 3DMV songs support focus camera mode.
You can enjoy camera mode that follows the idol in the selected position.

■Focus camera compatible songs
 nThe [Focus] mark will be displayed on the jacket on the song selection screen.
If you select a song that is compatible with the focus camera, you can switch between normal camera mode and focus camera mode in the camera mode setting on the unit confirmation screen.
 n
■Focus camera position selection
You can set in advance which position the camera will follow in the camera mode settings.
mlHelp_Body.126:
This is a mission that can only be challenged in that month.

By clearing a Season Mission, you can raise your Season Rank, and each time you reach a certain Season Rank, you can receive a reward. 

If you have a Season Pass, you can earn both regular and premium rewards.
mlHelp_Body.127:
In the Challenge Tour, you can challenge the tour with the Fes Unit you produced. Each unit has a separate tour that can be challenged, and various rivals will appear.
Initial clear and mission are set for each stage. By completing this, you can earn rewards such as Prism Jewel.
mlHelp_Body.129:
You can change the plain clothes's costume and stage's costume that your idol owns. You can move the viewpoint with a swipe operation. You can zoom in and out of the camera with a pinch operation. .

■Idol
You can set your favorite idol on the Dress-Up Room screen.

■Costume
By selecting your favorite casual's costume or stage's costume, you can set You can dress up as your idol.

mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1:
Good job.
I've been thinking about the work you talked about.
Since then.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.2:
I want to try it.
Please let me try.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.4: I'm sorry for the late reply.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.5:
Don't worry about it.
Take your time to think.
It's fine because it's at Mano's pace.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.6:
Thank you.
I'll do my best.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.7:
Good job.
I'm sorry for contacting you suddenly.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.8:
I want to tell you directly,
but I'm not good at talking in person.
So, I thought I could convey it properly in writing.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.9:
Once again,
thank you always,
Producer-san.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.11:
Seeing Mano doing her best
also gives me energy.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.12:
Thank you.
I'm really happy to hear that.
I'll continue to do my best so that
you can keep feeling energetic.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.15:
Thank you, Producer-san.
I'm happy that you accompany me
with my clumsy words.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.16:
Good job.
Do you have time tomorrow?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.17:
I have something
I'd like to discuss.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.18:
It's okay.
Is it urgent?
I can call you now!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.19:
It's too sudden,
and it's not urgent,
so tomorrow is fine.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.26:
I understand that Hiori
is thinking about various things.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.27:
I already know that
it's just straightforward,
so you don't need to be shy.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.29:
That being said,
I think there are things
that need to be fixed, so
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.30:
Please tell me
when it's not good.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.32:
Hiori is expressing it in words, right?
I really appreciate it.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.33:
But,
the words aren't enough,
right?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.35:
You just need to communicate.
It's okay.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.37:
Is next Sunday
confirmed as a day off?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.38:
Yeah, it's confirmed.
Unless something urgent
comes up.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.40:
Yeah,
cheering for a friend's
club activity!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.42:
Of course.
Make sure not to schedule anything.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.46:
Yeah, good job.
What's up? Is something wrong?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.48:
I just thought lately you seem busy,
Producer.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.49:
You can't let a busy person
wait for your messages!!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.50:
No no,
this kind of exchange is also a break.
You can't underestimate small talk.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.52:
If the person himself says so,
then there's no mistake.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.54:
Tomorrow,
I'll make the best hot milk
for Producer!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.56:
thank you for your hard work.
I've arrived at the lesson venue.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.58:
I'll take a bit longer,
sorry!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.59:
I'm still on the train.
I'll hurry as much as possible.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.61:
I understand how you feel,
but it's dangerous to rush.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.62:
Okay!
I'll hurry while
being careful!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.63:
Thank you.
I intend to be careful.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.64:
However,
I don't want to keep Mano waiting,
so I'll hurry while being careful too.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.65:
Thank you.
I'm thinking of going at a
pace that suits both of us ^^
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.67:
Keep up the good work in your lessons too,
but be careful not to rush.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.68:
But it's dangerous to rush,
so be careful about that.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.70:
Of course!
Safety first!
I'll do my best!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.72:
The school festival job is tomorrow, right?
I'm starting to get nervous.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.73:
I've prepared as much as I can,
so all that's left is
to face tomorrow, but...
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.74:
I still worry
when it gets close
to the event.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.76:
Everyone can do it.
I believe in you all.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.77:
I'll do my best
to meet expectations.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.79:
Thank you.
I'll do my best with Hiori-chan
and Meguru-chan.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.80:
Thanks to Hiori-chan
and Meguru-chan too ^^
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.82:
Even if it's tough alone,
we can do it together as three!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.83:
That's right!!
If we work together,
it'll be okay for sure!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.85: What kind of power is that?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.86:
However,
I also think that if
it's the three of us,
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.87:
Thank you.
I'm sure it'll be okay
if we're together.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.88:
Oh no~~~
I forgot today's script~~~!!!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.89:
Then, it was on the office desk!
The one with the yellow cover, right?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.90: That's right!!! I'll rush back to the office~~~
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.91:
I'll bring it right now.
It's still in time, right?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.93:
Producer, are you in the office now??
Is it okay if I come???
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.95: Do you have something to do?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.96: I just wanted to see you!!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.97:
Haha,
I'm glad to hear that.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.98:
Well then,
I'll go right away!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.102: I just wanted to drop by for a bit!!!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.104:
Haha, sorry.
But I'm glad nothing's wrong.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.105:
I'll be in the office for a while,
so feel free to come anytime.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.109:
Yeah,
since we have a lesson today, I thought
I'd remind you just in case.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.112:
As long as you didn't forget,
it should be fine, right...?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.114:
I guess it was needless worry.
Sorry, sorry.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.115: It's good that someone reminded me like this.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.117:
I'm heading back now.
※There are some nice sweets
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.121:
Hm?
What do you mean by that...
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.122: It should be safe to eat, for now.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.123:
The way you say that
sounds incredibly ominous though...
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.127:
Is that so?
Well, I'm sure it's fine.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.128:
When you say it's fine,
it makes me even more anxious.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.129:
Knowing Mamimi,
she's probably up to something again.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.133:
Thanks for the update!
Then today's work is finished,
good job...!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.135:
Thank you.
I always think, but you're diligent,
aren't you?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.137:
Indeed.
Even now, you've probably looked after me,
right?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.139:
Sakuya always does her best,
so it's natural to consider her feelings.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.140:
Calling attention to your thoughtfulness
is both your virtue and something that
worries me.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.141:
Please accept your wonderful qualities
just as they are.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.143:
Being able to directly comfort your
favorite is not something that
happens often!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.144:
Honestly, you always seem to
think you're benefiting somehow.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.145:
Thank you.
I'm glad I could consult with you.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.146:
No, not at all!
Sorry, I wish I could have spoken to
you directly...
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.147:
No, not at all. It was very
encouraging.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.148:
Even though we're apart, even
through text, I can feel your warmth.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.150:
I'm glad you say that.
Feel free to tell me if anything comes up
in the future too.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.151:
Supporting Sakuya is
my job, after all!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.152:
Thank you.
Just hearing those words gives me
so much strength.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.153:
Good work! Do you
have a moment right now?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.156:
I wanted to discuss tomorrow's
shooting.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.157:
I see. Is it okay to talk
here? I can also call you.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.158:
Really? Then I'll call you,
just wait.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.159:
No, I'll call you.
Yuika is waiting.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.161:
Sorry for not replying
for so long! I've confirmed the details
of the shoot!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.163:
Aww, quick response!
Was I keeping you waiting?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.165:
I was waiting,
but I was also doing other work,
so it's no problem!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.166: Oh, you've been working so late...
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.169:
Hint: Received a summary
of the studio's usage.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.171: Are you okay to go home?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.172: I'm fine! I rode my scooter today!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.173:
I see. Well, be careful.
And make sure to get some rest, okay?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.174:
Thank you!
But you too, Producer!
Let's both make sure to
get proper rest!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.176:
The lesson's over.
I'm heading home now.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.178: I have a favor to ask.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.180:
Please give some water
to Yukinoshita-san.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.181:
Oh, got it.
Leave it to me.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.183: Be careful on your way home.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.186:
Thanks for the update.
How did it go?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.187: It went smoothly and ended early.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.188:
I see.
Kiriko is working hard too.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.191: You're coming to the office now, right?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.195:
Debut live was a huge success!!!
So happy~~~
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.197:
That's right.
We'll continue to strive to deliver
even more captivating performances.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.199: L'Antica is the best in the universe.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.200:
I'm expecting activities
worthy of the universe's best unit.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.201:
Thank you!!!
We're the strongest, so please
keep your expectations high!!!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.204:
Please do your best for
the future of L'Antica!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.206:
We'll be in trouble if you don't
give it your all~
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.208:
Let's have a strategy meeting for the live~~~
What's everyone's schedule???
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.209:
I'm available from the day
after tomorrow onwards...
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.210:
Tomorrow
and after that, it's tough.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.211:
I can make it the day
after tomorrow afternoon!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.213:
Hmm~~
Seems like it's hard to find
a time that works for everyone~~
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.216:
I'll try to adjust my schedule
so we can gather as much as possible.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.218:
I woke up really early today
and got to school first!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.219:
Being the first is amazing!
Was there something different than usual?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.220:
Since no one was there,
the classroom was still dark!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.221:
It was really quiet
and kind of weird!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.222:
It felt like something
was about to happen,
even though it was morning!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.225:
Good job on your work.
I'll be heading to the office soon.
Thank you in advance.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.226:
Got it.
This message seems a bit
formal today, doesn't it?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.227: It seems like a work-related message.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.228:
Yes!
Since what I'm doing is also work,
I looked it up!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.229:
I couldn't read the last part,
so I left it out...
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.235:
I'll be heading to the office now.
Thank you in advance for your cooperation!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.236:
Understood.
Please be careful on your way here.
We'll be waiting for you.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.237:
The snacks you brought,
they were really, really delicious...!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.239:
I'm glad you liked them!
I thought they might be your favorite flavor.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.240:
You got it right...!
As expected of Producer-san!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.241:
Even if you praise me so much,
nothing will come out of it.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.242:
I want to say that...
but this time, believe it or not,
there's another recommended snack...!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.243:
Amazing...!
Are you not too good at advertising...!?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.244:
I want to hear!
Please tell me more!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.246:
If you happen to stop by the convenience store,
please try the newly released chocolate sandwich...!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.247: Oh, is that a recommendation from the chocolate idol?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.248:
As a chocolate idol, yes,
but also as a comrade who has researched chocolate together...!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.249:
Surely it's a flavor you'll like,
Producer-san!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.250:
I see!
Looking forward to it.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.251:
There's no doubt when Chiyoko chooses snacks,
and if Chiyoko guarantees it's to my taste,
then I can't help but be excited.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.252:
When you put it like that,
it makes me a little nervous...!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.253:
But it should be fine!
Please look forward to it!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.254:
Work's done.
I'll be heading back to the office now.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.256:
I received a set of delicious-looking jellies,
but is everyone from Houkura coming today?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.257: Ah, that should be the case.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.258: Then I better hurry back and put them in the fridge.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.260: Surprisingly, it's a perfect set of six.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.263: Good job. Finishing so early means it went smoothly.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.265:
Producer,
are you still at the office?
I want to come back and
report and discuss some things.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.266:
Yeah,
I'll be here for a while,
so no need to rush.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.267:
Sorry for bothering you
when you're busy.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.268:
I'm still a rookie,
after all.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.271:
So, I'd like you to listen to various things.
Please take care of me, Producer-san.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.272:
Good work.
I'm currently on the train.
I think I'll arrive at the office in about an hour.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.273:
Thanks for getting in touch!
Were you okay by yourself?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.275:
The scenery from the train window
is incredibly beautiful,
captivating my gaze.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.277:
Don't get too lost in the scenery
and miss your stop.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.278:
Thank you for your concern.
I'll make sure to safely return to you,
Producer-sama.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.280:
It would be great if there's
another opportunity for work.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.281:
When that time comes,
please join me.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.282:
I apologize for earlier.
I caused you trouble.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.283:
It's nothing to worry about.
It was just a small slip-up in greetings.
The other party didn't seem to mind either.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.284:
But, a mistake is still a mistake.
I've brought shame to you, Producer-sama.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.285:
Don't dwell on it too much.
I'm fine.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.286:
Besides, it's my job to protect Rinze.
If anything happens, I'll definitely support you.
So, rest assured.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.290: I've been a bit flustered today.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.291:
Good work.
I'm going to practice on my own for a bit today.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.293:
There are parts of the choreography
that I just can't seem to agree with.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.294:
I want to perfect them now
while I have the chance.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.295:
Got it.
Just make sure you don't push
yourself too hard.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.298:
I'm fine, thanks.
Still on set?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.299:
Yes,
I'm on a break now.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.300:
I have some time,
so I thought I'd chat with you if you're available.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.302:
Even though it's your precious break time,
thank you.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.303:
Oh, it's only natural.
You're an important presence to me,
you know?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.304:
Make sure to rest properly
after this.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.305:
I think Natsuha will be fine,
but do your best.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.306:
Of course.
I'll always do my best.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.307:
And with your support,
failure is out of the question!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.308:
The training camp
at the abandoned school
was such a fun time.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.309:
I've only just returned,
but it already feels nostalgic.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.310:
I know, right?
I already want to do another
training camp!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.313:
But making it at the office
won't be the same,
right?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.314:
Let's recreate the
miraculous taste born
from that time.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.315:
Shall we do another
test of courage?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.316:
Then leave the
ghost role to me.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.318:
I also want to
try scaring people.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.319: Please spare me if you can!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.322:
Good work, everyone.
Make sure to rest well!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.323:
Good job!
Producer-san,
please make sure to rest as well!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.324:
You're the one who never rests,
Producer.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.329:
There's a thing called the
law of the person who suggests it.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.330:
I'll make sure to rest properly.
So, everyone else,
please make sure to rest too.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.332:
Next is the unit live meeting,
right?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.333:
Yeah,
see you at the meeting!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.335:
Wow, you read the magazine?!
Thank you!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.339:
Seems like the article was well-received.
The journalist even contacted us to say thanks.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.340:
Teenage readers resonated with
Chiyoko's genuine story,
so they said.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.341:
I'm humbled...!
If they enjoyed it,
then I'm glad...!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.344:
Because there are people who hear our voices,
we can shine too.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.347:
Yes!
But it was really fun!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.348:
The finished product
turned out well too.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.349:
It's all thanks to
everyone's hard work.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.350:
Houkura's challenge seems to
encourage those who see the pamphlet.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.351: I think it turned out like that.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.353:
If it turned out like that,
it's really heartwarming.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.354: And we can't afford to lose either.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.355:
That's right.
Houkura will also take a new step forward!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.360:
You're glowing.
Did something good happen?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.361:
That's correct!
The trainer praised me for
visible signs of effort!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.362:
That's good.
In that case,
I'd like to see it next time.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.363:
Yeah!
I'll adjust to Producer-san's schedule,
so let me know anytime!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.366:
Amana,
let's work even harder by then!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.367:
Producer-san,
I've confirmed the materials
you sent for the job!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.368:
Wow, that was quick!
That's helpful! Was there anything
that caught your attention?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.369:
It's a few days of shooting in a distant location,
so if there's anything you're worried about,
please let me know.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.370:
Thank you.
I think Amana will be fine.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.371:
Producer-san,
it said you'd accompany me on the trip,
but are you okay?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.372:
You're already busy,
so with this schedule,
won't you get really tired?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.373:
Thank you for worrying, but I'll be fine.
I believe I can manage my body properly.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.375:
But if things get tough, tell Amana.
I'll help with what I can.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.377:
I received a lot of snacks as gifts on set.
Can I take them all?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.378:
Sure, it's okay.
Thanks for checking.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.381: What kind of snacks did you get?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.386: If you have a lot of them.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.390: Good job! You worked hard today too.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.393: Make sure to get home safely.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.394: Don't close up shop until you get home...
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.395:
On days when things don't go well,
I want to pamper myself.
Taking a stroll through the
department store basement,
enjoying the finest chocolates
all to myself.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.397: Ah, sorry! I was jotting down ideas for my column!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.398:
I just wrote down whatever came to mind...
Ugh, embarrassing...
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.401:
If you ever need anything, feel free to talk to me.
I'll listen anytime.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.402:
Thank you, Producer-san...
I'll share some chocolates with you then.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.404:
Good work.
We finished recording the radio show.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.405:
The conversation flowed so well!
It was almost sad when the time was up.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.406:
That's good to hear.
I thought that guest would get along well with Chiyuki.
I'm glad we invited them.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.407:
Thank you.
They're reputed to rarely appear on radio shows,
so I wondered if it was difficult to arrange.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.408:
Haha,
it's part of my job.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.409:
Producer-san,
the way you say things so casually
without making it seem like a hassle,
it's really amazing.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.410:
I'm sorry,
I sent that prematurely.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.412:
To be able to express it so casually
without making it seem difficult,
it's truly impressive.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.413:
If I say it again,
it feels a bit embarrassing.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.414:
Well,
I'll do my best to bring in
more wonderful guests.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.415:
The lyrics of the
next song are wonderful!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.416:
I understand the feeling of wanting
to make someone special happy on
an important day.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.417:
I'm glad you like it.
I hope I can convey Chiyuki's
feelings through the song.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.418:
I hope this song becomes
something important for
the fans too.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.420:
When people listen to the song,
it's a special moment just
between them and me...
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.421:
I have to work hard to
make it something wonderful.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.422:
'Special day'...
Do you have days like that,
Producer-san?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.425:
Days filled with excitement and anticipation...
I wanted to know what kind of days they are for you,
Producer-san.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.428:
Yeah, listening to Chiyuki's solo song
and coming to the office...
Doing work like this lifts my spirits.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.429:
It's a bit embarrassing to hear you say that...
But thank you♪
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.431:
Since scouting Chiyuki,
every day has been special,
hasn't it?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.433:
Then, I'll make sure to make every day
even more special to keep you entertained,
Producer-san♪
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.434:
Summer goes by
in the blink of an eye,
doesn't it?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.437:
I want to go to the
festival again next year.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.448:
There's been no response
from her Chain for a while.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.452:
No, it's okay.
As long as she's safe.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.455: No, I'm sorry for making you worry.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.456: No, I was just checking on Twesta!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.459:
There were empty priority seats
on the train today, but
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.461:
Because someone else
might need it!!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.475:
Sorry, you tried to contact
me multiple times.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.477:
I was in a meeting
and couldn't answer right away.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.479:
No, I think it's better
to talk on the phone.
Are you available now?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.481:
Asahi,
have you forgotten that
the lesson time changed today?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.483:
Parfait, huh?
That means you're at a family restaurant, right?
I wonder which one it is.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.485:
Huh, you don't know?
Are you okay?
Should I come pick you up?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.487:
Good,
I was a bit worried
for a moment there.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.488:
If it's a nearby shop,
there's still time.
Take your time and enjoy your meal.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.494:
No reason.
There's no deep meaning behind it.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.495:
Just wanted to know,
that's all.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.497:
There's a new restaurant near the station,
and I've been curious about it.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.499: Huh? Yeah, if I have time.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.507:
Just testing.
Wanted to see how long
it takes to get a response.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.508:
Sorry about that.
I'll try to be more responsive.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.519:
Hey, I wonder if that was
written with Fuyuko in mind.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.522:
It feels like they made it
with the intention of conveying Fuyuko's charm,
or something like that.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.523:
Thanks.
You're saying something
that puts pressure on me.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.524:
Huh?
Did I phrase it wrong?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.525:
Well, I'll do my best.
In a Fuyuko-like way,
with all my might.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.528:
Got it. Well,
see you then.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.530:
Oh, speaking of which,
Fuyuko's solo song was playing earlier.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.532:
At a cafe, maybe.
It suddenly started playing inside the store.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.533:
Which cafe?
Is it a chain store?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.534:
Wait a moment,
let me remember.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.539:
So, I was on the train earlier
and I heard something like
'Stra, something'...
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.540: I thought it might be about us!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.541:
They were talking about
wanting to stop the game!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.544:
I also heard something like
'pro something' the other day and
almost responded.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.548:
If I had replied,
it would have been totally
embarrassing.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.551:
Producer!
Do you have time today?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.555:
I have homework!
It's too hard!
It's bad!!!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.558:
Of course,
but make sure you think
about it yourself too.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.560:
I'm going to call you 'God' today,
Producer!!!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.563:
Everyone,
even though there were various things,
great job and thank you very much.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.567:
No, no,
let's just let that go.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.568:
Well, that's just
the beginning, right?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.569:
Just watch,
Fuyuko will become the
top idol someday.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.572:
Asahi, I'm counting on you too!
Together, the three of us make up Straylight.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.581:
I haven't watched movies lately.
What's the title of the film?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.584:
The tuna exploded
and I thought it was dead,
but it was alive.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.585:
And then,
the lover was the culprit.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.587:
The other day,
I rode a swing.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.589: It used to be big and shiny before.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.590:
But I could still fly,
really high.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.591:
Swings, huh?
Sometimes you feel like riding one.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.592:
But, I try not to do
too many dangerous things, you know?
You might get hurt.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.594:
Hey,
do you think it will
rust someday, even now?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.595:
Now...
I guess so.
It might happen someday.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.596:
But even if it does rust,
you can always polish it again.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.601: Ah, sorry for making you worry.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.602:
If you see Koito,
please convey that message.
She was concerned.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.603:
It's counterproductive if you
push people too hard and end up
compromising your idols health.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.604:
Yeah,
I'll make sure to
take care of everyone.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.605:
That's all for the discussion.
Goodbye.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.607:
Madoka, make sure to take care
of your throat since it seems a bit dry.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.610:
I'll borrow the key
to the practice room.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.612: Try not to stay out too late.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.617:
It seems like Madoka's
progress is impressive.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.618:
Just continue doing things your way,
Madoka.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.622: We're also looking forward to the melody.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.623:
Ah, as soon as I receive it,
I'll send it over.
They say the song fits well
with Madoka's voice.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.625:
Even if it's just
interpreting the lyrics for now,
I'll proceed.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.626:
I've been getting more
opportunities to work on my
solo song at my workplace.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.627:
It's great to see Madoka's
work being recognized.
I'm happy for her.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.629:
The lyrics and melody matched well,
so I think the evaluation would have been
positive even if it weren't me.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.630:
Certainly,
both the lyrics and
melody were good.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.631:
But I think I was able
to achieve better expression
precisely because it was me, Madoka.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.632:
Well, in the end,
results are everything.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.634:
I'll strive not to let
my efforts go to waste.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.635:
Is the practice
room available today?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.637:
That's good.
I want to practice right
after lunch, is that okay?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.638:
Sure, I'll keep it reserved.
You've been even more diligent lately.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.639:
Yes,
I left earlier than everyone
else the other day.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.640:
I want to make up
for the time I was late.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.641:
It's okay.
You're not late at all.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.643:
But just in case,
I want to practice.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.644:
No matter how
much you practice,
it's never a waste.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.646:
That's not true.
It's only natural!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.648: Is it for my solo job?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.649:
It's a light interview job,
but can I ask you?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.650:
They might ask about
the unit and our future.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.652:
Honestly,
I still don't know about the future.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.653: I want to be with everyone, but...
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.656:
Is it okay even if I can't say
anything specific about the future?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.657:
Wanting to be with everyone
is Koito's honest feeling.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.659:
Yes, understood.
Thank you very much!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.660:
I'm indecisive about the nail color!
Which color do you think is good?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.663:
If I paint them,
I'll show you again!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.666:
Red, huh? Yeah,
I'll try painting them a bit!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.668:
If it's Hinana,
I think any color would suit her.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.671:
I'm going to the office
in new clothes today!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.672:
Did you buy the
one you wanted before?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.673:
Eh!
Did you remember by any chance?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.674:
Of course I did.
You really liked it.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.677:
Don't get too excited
and fall over.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.678:
Okay!
Well then, see you later.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.680:
Finally.
It's good for a while.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.682:
Yeah, it might be lonely,
but I thought of something that
could make us happier.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.684:
Let's go to an
all-you-can-eat sweets buffet!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.686:
There's a shop
I've been curious about.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.688:
Haha, then I'll make
a reservation.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.689:
The show we recorded the other day
will finally air today.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.690:
No need for reminders.
I know, so don't worry.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.691:
Or rather,
aren't you looking forward
to it more than me?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.692:
If Nichika has a part,
you can't miss it.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.695:
By the way,
could you also record it for me?
I'll check it later.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.696:
Also,
please let me know
the good parts.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.700:
I'm not sure if
I enjoyed it, but
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.701:
I made eye contact
with the audience.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.704:
I wonder why you
were looking at me,
even though Mikoto-san was
right next to you.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.705:
Because I wanted to see Nichika,
right?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.707:
Were you deliberately
looking at the less skilled one
and finding it amusing?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.709:
I hope you won't
forget the people who
were watching Nichika today.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.710:
Nichika is already an idol,
so I think she was captivating
everyone's attention.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.711:
I understand that
much even without being told.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.712:
Until what time are you
using the practice room today?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.713:
Are you okay?
You're not overworking
yourself again, are you?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.714:
Sorry,
I just realized it now.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.715:
I've just finished.
I'll lock up and leave.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.716:
Oh, did you need
to use the practice room?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.718:
I might be staying late,
so I thought I'd come
to get the key.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.720:
Mikoto,
make sure you don't push
yourself too hard.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.721:
How was today's
performance from Producer's
perspective?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.724:
I think I was able
to showcase my skills.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.725:
But I still have
a long way to go.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.726:
I want to make
even better stages.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.728:
Then I'll work harder
together with you.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.729:
Yeah, could you send
me today's video later?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.731:
And I'd like to use
the practice room as well.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.732:
No, let's rest properly today.
We need to give our bodies
a break after the stage.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.733:
Okay, I understand.
Thanks for considering.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.734:
The recording of the last stage arrived.
Both of you were amazing.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.735:
You can check it when
you come to the office,
so let me know if you
want to see it.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.736: No need to go out of your way to inform us.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.738:
After dance practice,
let's check the recording.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.740: I want to check it too.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.741:
Roger.
Let's do our best
for the next stage.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.745:
I want a response
when you see this.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.749:
If there's anything
you're struggling with,
please tell me.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.752:
I contacted you because
there was something bothering
me about today's stage.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.753:
You seemed unwell
during the performance.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.756:
If anything's wrong,
please tell me.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.759:
If you're okay with it,
I'm always here to listen.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.761:
Stop contacting me
all the time.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.765:
That is also
part of the job...!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.766:
Huh,
you think Producer
is working?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.769:
Then, just for now,
let's consider it private.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.772:
↑
To Producer during
their private time
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.776:
Is it Okayama dialect?
What does it mean?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.777:
It's like getting into
the spirit, I think?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.778:
Is that so?
I've learned something new.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.779:
Producer,
let's start getting into it too.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.781:
Producer-san,
I went to see the movie
you recommended.
It was really good!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.782:
I couldn't help but cry.
A handkerchief was definitely necessary.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.783:
Oh,
I'm glad you enjoyed it.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.784:
Haruki,
what did you particularly
like about it?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.785:
I'm sorry.
I was just about to tell you.
I was thinking about how
to phrase it.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.786:
It seems like
it's going to be
a really long message.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.787:
I see.
In that case,
I'm even more curious.
Maybe we can talk about
it when we meet in person.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.788:
That's great.
I really want to
hear about it!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.789:
Actually,
I'm about to head to the office.
Is Producer-san there?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.790:
Oh, I'm here.
When Haruki arrives,
I'll take a break.
Tell me all about it then.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.791: Well, I'm heading there now! Please wait for me.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.792:
Sorry for the late response.
I just finished work.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.793:
Good job.
It took quite a while,
didn't it?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.794:
I'm sorry,
actually I finished much earlier,
but I was staring at
the sunset absentmindedly,
and before I knew it,
it was this late.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.797:
Actually,
there was a little issue
that didn't go as smoothly as I hoped.
We managed to resolve it on set,
but it's been bothering
me for a while.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.798:
I see.
I'm here to listen whenever
you want to talk about it.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.799:
Thank you.
But I realized I need to solve
some things on my own occasionally.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.800:
Hmm,
am I really that unreliable?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.801:
That's not true!
I really rely on you!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.802:
Actually,
I feel like I rely
on you too much.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.803:
But talking about it will
surely lead to a quicker resolution, right?
Can I tell you about it again?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.805: The one from the other day,
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.806:
The stage we stood on
as CoMETIK was fun,
wasn't it?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.808:
I'm still feeling
excited about it~
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.809:
Both of you,
we have the footage
from that time.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.810:
Should we all watch it
together at the office
next time?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.814:
If you read this,
get in touch.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.816:
Tell me one good thing
that happened today.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.817:
A good thing...
The weather was really nice today.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.818:
I didn't have any
homework today.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.819:
The coffee I got at
work was delicious.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.820:
I got to chat with
Producer at the chain.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.822: But it's still a good thing.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.823:
If you say so,
then I guess so too.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.824:
I got to chain
with Toru today too.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.828:
I put some snacks in
the office fridge for you.
Feel free to have them
when you come by.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.829:
Looking forward to it!
Are they good ones?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.830:
Nah,
they're just snacks you can
buy at the shopping arcade near the office.
The sales association came
by earlier to say hello.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.831:
There aren't many,
so it's first come,
first served.
Sorry if there's none left.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.833:
I'm busy today,
so I can't go...
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.838:
Just to confirm,
there are no appointments
for today anymore, right?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.839:
The meeting has been rescheduled.
There's nothing else.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.843:
Yeah, I am.
Because I swapped with
someone last time.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.847:
Impressive, Madoka!
That kind of thoughtfulness
is important.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.848:
Let me know when
the meeting schedule is set.
Goodbye.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.849:
Producer-san,
are you at
the office?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.851:
Actually,
I wanted to bring
you a gift.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.852:
The sweets we had with
Hana-chan last time were delicious,
so I thought I'd bring some
for you too, Producer-san.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.854:
When Hana-chan and I
went there last time,
we had a drink with a
marshmallow snowman on top.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.855:
It was so cute
that I hesitated
to drink it.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.857:
If you get the chance,
Producer-san, you should try it too.
It's a limited-time offer,
so do it sooner rather than later.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.858:
Now that you mention it,
I'm curious. I'll try to find
some time to go.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.859:
I'm sorry for bothering you,
Producer-san.
You're busy, after all.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.860:
I'll hurry and
bring the gift,
so cheer up with it.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.861:
You don't need
to hurry, it's okay.
Thank you.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.862:
It's about the
temporary song data
I sent this morning.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.863:
I'd be happy if
you could let me
know once you've
checked.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.873:
Everyone,
it seems like the Hanamuke no Hanataba video
is airing on the street vision today.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.874:
I'll try to find time
to go see it too.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.876: I want to see it too.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.877: I saw it a moment ago.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.879:
Then,
shall we all go
see it together?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.881:
Is it okay
if I join too?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.886:
Sorry for the late reply.
It got a bit delayed,
but it's finished safely.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.887:
It's already late,
so I'll head straight home.
Producer, are you done with work?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.888:
Thanks!
I was just about
to head home too.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.889:
Producer,
are you staying at the office late every day?
Make sure to get some rest.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.891:
I'll go out
and refresh on
the next day off.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.892:
That sounds nice.
How about a puzzle-solving activity?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.893:
The other day,
I went with Mano and Meguru.
It was fun.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.894:
I see.
Thanks for recommending it.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.895:
It's refreshing because
you use your brain differently
than usual.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.896:
Yeah, you need
creativity and flexibility.
It's not just about
academic skills.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.897:
That sounds exciting.
I'm looking forward
to it.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.899:
I'll send you
the New Year photos
you asked for.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.902:
I see.
This is fine too,
but...
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.903:
Sorry.
I'd be happy if the photo
includes everyone.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.904:
Can I ask
for another option?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.907:
Producer-san,
thank you again for earlier.
I'm relieved that the
Live stream went smoothly ^^
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.909:
I mentioned it earlier,
but Mano's essence came
through really well.
It was great.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.910:
Thank you.
Your words, Producer-san,
are very reassuring.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.911:
I wish I could convey
more gratitude to everyone
who watched.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.912:
It's okay, Mano did great.
You handled it well on your own,
and the fans understand too!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.913:
I'm really happy
to hear that ^^
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.914:
This was a great experience.
Thank you very much.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.918:
I was surprised how much
time had passed.
Was it okay?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.919:
I feel like we didn't talk
about much considering
the time...
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.920:
Really?
You got a lot of comments,
and you introduced yourself well.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.922:
Good job.
The shooting is done!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.926:
Lately, there's been
a lot of heavy work,
but you've been working hard.
I really appreciate it.
Thank you.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.927:
Oh,
stop with the
sudden praise!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.928:
But you've been
working hard too,right?
Mitsumine saw, in a decisive moment.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.930:
The other day,
you were sound asleep
in the office.
It felt like a dream.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.931:
No way,
I didn't know about that.
So, you didn't notice when
Mitsumine came?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.935:
I've listened
to the solo song.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.936:
It's a wonderful song,
and I've been listening
to it repeatedly.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.939:
I'll sing
with all my heart
and soul.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.940:
Seems like your solo
song is getting good reviews.
That's great!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.942:
Let's keep singing
a lot in the future.
Fans must be hoping for that.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.943:
Producer-sama,
would you like that too?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.944:
Of course!
It's a great song,
and I want to listen
to it over and over.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.946:
If you wish,
I'll sing it as many
times as you like.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.948:
and your precious hearts,
may flowers bloom.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.949:
The unit live has
been officially decided.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.952:
I'm also looking forward to it♪
Thank you so much, Producer-san,
for your efforts.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.953:
No, thank you.
I'm excited to see what
kind of stage everyone
will show.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.954:
So,
I want to hear everyone's
ideas about the theme
and production of this live.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.955:
Just think about it roughly
and come up with some ideas.
How about that?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.956:
Got it!
What kind of ideas
would be good?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.957:
Why don't we all bring our
ideas together and discuss?
I think we'll come up
with some wonderful ideas.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.960:
Good work.
Sorry for suddenly bothering you.
Chiyoko, is there anything
troubling you right now...?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.961:
Good work!
Thank you for reaching out!
Nothing in particular...
I think.
Was there something...?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.962:
The trainer mentioned
that Chiyoko looked troubled
before the lesson.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.963:
Since it was around
the time your solo song arrived,
I thought something might
have happened.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.964:
I'm sorry for worrying unnecessarily!
It's probably nothing to
worry about at all!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.966:
A body that starts
humming the solo song.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.967:
I was probably trying
to suppress it,
which might have
made me look troubled.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.968:
Yes,
it's a body that starts
humming the solo song!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.969:
So, there's really
nothing to worry about!
Thank you for your concern,
and I apologize for
causing a stir!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.970:
No, no, not at all!
I'm just glad Chiyoko isn't troubled.
It seems like you're getting
used to the solo song.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.972:
The other day,
I had a choco sundae
at a cafe.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.973:
It reminded me of
'Choco Date Sundae',
and I couldn't help but smile!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.974:
You're really
captivated by that song!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.976:
Thanks to you,
I've been able to form
a connection with wonderful songs!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.977:
I'm filled with gratitude.
Thank you so much...
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.978:
No, it's not.
Your hard work so far
has led to this solo song.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.982:
Meguru, good job today.
It was a good stream.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.983:
You said that when
it ended too, but really?
Wasn't it a bit chaotic?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.984:
I had fun,
but wasn't it
a bit chaotic?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.985:
Didn't you hear
it when it ended?
I had fun too,
so it's okay.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.986:
I feel like I'm
starting to think it's okay!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.987:
That's good to hear.
I'll be looking forward
to the next one!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.988:
I'm starting to
feel anxious again!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.993:
I see.
Seems like you
did a good job.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.994:
Yeah.
It felt different from the usual stage...
It was like talking with friends...
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.995:
I'm really happy that
I could talk a lot about
L'Antica to all the fans...
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.996:
Hehe,
it's thanks to Producer
and everyone's encouragement!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.997:
Haha,
I'm glad if I
could be of help.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.998:
Yeah!
I'll keep doing my best from now on,
so please continue supporting me,
Producer!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.999:
I heard the production of
the new song is going smoothly.
The one with the provisional
vocals should be ready soon too.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1001:
But the mini-live is also coming up,
so maybe we should focus on that.
If you don't have time to listen right away,
it's okay to take your time.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1002:
I'm okay.
I'll share it right away.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1003: Please share it with me too.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1004:
I'd like to hear it
as soon as possible.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1005:
Thank you both.
Once I receive the data,
I'll send it immediately.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1008:
I'm excited for
any kind of song.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1010:
Good job at the release event today!
It was really exciting.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1012:
We gave it our all in the
performance as much
as we could.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1013:
Yeah,
it was a great stage.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1015: I heard a lot of voices.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1016:
Events like that
make us feel closer
to the fans.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1017:
It feels like our feelings
reach the fans more directly
than usual live performances.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1019:
Good work!
Sorry for the late message,
but the filming for today has finished!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1020:
I'll go home with
Juri-chan and Rinze-chan!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1021:
Thank you for your hard work,
and thanks for getting in touch.
It seems like it took quite a while,
but were you okay?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1022:
I'm sorry for making you worry...!
There weren't any troubles,
so everything's fine!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1023:
The photographer seemed
to really like us
wearing glasses,
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1024:
so they ended up taking
more photos than planned...!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1025:
I see,
so that's what happened!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1026:
Isn't this the first step
to success in our strategy?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1028:
Letting the world know that
cool photoshoots are a piece of cake...
We'll keep thinking of various
strategies from now on.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1029:
Thank you very much!
Please continue to support
us from now on!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1031: I can't make it to today's meeting.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1033:
It was for a
drama shoot, right?
You didn't do anything
wrong, did you?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1034:
No need to worry.
It's actually the opposite.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1035:
The director really likes Asahi
and wants to take even better shots,
so they've decided to extend the shoot.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1038:
Looks like we'll have to.
I'm sorry.
I'll adjust and get back to you.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1041:
There are things we
can't decide without you.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1050:
Are you perhaps
worried about the
reaction to the stream?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1052:
Don't worry.
I checked Twesta for feedback,
and it seems like fans are liking it.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1054:
If there's a chance,
I'd be willing to
do it again.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1055:
Looks like you're motivated.
I'm looking forward to it.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1057:
I searched Twesta
for feedback on
today's stream.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1058:
I was curious about
what everyone thought.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1059:
And then,
I found a comment saying,
'I'm glad I got to meet
idol Sakuya-san.'
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1061:
Yeah.
There are probably many
people who wouldn't have
met if they hadn't become idols.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1062:
Every time I think about that,
I can't help but be grateful to you.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1063:
I just scouted you.
I think if it weren't for Sakuya's efforts,
you wouldn't have met so many people.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1064:
Is that so?
But I can only work hard
because you're here.
I want you to understand that.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1065:
There was someone taking
pictures of cherry blossoms earlier,
so I couldn't resist taking some too!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1066:
There are so many
places in full bloom.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1068:
It feels like
spring has arrived...
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1069:
We might discuss such
topics during recording.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1070:
Certainly, considering the timing.
Episodes related to spring
might be in demand.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1071:
We need to prepare
what to talk about.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1072:
Yeah,
I want to create many spring
stories with everyone.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1073:
Mano's drama will
finally be broadcasted.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1074:
The one Mano
worked hard on!
Exciting!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1075:
I'll record it too.
Looking forward to it.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1077:
I'd be happy if
everyone enjoyed it.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1078:
I think we were able to
create a wonderful work by
working together with the
director and fellow actors.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1079:
The atmosphere on set was amazing.
I'm sure it'll come through.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1082:
Producer-san,
you seemed a little tired today.
Are you okay?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1083:
Is your work tough?
Are you not getting
enough sleep?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1084:
Sorry!
I didn't mean to worry you,
but I'm fine.
I just had trouble falling asleep today,
that's all.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1085:
I see...!
That's good to hear...
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1087:
Even though I don't have any worries,
sometimes that happens.
I wonder why...
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1088:
Could it be
because of the futon?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1089:
The other day,
I went to a bedding exhibition
with Tenka-chan and Chiyuki-san,
and there was something that said,
'Perfect for improving sleep quality.'
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1090:
Oh, they have something like that?
I'd like to try it out.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1091:
It felt so comfortable!
When I lay down,
it felt like I was being enveloped!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1092:
I remember the name
of the futon, so I'll send
you the URL later!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1094:
But if I sleep on such
a comfortable futon,
I might not be able
to wake up.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1095:
Indeed...!
A futon that's too comfortable
might be dangerous too...!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1098:
I'm happy that fans seem
to be enjoying the stream!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1100:
Yeah,
I was reading the feedback too.
It's great, isn't it...!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1102:
What should we do
next to keep this
enthusiasm going?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1103:
As expected of P-tan,
always dedicated to work!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1104:
Because the idols
I'm in charge of are so
dedicated to their work,
I want to work hard
to meet their expectations.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1107:
Do you all have time later?
I have something to discuss
at the office.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1112:
If you want to talk
about something important.
You could speak directly.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1113:
It's not like that.
Don't worry.
Everyone is doing well.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1114:
I have something
I want to discuss.
I'll talk about it
in detail then.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1115:
I listened to
the new song.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1117:
I listened to it
multiple times because
it made me happy.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1118:
It reminded me of
various times and
things.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1119:
I see.
Surely, those who listen to
Kiriko's song will also recall
various times and things.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1120:
Just like Kiriko,
various times and things.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1121:
Let's make it a
good song for that.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1123:
The reception for the
new song is excellent.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1124:
We also received a
lot of fan letters,
so if you'd like,
read them later.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1126:
Kiriko's song will
continue to comfort
everyone from now on.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1139:
I miss everyone so much~
I want to see
you all more!!!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1140:
Didn't we meet
at the office a
little while ago?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1141:
We've been missing each
other for the past few days.
I understand Kogane's
lonely feelings.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1142:
I miss Mamimi's
retorts these days too!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1143:
Then let me retort here.
Why, I say.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1145: I want to see everyone too.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1146:
Actually,
we've received a proposal
that's perfect for everyone.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1147:
It's a job where
all five members of
L'Antica are together!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1150:
Did you see the
CM for the mini-drama??
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1151:
I saw it!
They're really putting
effort into the promotion!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1152:
I wonder if more
people will watch
the drama.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1153:
Everyone will
definitely watch it!!
It looked super interesting!!!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1154:
The cafe [Le Moment]
was portrayed as a very
charming place, wasn't it?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1155:
Yeah!
I want to become a
regular there already.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1156:
I wanted to go there
as a customer too.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1158:
I'll treat you to Espuma
shaved ice anytime~~~!!!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1159:
I was asked if I
wanted to listen to something
while riding in a taxi.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1160:
But I didn't have
anything particular in mind.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1161:
I wonder what I
should have answered.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1162:
Was it about the
radio channel?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1163:
If you didn't have
anything in mind,
I think it's fine to
say you don't need anything.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1165:
I'll answer like
that next time.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1166:
Yeah, you might come
across a good song by chance.
