mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.2: Oh, welcome back, Mano. What's up?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.3: I'm, I'm sorry... I took some time getting ready to leave...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.4: I might be a little late returning the key to the practice room...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.5: Ah, I see. Thanks for letting me know.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.6: It's okay, it's just a little late, so no problem.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.7: Um... I'll try to hurry... I'm sorry for the inconvenience...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.8: ──No, yeah. I'm glad you're in a hurry.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.9: But you don't need to rush, just come at your own pace.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.13: Good job! Thanks for letting me know. How was it?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.14: ......Yes... um... I feel like I did well today...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.15: Thanks to the advice you gave me, Producer-san...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.16: Haha, that's good to hear. Sorry I couldn't be there on set.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.18: I was working while recalling your words...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.19: I felt like you were always nearby...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.23: ......It's a big cloud shaped like a fish...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.24: ......Haha, it looks like it's swimming leisurely...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.26: ......Oops! I was supposed to catch the bus...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.27: I'm really sorry, I got sidetracked from the work report...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.30: ......Also, it's really fun looking at the same sky as you, Producer-san...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.31: Thank you for taking a break outside, Producer-san.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.32: Producer, good job. I finished today's work, so here's my report.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.33: Good job, Hiori. Right on schedule, as expected.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.34: No, it's all thanks to the staff that everything went smoothly.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.35: Even though I did my best, all I noticed was room for improvement and reflection... I still have a long way to go.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.38: There's no such thing as a perfect person. Plus, reflecting means there's room for growth.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.40: Hiori, you're still ahead of the game! Let's reflect and move forward aggressively!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.41: You suddenly got so passionate...? But... thank you.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.42: If you're okay with it, please let me consult you directly about today's insights and reflections.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.46: Oh, no, good work. Did today's work go well?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.47: Um... yes. I was praised for having a good smile...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.49: Your voice sounded a bit livelier. I figured something good must have happened.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.53: Just from my voice, you were able to understand that much, Producer. That's all I was thinking.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.54: ──Well then, see you tomorrow. Good job.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.55: Yeah, see you tomorrow... Oh, right. Is it still okay for you, Hiori? Do you have time?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.56: ...? Yes, it's fine. Did you forget something...?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.57: No, no, work is all good. Now it's just chatting.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.58: Hiori, you said you liked this outfit, right? I was talking about it with the staff today.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.59: Since you have an idea of that kind of dress, if you're okay with it, come try it on.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.61: No, no! I just spoke without thinking! If anything, I should apologize.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.62: Hiori, I noticed you were serious, so I couldn't help but think if there was anything I could do.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.63: No...! Um... I'm happy. Thank you very much.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.64: I'd like to hear more about that tomorrow. Let me thank you again properly then.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.68: Haha, sorry! I guess that was a surprise out of nowhere!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.70: No, nothing! But I just felt like telling you something right now!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.71: I thought about whether it was okay to call suddenly or if it was the right time.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.72: I'm glad you picked up! So, thank you for that too!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.73: Haha, it's just 'thank you' all the time.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.74: Hehehe, yeah. Because I wanted to say 'thank you'!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.75: Hey hey, Producer. Can I ask you something weird all of a sudden?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.77: Is being a producer fun for you?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.78: Of course. It's fulfilling, and there's a sense of accomplishment.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.80: Do you have any thoughts about it?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.81: Hmm... I always think work is fun, you know?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.82: So, I hope that 'fun' can reach the people watching, and I hope I can feel fun too...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.83: But, it's probably not just me. It's probably better if Producer, Mano, and Hiori are all having fun...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.84: I'm not sure what I wanted to say anymore! I'm just glad you enjoy your work, Producer!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.86: Haha, sounds like it went well. I can tell from your voice.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.88: I gave it my all in the audition, so the judges were probably impressed!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.89: Oh, I'm looking forward to the results.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.91: It's thanks to Producer for discovering talent in our idols.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.92: I'll work hard and repay that favor...! Look forward to it~!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.93: Producer, are you available now? I have something to discuss.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.95: I'm going grocery shopping for dinner...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.96: ...And, your face just came to mind out of the blue...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.97: I wondered what you might want to eat... And then...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.98: Um... So, you want my opinion?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.99: Y-Yeah... I guess I was wondering... Sorry for bothering you while you're working...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.100: Haha, it's fine. Feel free to talk to me about anything, even if it's nothing important.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.102: If... if you finish work and feel hungry...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.103: Let me know... I'll make something and bring it over... Anything you want to eat...?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.106: I was walking home from shopping, and then a ball came rolling towards me...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.107: I tried to jump over it, but I tripped and fell...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.109: I accidentally spilled the vegetables I bought on sale all over the road~! It was a disaster...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.111: I'm okay! Just stumbled a bit, so it doesn't hurt much.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.112: I-I see. Well, that's a relief.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.113: N-No, it's not...! I wanted to jump gracefully like a rabbit...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.114: I wanted to jump more smoothly and elegantly... Producer, I want you to train me!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.116: Hehe~ Were you busy with work?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.117: Well, yeah, but... Was there a problem?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.118: No, there isn't, but... Do you know where I am right now, Producer?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.119: Where you are, Mamimi...? Uh... Where could it be...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.120: The correct answer is, I'm in bed at home~!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.121: I'm going to take a nap now, so I wanted to boast to the busy Producer.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.124: I'm starting to feel pleasantly sleepy. Maybe your voice has a healing effect, Producer.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.125: Well then, with that said, please do your best at work.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.131: I plan to continue from now on.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.133: Yes. It's important, so I wanted to report it properly.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.135: No, it's not like that... Haha...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.136: But I'm glad you said that, Mamimi. You've been working diligently lately.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.137: I think that's just your imagination.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.138: Well then, I'll continue to do my best from now on, so please keep an eye on me.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.139: I'm tired today, so I'll head home without stopping by the office.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.140: Alright, good work. The shoot must have been tough.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.141: Well... The set and costumes were elaborate, so...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.143: I wonder... I was praised for my performance, but...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.144: Maybe I'd prefer a more relaxed, laid-back job next time.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.146: Yes, something like eating snacks and lazing around, and still getting praised.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.147: There aren't many jobs like that...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.148: Really? Well then, please do your best, Producer.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.149: Hello, Sakuya? What's wrong? Did something happen?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.150: Oh my, I can't accept that, Producer.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.151: It's almost as if you shouldn't call without having a reason. We could use a bit more playfulness, don't you think?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.152: Whoops, you're right. That was a bit blunt, wasn't it...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.153: ─ 'I unexpectedly heard Sakuya's voice and it made me happy.' ... So, what do you think?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.155: If those words are truly heartfelt, then the maiden within me would feel like she's soaring to the heavens...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.156: Of course, they're from the heart.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.158: Leading on an innocent maiden... What are you planning to do?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.160: Sorry for calling out of the blue, Producer...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.162: ...That is, I don't particularly have any specific reason...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.164: ...I see. But if you called me, then that's something to be happy about.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.166: I actually wanted to ask you something, Sakuya. I got a winning ticket from the vending machine earlier.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.167: I chose the juice you said was delicious. It's really... addictive!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.168: .......... Oh, I see. If you also think so, then I'm happy...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.170: Ah, I didn't make it in time~...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.171: Huh, what...!? What do you mean you didn't make it...?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.173: I was actually trying to send a message... It was a mis-tap... an accidental call, so to speak.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.175: You wanted to end the call before it connected.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.176: Got it! Sorry for the weird call, Producer...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.177: No problem at all. So, what was it about the message you were trying to send?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.178: Oh, yeah. I just wanted to confirm something...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.180: Yeah, I'm fine... Oh, wait. Can I say something first? I have something I want to say.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.182: I heard that yesterday Yuika accepted a package addressed to me and left it on my desk.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.184: ──Jeez, what was that about~! You totally got me!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.186: And besides, you didn't have to go through all that trouble...! You could have just said it was thanks to the fairies or something.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.187: Well, you know... I'm the type who wants to find fairies.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.188: I think it's kinda weird for a grown adult to talk about fairies, you know~
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.191: ......──Well, whatever. That's all from me. Tell me what Yuika wanted──
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.193: Oh, what's up? You have auditions later, right?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.194: Yes... But before that... Can we talk for a bit...?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.195: ......! Sorry, I can't hang around today.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.196: If it's Kiriko, she'll be fine if you treat her like usual.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.197: ────Oh, right. Do you still have the candy I gave you before you left?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.199: That candy gives you strength when you eat it. I want you to try it, even if you think I'm tricking you.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.201: Okay... I'll eat it... and do my best...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.203: Thanks for letting me know. How did it go?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.204: I was a little... worried, but...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.205: It was... at a really beautiful waterside...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.206: A big bird... came to see us...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.207: ...Oh. Maybe it came to see Kiriko.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.209: ──I wish I could turn into a bird too, then I could go see Kiriko.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.222: Good work! HO-KA-GO CLIMAX GIRLS, job completed!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.223: Hey, good work. Today, Kaho was in charge of the report, huh.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.225: I wanted to report to Producer-san! So I asked everyone for help!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.227: Reporting is important, so thanks for taking on this important role, Kaho.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.229: Thanks. By the way, can I ask you to pass on a message to everyone?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.231: I'll definitely make sure to pass it on!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.232: Producer-san! Are you at the office today!?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.233: Yeah, I'm here. What's up? Do you need something?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.234: No, I don't need anything... but...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.235: I want to visit the office!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.238: Today we have some fancy snacks, so look forward to it.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.239: Wow! Once I put my backpack at home, I'll hurry there!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.242: We played dodgeball in PE class!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.243: Oh, how was it? Did you win?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.245: But, I managed to stay in the infield until the end!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.246: Impressive, Kaho. With the outfield increasing rapidly, it's tough to stay in.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.248: Today I felt like I could do it, and when I tried, I did it!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.250: 'Felt like I could do it' huh...! It must have been an invincible day!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.251: Invincible...! Hehe... Yes! I was invincible!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.252: Good work! Producer-san, are you okay now?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.254: How many people will come to the office tomorrow...?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.255: Also, I'd like to ask if Producer-san prefers custard cream or chocolate cream!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.256: Haha, are you possibly trying to buy snacks for us?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.257: Yes! It's from a local shop, they have incredibly delicious cream puffs...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.258: When I saw them at the department store event, I decided I wouldn't miss them!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.259: Since I'll stop by the office tomorrow, I thought of bringing them for everyone, but they won't keep long...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.260: I see, I see. If Chiyoko says they're delicious, then I'm looking forward to it. ──But just one for now.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.262: Don't you think it's a foolish question whether to choose chocolate or custard?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.264: I apologize, one chocolate confirmed. Understood! What else should we do...?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.269: ──I won the right to purchase limited edition chocolates!!!!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.271: Oh, is it the one we talked about the other day...!?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.273: I was so anxious about my luck, I thought I might not win, so I'm really happy...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.274: Well... good for you, Chiyoko...! Congratulations!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.276: As long as there's no limit on the quantity, I plan to buy enough for us and everyone in the office to enjoy...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.278: Sorry for not being able to pick up earlier...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.279: No, it's fine. Sorry for having you call back. Are you okay now? Are you in the middle of something...?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.280: I'm fine! Actually, I'm glad you called...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.282: I was planning to do my homework, but it seems like I fell asleep without realizing it...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.283: I woke up because of the phone ringing. I'm glad I woke up before it was too late...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.285: ──Then I should quickly finish my homework so I won't run out of time, right?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.286: Oh, no, no! You don't have to worry about that...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.287: Please talk as much as you need to! Feel free to ask whatever you need...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.290: ──So the introduction is done, but... I should probably watch some of the director's past works.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.291: I see. Then I'll pick out a few for you to watch.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.292: ──Haha, Juri always manages to find tasks and improvement suggestions, it's amazing.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.293: Oh... is that so? But, I might overlook something too...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.294: Because we have a producer who gives us better suggestions and advice, we can have these discussions.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.295: Hmm, when you put it that way... It makes me feel even more determined...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.296: Ahaha. You don't have to worry so much, ──but, well, I'm counting on you.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.299: Oh, it's nothing. I'm glad I got to hear your voice. Thanks.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.300: Hello? Producer-san, our self-practice just ended.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.301: Thanks for letting me know. You worked hard until quite late.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.302: Yeah. I wanted to finish perfectly.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.303: You don't want to disappoint the people who come to see you, right?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.304: I'm glad I scouted Juri back then...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.305: W-What's gotten into you all of a sudden...!?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.306: Because she puts in so much effort, thinking about the fans and practicing hard.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.307: I'm sure that sincerity will come across to the people watching.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.309: And, remember, those people watching also include the Producer, okay? Make sure to watch over us properly.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.311: S-Sorry...! I'll be there soon, just wait a little longer...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.312: As soon as the pedestrian light turns green... I'll run, it's close...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.317: Producer-sama... Right now... at the intersection...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.323: Huh, that much...? It seems like where Rinze is, it's getting rougher.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.324: I can hear the rumbling of thunder too... Are you okay?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.326: Right now... I can't hear it...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.328: Producer, are you working all this time?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.329: I appreciate your hard work... but you should take breaks too.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.330: Yeah, you're right. Thanks. I was just about to take a break.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.334: Ah, yeah. I just bumped into something. I've been sitting for too long, so my legs are a bit shaky...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.335: ────Be careful. If you only do desk work, your body will get stiff.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.336: Set a time to move your body... I got it!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.337: What about turning all the office chairs into balance balls!?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.338: T-That's a good idea... balance balls... I'll consider it... haha
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.339: The schedule is filling up quite far ahead... Natsuha, is everything okay with this?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.342: But if it seems too tough and overwhelming, please make sure to tell me, okay?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.343: Thank you. But really, there's no problem at all...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.344: On the contrary, I'm so excited about it.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.345: To think that I can feel how fulfilling the future is... Don't you feel the same way?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.346: ────Ah, yeah, I do. I'm looking forward to it too.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.347: Because I'll be able to watch Natsuha soaring higher and higher, closer than anyone else.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.348: ...Hehe. I'm really glad you're the producer, after all.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.349: Let's keep running together aiming for the top from now on!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.350: ────That's why, I'm sorry, but please keep that day clear on my schedule.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.351: Got it. I hope you have fun at the party.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.352: Hehe... Yeah, but there might not be much time for fun.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.353: Because there are many people my parents are indebted to, so it might end up just being greetings all around.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.354: Haha... I see. Being sociable is quite something.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.355: Thank you... But I think this is wonderful too.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.356: The connections between people, making everyone smile...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.357: I suddenly thought, this is what producers do every day, isn't it?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.358: Haha, mine isn't as flashy as that, though. It's nowhere near as splendid as Natsuha's dazzling figure.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.359: Is that so? To me, you shine brightly... Hehe.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.360: Oh, welcome back, Amana. Did something happen?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.361: Ah, n-no! It's not like it's a big deal or anything, but...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.362: On my way back from work, I found some delicious-looking pudding, so I bought some for you too, Producer-san.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.363: I see, thanks. I'm looking forward to it now.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.364: Ehehe... By the way, about how much longer do you think you'll be out...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.365: Let's see... there are still quite a few places to visit, so I won't be back for a while.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.367: ...Got it! Don't push yourself too hard...! I'll put the pudding in the fridge for you!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.368: Ah, I'll use that as motivation to do my best! Well then, see you later.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.370: Oh, Producer-san...! Sorry, it looks like I'll be back a little later than expected.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.371: ！ Are you okay? Did something happen?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.372: I'm sorry! I must have worried you... It's just... It's nothing serious...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.373: ...I forgot to bring an umbrella, so I'm taking shelter from the rain...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.374: I see... Well, that's good... No, it's not. Where are you?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.376: Got it, I'll come right away, so wait for me.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.377: Huh!? But Producer-san, you have a lot of plans today...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.378: Ah, but I have enough time to go pick you up, Amana, so don't worry too much about it.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.380: Oh, Amana. I thought you had the day off today, did something happen?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.382: I accidentally pressed the call button and tried to hang up right away, but it connected.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.383: So, um... I don't have any errands or anything...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.384: Haha, I see. It's okay, I was just taking it easy too.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.385: Is, is that so... Then... can we... talk for a bit...?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.388: Um... I was making pancakes for snacks earlier, and they turned out really well──
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.389: Producer-san... Can I ask you something?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.390: Yeah, what's up? We have a lesson coming up, right?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.392: Today's trainer... seems strict, so... I'm a little scared...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.394: B-but... If Producer-san... encourages me... I might be okay...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.395: Ah, I see...! If it's okay over the phone──
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.396: ──Then, Tenka, you can do it! I'm rooting for you, so go for it!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.399: Producer-san...! Next time... let's play games with Tenka...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.402: Producer-san... You always seem busy... so...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.403: Sometimes... it might be good to... play, right...?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.405: Thank you, that means a lot. But I do make sure to take breaks, so don't worry.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.406: ─But, since you mentioned it, why not? Let's play a game together for a change of pace!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.408: I'll lend you a controller too...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.420: I'm sorry... about the column I gave you today...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.421: After reading it again, I couldn't help but notice some small details bothering me...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.422: ─Could I have just one more day? Is that okay?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.423: Ah, no problem. The deadline is still ahead.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.424: I'm really sorry for being so selfish...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.426: If it's something you're putting under Chiyuki's name, then Chiyuki should be satisfied with it, right?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.428: If Chiyuki's motivated, she can make it even better. Take all the time you need.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.429: Thank you very much. I'll do my best to make it perfect.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.430: Producer-san, please try to reach out as far as you can!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.433: Hehe, how does that feel? Did it relieve some tension?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.434: Yeah, thanks. It feels much better around my neck. I was surprised since it was sudden.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.435: I'm sorry... I was just fooling around a bit.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.436: I thought you might be working hard again today, so...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.437: I wanted you to relax even just a little bit.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.438: Haha, thanks. I actually feel more relaxed now. It was perfect timing.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.439: Since we're at it, I'll brew some coffee and take a break.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.440: Hehe, then... would you like to join me for a coffee break from afar?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.441: Producer-san, did you try to contact me? I'm sorry I couldn't respond...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.442: Ah, I'm sorry for bothering you even though it's my day off. If you're busy, we can talk tomorrow instead.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.443: No, it's fine now. I was watching a movie, so my phone was off...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.444: No wonder I heard such cheerful voices. What movie did you watch?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.445: Yes, it was a really good movie. It was a revival screening of a classic, and...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.446: The lead actress's fashion and behavior were all so lovely...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.447: Oh, sorry... She was just so charming, I couldn't help but admire her...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.448: Haha, looks like you really liked it. Maybe Chiyuki will start hearing words like that too someday.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.450: Yeah. Chiyuki is already someone to look up to.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.452: Producer-san, I found an amazing building!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.453: The walls are cracked, and it's completely covered in ivy!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.454: Wow... really? Is it an abandoned house?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.455: I'm not sure. We need to check it out...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.456: Hey hey, even if it's abandoned, you can't just enter without permission, okay?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.458: Hmm... I wonder how the ivy looks from inside that house...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.459: By the way, I've been to a mansion covered in ivy for a shoot. Maybe we can see inside there too.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.460: Really? I want you to take me there!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.461: Okay, okay. Let's go together sometime.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.463: ... Asahi, is something wrong? You should be in school right now...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.464: ...? There's nothing wrong. It's break time right now.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.466: No no, if you don't have a reason, you shouldn't call. You're at school, after all.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.468: It's fine if you call after school. Come talk to me then.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.469: Got it. I'll prepare an interesting story by then!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.470: Hmm!? I wonder about that... I'll handle it, but...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.471: Ahaha! Well, talk to you later!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.472: Producer-san, where are you right now?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.473: Sorry! The meeting ran long...! I'm almost there, just finished the recording over there, I'll be there soon──
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.475: Asahi, what's wrong? I heard a loud noise, is something happening?──
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.476: Something's starting. Is it a street live performance? There's someone really flashy!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.477: Ah, Asahi! Did you go outside? You need to wait in the dressing room──
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.478: Wow... that's a loud sound. I wonder what song they're singing?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.479: Ahaha! I don't know, but it sounds fun!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.480: I'm curious! I'm going to check it out!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.481: Wait, Asahi! Tell me where you are──
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.484: Just a feeling. Your voice sounded a bit off.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.486: The studio earlier had strong air conditioning, so maybe my stomach got a bit cold.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.487: Got it. I'm in front of a convenience store, I'll buy something gentle for your stomach.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.488: You don't have to worry about that──
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.493: .... What's wrong, all of a sudden?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.494: Well... at the site earlier, you were spoken to in a pretty harsh manner, right?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.495: Haha, what? Did you think I'd be upset?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.499: But it's a fact that you were spoken to harshly. I just thought if Fuyuko was hurt even a little, then...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.501: If anything happens, give me a call. I'll listen anytime.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.503: ──Yeah, got it. If anything happens, I'll give you a ring.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.506: The outfit today suited you really well.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.507: .... I mentioned it earlier, didn't I?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.508: Yeah, you did... I just wanted to tell you again.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.509: When you say it like that, it seems like the usual Fuyuko isn't like that.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.510: Ah, no... that's not what I meant.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.513: Good work, Mei. Is it about work?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.514: Ah, nah, nothing like that~ Just wanted to chat with you a bit, Producer~
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.516: ! Could it be that you were busy!?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.519: So, today~ something really funny happened~
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.520: We decided to have lunch together~ and when we connected the tables~ and opened the lunch boxes~ guess what happened?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.521: Let's see... was it empty inside? Or something like that?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.522: Ahaha, that would've been crazy~ But no, it was different~ I accidentally took my little brother's instead of mine──
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.523: Hello? Producer? Are you free right now?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.525: Ahaha, can you tell? I found our poster at the station~
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.526: Oh, the promotional one we shot the other day? Mei liked it too, right? 'Turned out well,' she said.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.527: That's the one~! It was the first time I saw it hanging up, so I got really happy~
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.528: .... It's nice, isn't it~? Feels like a proof of our efforts, doesn't it?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.529: Haha, it's your effort, isn't it? I'm just lending a hand──
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.530: ──Nope~! It's our effort together, isn't it?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.531: .... Yeah. It's the culmination of both my and Mei's efforts.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.532: Alright! Passed~! So, let's go see it together next time~!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.533: Hello~ Producer? Are you feeling hungry~?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.534: Yeah... I could go for something to eat.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.535: Oh, really~? Then I'll buy yours too~ Chicken~
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.536: Fried or grilled, which one do you prefer~?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.537: Hmm... I'll go with fried, please.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.538: Okay, I'll also grab a good drink for you~ Ahaha, a mini cola~♪
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.539: ...! Sorry...! I am hungry, but I don't have time to eat slowly... There's still work to do...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.541: ...Sorry. I shouldn't have said something that dampens Mei's mood...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.542: ...Hmm... then! Tell me your schedule~! I'll make sure I'm free on the day you pick~♪
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.545: ...No. Toru has a day off today.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.548: ...Could it be about homework? I think you mentioned something like that yesterday.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.550: Haha, I can't remember everything, so make sure to jot it down next time.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.551: Aw, you should remember everything about me.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.554: It was pitch black when I woke up.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.555: ——Haha, were you taking a nap or something?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.558: Both my room and the city...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.560: Haha, then at that time, I must have been far away, also in the night.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.565: Ah... I probably saw that program too. It was a live broadcast from a pond covered with lotus flowers, right?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.567: Actually, they're not floating. They have stems underwater that support them...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.568: Did they explain it like that?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.570: But, yeah, that's how it is.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.573: Ah, Madoka...? I've sent the documents, so whenever you have time to─...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.574: Thank you very much. I've checked them, and there don't seem to be any issues.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.575: Oh... you've already checked? Thank you!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.577: Okay, since Madoka has confirmed it too, I'll just go ahead and send it to the other party!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.579: Well, even if there are typos, it won't be a problem for me.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.582: Huh, Madoka... Where are the typos... ah... they're cut off...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.583: The shoot from last week was well-received.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.585: It seems like the director quite likes Madoka. They said they'd like to hear more from you.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.587: ...Thanks to Madoka doing her job properly. Thank you always.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.589: Huh? Ah...! Sorry for calling you out of the blue like that.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.590: No, not at all. Then, goodbye.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.591: Please convey my thanks to the director.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.593: The sunset is beautiful. Can you see it from where you are, Madoka?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.594: ─I can't see it. I'm inside the studio.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.596: If there was a window, could you take a quick look? It's really a stunning sunset.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.603: Uh, thank you! We're heading to our lesson now...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.604: Got it. Is everyone going together?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.606: We were just at the family restaurant until a moment ago...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.607: If we leave now, we might end up cutting it close...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.608: Understood, thank you. Koito is really diligent.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.611: Hehe... Well then, please take care of us.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.613: Uh, um... Thank you for today!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.616: I just wanted to express my gratitude when I could.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.618: Isn't something to take for granted...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.621: No, I'm sorry...! I just felt Koito's seriousness.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.622: It's not something to take for granted, huh... Yeah, thank you.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.624: Hello, Producer? Hinana is feeling hungry~
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.625: Haha... After a rigorous lesson, huh?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.626: Yeah... I'll grab something sweet on my way back~
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.631: I appreciate the invitation, but I have urgent work to do.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.632: Ah~ Well, that can't be helped~ Hinana will go alone today~
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.633: Sure, invite me again. I'll make time and definitely go.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.636: Good job. It seems like it went well from your appearance.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.637: Yeah~! It was so much fun!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.638: It would have been nice if Producer could come too~
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.639: Yeah, sorry. Our schedules didn't match.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.640: But even without seeing it, I know. Hinana makes everyone happy.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.642: Even if I'm not there, I can tell about Hinana~?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.643: Haha, not exactly, more like imagining it. If Hinana is there, it's bound to happen, right?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.647: Ah...! Good work with the late-night lesson.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.649: ─Ah, Nichika, can I have a moment?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.654: ............ What's this all of a sudden?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.655: Yeah... Your voice sounded a bit down, so I thought I'd check in.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.656: ............ If you don't have anything else, I'll hang up.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.657: Hey, good job. What's up, Nichika?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.660: ────Melon pudding...! Have you already tried the one that came out the other day...?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.661: ......Huh? Ah... No, not yet, I guess.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.662: It's not melon at all, so it was surprising...! I wondered if the tasting sessions were really done properly...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.663: Is that so? I'll try it next time.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.665: ............Nichika... Did you... have something you wanted to talk about?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.667: ......Ughhh... I totally forgot what I was going to say...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.668: Producer-san, are you interested in concept cafes?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.670: You know, the costumes we saw the other day, they're not exactly sweet lolita, but that kind of style, right?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.671: I thought a concept cafe like that might be helpful for fashion and movement references.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.672: Ah, I see. If that's the case, I might be interested.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.673: Then, I'll make a reservation for two.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.675: Um, would you prefer a different place?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.677: Could you send me the link to the cafe later?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.678: I want to check out the interior, atmosphere, and also the prices...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.679: Sorry, I didn't notice the call. Did you need something?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.680: No, I was just curious about the self-practice. It seemed like you were really focused.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.682: That's good. Sorry for getting in the way.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.683: It's okay, you weren't a bother at all.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.684: I was thinking it's about time to wrap things up...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.687: ... Well, let's keep up the good work from tomorrow as well.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.690: The practice room still isn't available, so I had some waiting time.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.691: It's not like I had any particular reason to be here...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.693: Of course not. It's never a bother to hear from you, Mikoto.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.696: Wanting to call someone like this...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.697: Haha, isn't it fine? If you want, I can be your listener.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.699: Producer, can I talk to you for a moment? It's about today's performance...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.700: Huh? Oh, today is the day of that ballet performance, right?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.701: Yes. The tickets you gave me...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.702: I thought of it as part of my job and decided to come.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.703: I see. Then the theater must be the place now, right?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.704: Yeah... Was it okay? That I ended up with these tickets...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.705: Ah, it's fine. Originally, they were intended for someone in the office from a client.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.706: I thought you would absorb a lot from it, Mikoto.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.708: You won't miss a single thing.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.712: ... Do you have anything you want to discuss? Or any problems you're facing...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.714: I ain't got nothing like that.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.715: Even if I did, I wouldn't consult anyone about it...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.717: If you don't have business, I'm hanging up.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.718: Hey... I want to ask you to handle the photoshoot next month as well...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.721: Is this possibly an offer to extend the photoshoot?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.723: ─ Haha, I see! Thanks! It's all thanks to Luca's great work!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.725: I was sure this job would be perfect for Luca, so I'll ask the details from the other party!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.726: Luca, you did really well. Good job.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.730: Luca? I was just about to call you too.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.732: Thanks for checking it right away...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.733: The draft of the live report from the other day came in... Any dissatisfaction...?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.735: I... felt uneasy about the words used to introduce Luca, so I was planning to consult about that...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.737: If you understood, you should've said so from the start.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.738: Ah, sorry. That's why I was about to call Luca now...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.741: Hey, Hana. Good work. Did today's shoot go smoothly?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.743: I'm feeling tired, so I thought I'd call Producer-san to cheer me up.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.744: ... Hehe, that's why I'm happy that Producer-san picked up the phone.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.745: Haha...! If just a phone call can cheer you up, then that's great.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.746: Ahaha, then can I ask for one more favor?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.747: ... Can you praise me for doing a good job as a reward?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.749: Hana, you did a great job! Let's keep working hard together from tomorrow onwards. I'm counting on you...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.750: Hehe, thank you! Let's do our best at work starting from tomorrow too!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.754: ............ Um, so what was it you needed?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.755: Ah...! What I needed...? Ahaha, I wonder...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.756: I just wanted to hear Producer-san's voice and called without thinking about anything else.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.758: ... But if I keep talking for too long, I'll just be a bother to Producer-san... Should I hang up soon?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.759: Good luck with your work after this too. Bye-bye.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.762: Ahaha, in that case, are you in the mood for something sweet right now?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.763: Something sweet...? Yeah, I'd be happy to have some, but...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.765: I got a cake as a gift at today's shoot, but it looks like I can't finish it alone, so I was thinking of taking it to the office...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.766: Oh...! Sorry for the trouble. Thanks a lot.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.768: Well then, see you later. Bye-bye.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.769: ... Ah, it's already this late... Sorry for taking up so much of your time...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.771: No, no, it's okay. It hasn't been that long, has it?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.773: But I really appreciate it. Listening to your stories like this...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.774: Talking to Producer-san helps me organize my thoughts...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.775: I get ideas of things I want to do, and my motivation increases.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.776: Haha, that's nice. But it's not my power, it's Haruki's inherent strength.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.778: It's still thanks to Producer-san. You help shape what's inside me...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.779: Hehe, please keep listening to me like this?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.780: Producer-san is good at work and kind... It's amazing, isn't it?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.782: Hehe~ Nothing at all. I always think that.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.783: Haha... That's nice to hear, but... I still have a long way to go.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.784: I make mistakes, I hesitate, and so on.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.785: I see... But it's because of those things, too, that you are who you are now, Producer-san.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.786: Thanks to that, I've been helped a lot...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.787: Someday... I hope I can become strong enough to help Producer-san too.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.789: Hehe... It seems like there's still a long way to go, but I hope such a future exists.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.791: Hey, good work. Haruki, did something good happen?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.792: Hehe, do you understand? I actually received a stuffed animal as a gift.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.793: Oh...! Is that so? What kind of stuffed animal is it?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.794: It's a sheep. They said it looks like me.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.795: It's very fluffy and cute...! I wonder if I'm like that...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.796: Haha, I'd love to see it.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.797: Then I'll bring it next time...! Let's have Producer-san give it a name.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.798: It looks like Haruki, right? Then maybe you'll want to call it 'Haruki'.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.799: Hehehe... That's true~ But please don't call it anything other than 'Haruki-chan'.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.800: Tomorrow's photoshoot is quite early... Are you okay with that?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.802: I-I wake up early and do some preparation...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.803: I'll set up a backup alarm too...! S-so, it'll be fine...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.804: Don't push yourself too hard. Oh, right... If you need, I can do a wake-up call for you...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.805: I can't let you go that far to help me out...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.806: I-I'll manage to wake up on my own! Because it's work...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.807: ...I see, understood. Then, rest early today and prepare for tomorrow.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.808: Y-yes...! A-and, Producer-san, please don't overwork yourself...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.809: Haha, sure. Thanks. I'll make sure not to oversleep either.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.810: Hey, Producer-san, did you see the photo I sent earlier~?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.811: Yeah, it's about the hairstyle, right? You did a great job with the hairpin.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.812: Today, I went with a single bun and tried various hairpins~. Cute, right~?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.813: Did you do it yourself? It was neatly done.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.814: I watched some videos and managed to do it~ There were various styles, it was fun♡
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.815: I see. Hinana, you're good at hair arrangements too.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.816: Aww I'm flattered~! I'm going to paint my nails to match the hairpins~
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.817: I'll send you a photo after I'm done painting~ Is it okay to post it on Twesta~?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.818: Yeah, it's fine. ...Hinana is really diligent in her studies. I'm impressed.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.819: Hehe~ Hinana is just doing what she likes~
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.820: ...I see. That's right. Looking forward to the photos.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.822: Producer-sama... There's something... I'd like to ask...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.824:
Well...──
Do you have... any wishes...?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.825: If it's alright with you... Rinze would... like to make a wish... in your place...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.826: A wish, huh... I do have one, of course...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.827: But instead of a god, I'd like Rinze to fulfill it herself.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.829: Yeah, because I want Rinze to continue to shine more and more as an idol from now on.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.831: Yes... Rinze will definitely make it happen...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.832: Hello, Producer? Sorry, I couldn't answer your call earlier...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.833: No, I'm the one who called suddenly, sorry about that. It's not anything important...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.834: Remember when we went to the shrine the other day? I just passed by it earlier...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.835: Ah... So you remembered me and called, huh?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.836: That's right. So, I didn't really have any real reason for calling.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.837: That's disappointing... I was hoping you might invite me for tea or something...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.838: Huh? Oh... Well, want to go for tea then? Since we have time until the next job...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.839: Oh my, that's a bland way to ask. Is that your line when inviting a lady?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.840: Ah, sorry...! That's right... Um... If you're okay with it, would you accompany me for tea?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.841: I wanted to have a leisurely chat with Sakuya about the upcoming work and other things...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.842: Hehe, about work, huh... That's like you, Producer. Then, shall I escort you again?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.843: Hey hey, isn't the party you're invited to in the evening?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.844: Yeah. It seems they'll provide dress rentals and makeup too.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.845: What about Meguru? Should I ask for both?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.846: I want both~! I'm not sure what would be good...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.847: I'll ask for everything from top to bottom! Doing makeup myself is 100 times better!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.849: Ah, you thought it was exaggerated? I'm really not that good at it, you know?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.850: Since it's an invitation, I have to go looking nice!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.852: Right, right? I'm going as Meguru Hachimiya from 283 Production, after all.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.853: I'll make sure to be perfectly prepared!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.854: I have to check the one we shot the other day. I'm going to the office now.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.855: Thanks. I'm looking at it now, and it looks really good.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.856: Oh... I see. I can't wait to see it.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.857: Oh, you'll be surprised. It's captured both cool and cute really well.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.859: I tried to make the costumes look cool, but... Combining that with cute... It's impossible, right?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.860: That's not true. Being able to combine those is what makes Juri amazing.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.861: Hmm... My body feels restless for some reason.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.862: Well... I'm happy to be myself, though.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.868: It's the snow rabbit Producer-san made for Yuika!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.870: You made it next to Yuika-chan's snow rabbit, right? So we don't feel lonely.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.872: You're welcome... um... is it okay to call it my snow rabbit...?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.873: Yeah, it's okay! What is it?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.874: Thanks for calling. Your feelings make me happy.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.878: Haha, continuing from the previous job?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.879: Yes! Is there anything troubling you?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.881: Yeah, I tidied up the desk earlier, but I feel like there's still something I can do.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.882: If it's okay with you, could I get your opinion next time?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.884: I'll definitely meet your expectations! Please leave it to me, Amana!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.885: Thank you, I'm counting on you.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.887: The music program we appeared on the other day seems to have received positive feedback from viewers.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.888: Thanks to Luca's hard work, it led to good results...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.891: Ah, ah... Sorry, was that unnecessary?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.892: But I wanted to make sure Luca's efforts were appreciated.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.893: Keep up the good work for the next job too...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.899: Um... well... The cherry blossoms... are blooming...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.900: Producer-san... I'm looking forward to the cherry blossoms...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.901: Haha... yeah, I was looking forward to it. That's great news.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.906: Ah. I'm nearby too. Can I come over now?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.911: Are you okay? Take your time, tell me what's going on.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.912: Tenka wants to go back to the place she went with Producer-san... But she got lost...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.913: Okay, I'll come right away. Is there anything distinctive nearby?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.914: Um, well... there's a narrow road... and there's a big tree beside it...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.915: Alright, try to stay where there are people around. If you see something distinctive from there, let me know.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.917: Producer-san! Good job! I saw the outfit!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.918: Oh, you're fast! I just sent the reference materials earlier.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.921: There are so many colors, it looks powerful! The candy cane looks like something a hero would have!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.922: Ah...! It really does look like a magic wand, doesn't it?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.923: Yes! It feels like you could do anything once you wave it!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.924: I can't wait to try it on!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.926: With Kaho singing and dancing with the candy cane, it'll be fun to watch.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.927: I'll cast a candy magic spell on Producer-san!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.928: Good job! The recording went smoothly without any problems.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.929: Ah, good work. Heading back to the office now, right?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.931: Um... I got marshmallows again... Do you want some?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.932: I appreciate the thought, but isn't that something Nichika got?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.933: I already ate mine, so I'm fine. I'm also keeping track of my calories.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.934: I see, that's too bad. I wanted to see Nichika's face while eating marshmallows.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.935: It might be better to just stop... saying things like that.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.937: It's a good thing we're talking on the phone. If you were in front of me, I might have punched you.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.938: Haha... Nichika isn't one to sugarcoat things.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.941: This might be sudden, but can you list things that you think are 'Yuika-like'?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.943: It's for a magazine survey ♡ Just for reference!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.944: Hmm...? I'd prefer if you come up with that on your own──
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.945: I won't use it directly! It's just for reference! I want to know what kind of image comes to mind.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.952: It's for a Street Snap's Private. There's nothing that fits the theme.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.953: I'd like to go shopping. Do you have any convenient days?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.955: Let me check mine and Haruki's schedule. Just wait a moment.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.957: Sorry for keeping you waiting. Tomorrow works fine──
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.958: Yes, thank you. Sorry to bother you while you're shopping.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.961: Oh...! Producer-san... You picked up quickly...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.962: ...? Oh, did you call because you had something to say?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.963: Uh, yeah, but... It's nothing too important, I guess...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.964: Well, since you picked up so quickly, I was surprised.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.965: Haha. Well, since you called, why don't you tell me anything you want?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.966: Yeah... I was so surprised that I forgot what I wanted to talk about.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.967: I see... Now I'm curious about what it was.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.968: Hmm, it was something that crossed my mind during today's lesson... What was it...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.969: ──In that case, tell me about the lesson. Talking about it might help you remember.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.971: Hey, Producer, can I ask you something?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.973: I've been thinking since I wore that costume with the piano motif the other day...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.974: For the next costume, I was thinking something a little more classical...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.975: Ah, I'll consult with the costume designer about that... Did Mikoto develop an interest in classical music?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.977: ...I just felt like I could bring out a more nostalgic side of myself.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.978: Using memories to enhance the present, huh? That's very much like you, Mikoto.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.979: I bet you were a hard worker even back then.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.981: I'd like to hear some of your past stories too, Producer. Like if you were a hard worker... or something else.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.982: Hey, Producer? I saw the design for the next costume.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.983: Oh, I see. What did you think?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.984: Hmm, I'm not sure... but how do you think I'll look in that costume, Producer?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.985: How you'll look... That's a tough question...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.989: Huh...! I didn't hear anything about a time limit!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.991: If it's difficult to answer right away, it's okay. You can tell me when you actually wear it!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.992: I'm looking forward to hearing your thoughts, Producer!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.993: Producer-san, good work. I've finished work for today and I'm heading home now.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.994: Good job, Mano. Thanks for the report... Did something good happen? You sound happy.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.995: Uh... well... yes... There was something that made me happy...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.996: Since Twesta shared the image cut we took at the park...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.997: We received a lot of feedback from fans.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.998: Among them, there was someone who knew about the prince's picture book illustrations...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.999: Ah, the picture book Mano used to read...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.1000: Yes... They said it resembled a picture book I used to love...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.1001: ...Thinking that someone among the fans loved the same book as me...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.1002: It made me really happy... My heart feels warm...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.1003: Hey, Producer? Are you free tomorrow night?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.1004: Huh, tomorrow night? Yeah, I am... What's up?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.1006: They're supposed to be shooting tomorrow.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.1007: Ah... it's probably a meteor shower, right?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.1008: Yeah, I've never seen one before, so I want to see lots of shooting stars.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.1009: Got it. Let's go see them together.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.1010: Yeah... I wonder if we'll see them properly...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.1011: I'm not sure... But I remember the forecast said it would be clear tomorrow.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.1012: I see. Then we should be fine.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.1013: They'll probably be crystal clear in the sky.

mlPhoneText_PhoneCallTitle.17: Even though it was a mistake
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallTitle.19: The person who gave me sweets
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallTitle.44: I want to know inside that
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallTitle.48: Even if it's an invisible wound
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallTitle.49: It's okay to have it happen again and again
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallTitle.73: Right now, that's all I want
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallTitle.75: The power to make it take shape
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallTitle.95: Even if it's not right away

mlProduce_TutorialText.1: You can conduct lessons while displaying tutorials. Would you like to display the tutorial?
mlProduce_TutorialText.2: Swipe up to use Producer Cards.
mlProduce_TutorialText.4: Operate until the game is cleared.
mlProduce_TutorialText.5: Swipe left to use Idol Skills.
mlProduce_TutorialText.7: Use Sparkle Sunshine to reduce the required PP for the next card.
mlProduce_TutorialText.9: Use consecutively the cards whose required PP has decreased.
mlProduce_TutorialText.10: Use Visual Appeal Preparation to enhance the next card.
mlProduce_TutorialText.12: When Me is below 30%, enter a pinch state.
mlProduce_TutorialText.13: Use Melody of Burning Life to decrease Me.
mlProduce_TutorialText.14: Use Resounding Melody of Immortality in a pinch state.
mlProduce_TutorialText.17: Use Hidden in the Sea to increase evasion rate.
mlProduce_TutorialText.18: Evasion probability is displayed at the top of the Mental Gauge.
mlProduce_TutorialText.19: Use Singing Voice Harmonizing with the Sea, coordinated with evasion.
mlProduce_TutorialText.20: Use Dancing with the Ripples, coordinated with evasion.
mlProduce_TutorialText.21: Evasion buffs are activated in coordination with evasion.
mlProduce_TutorialText.22: At 80% or more Me, enter a safe state and increase acquired Appeal Points.
mlProduce_TutorialText.23: In a safe state, take 20% damage when acquiring Appeal Points.
mlProduce_TutorialText.24: Use Sound of Tranquility in a safe state.
mlProduce_TutorialText.25: At 100% Me, maintain a safe state once despite receiving demerits.
mlProduce_TutorialText.26: Use Dancing with Happiness in a safe state.
mlProduce_TutorialText.27: Recover Me after demerits to transition back to a safe state.
mlProduce_TutorialText.28: Currently in Nichika Phase. Use Change to Sky to change to Mikoto Phase.
mlProduce_TutorialText.29: Since it's now Mikoto Phase, the Double Cards have been changed to Mikoto.
mlProduce_TutorialText.30: Use Change Rank-Up Boost with Straddle Go Up.
mlProduce_TutorialText.31: Use Change to Sky to perform a phase change.
mlProduce_TutorialText.32: Use double radiance after ranking up.
mlProduce_TutorialText.33: Use Dilemma's Lie to Banish cards from your hand.
mlProduce_TutorialText.34: The effect will activate when the last song is sung.
mlProduce_TutorialText.35: Try banishing cards with Dilemma's Lie.
mlProduce_TutorialText.36: The effect of the last song has been activated after exclusion.
mlProduce_TutorialText.37: banishing cards will increase the number of banished cards.
mlProduce_TutorialText.38: The number of banished cards increases when cards are removed.
mlProduce_TutorialText.39: Using cards and skills, acquire corresponding system counters.
mlProduce_TutorialText.40: Using Vocal Preparation of the Vo system increased the Vo counter by 1.
mlProduce_TutorialText.41: There are cards that grant effects to acquire system counters.
mlProduce_TutorialText.42: Use Illusion VOICE with an additional effect of 'liberation'.
mlProduce_TutorialText.43: Use 'liberated (consumed)' Vo counter to increase additional Appeal Points.
mlProduce_TutorialText.44: Use Happiness Rhythm with a yellow effect indicating that the conditions are met.
mlProduce_TutorialText.45: Use Combination Rhythm to search for cards.
mlProduce_TutorialText.47: Use the Searched Powerful Rhythm to increase the maximum hand size.
mlProduce_TutorialText.49: Use Begin at the End to return banished cards to the deck.
mlProduce_TutorialText.50: Since cards have been returned to the deck, the number of banished cards has decreased.
mlProduce_TutorialText.51: Tap Producer Card to confirm its effect.
mlProduce_TutorialText.52: Producer Cards glowing green can be used.
mlProduce_TutorialText.53: Current status of the displayed effect can be checked. Tap to display the effect explanation.
mlProduce_TutorialText.54: Tap anywhere other than the icon to make the display disappear.
mlProduce_TutorialText.55: Tap anywhere other than the icon to make the display disappear.
mlProduce_TutorialText.61: Would you like to proceed with the production tutorial?

level of the selected episode has not been cleared.

mlProduceKeyword_Description.1: Reduce Me by the value of Mental Guard Reduce the value of Mental Guard by the number of Me reduced (when Me is reduced by the effect of a card used by the player, it cannot be reduced by Mental Guard).
mlProduceKeyword_Description.2: 【Exclusive to L'antica】 Me less than 30% of Max Me
mlProduceKeyword_Description.3: When evasion occurs, the evasion effect disappears and the probability is reset.
mlProduceKeyword_Description.4: The effect is triggered once when evasion occurs.
mlProduceKeyword_Description.5: 【Exclusive to ALSTROEMERIA】 If the unit's Me is 80% or more, Appeal is increased by 10%; if the unit's Me is 90% or more, Appeal is increased by 20% instead; if the unit's Me is 100% or more, Appeal is increased by 40%; if Appeal is increased while the unit is safe, 20% of its Me value is damaged When Appeal is increased in safe state, 20% of Me value is damaged.
mlProduceKeyword_Description.6: Activate the effect when there are more than a certain number of card lines (this card itself is also included in the effect activation conditions).
mlProduceKeyword_Description.7: Add the specified card from the deck to your hand (If the specified card does not exist in the deck, draw a card regardless of the effect)
mlProduceKeyword_Description.8: The specified lineage is added to the card. (When a card with the lineage added is used, the effect is lost. The same lineage cannot be granted)
mlProduceKeyword_Description.9: During Lesson /Special Lesson /Audition, the effect will continue to work.
mlProduceKeyword_Description.10: Additional effects that take effect by consuming a specified number of lineage counters. When there are effects that consume multiple counters of the same lineage, the effect that consumes the most counters takes priority.
mlProduceKeyword_Description.11: Add a card with the same name as the target card to your hand or deck (The rank of the card added by this effect becomes the same as the rank of the duplicated card.)
mlProduceKeyword_Description.12: Removed from the Deck during the game and cannot be added to the hand by drawing cards.
mlProduceKeyword_Description.13: 【Exclusive to SHHis】 If in Nichika Phase, switches to Mikoto Phase / If in Mikoto Phase, switches to Nichika Phase
mlProduceKeyword_Description.14: 【Exclusive to SHHis】 Each time the Phase changes, the rank of the card in hand is increased by one (using a card whose rank is increased by this effect eliminates the change rank boost effect of all cards. It rises to rank 3)
mlProduceKeyword_Description.15: Cards that switch available effects depending on Phase
mlProduceKeyword_Description.16: Effect of reducing your unit's Me by Produce Card or Idol Skill used by you.
mlProduceKeyword_Description.17: Each time a card with a lineage is used, a counter for that lineage is gained (up to 99 counters can be accumulated for each lineage)
mlProduceKeyword_Description.18: PP becomes 0 and cards cannot be used for a certain period of time / The number of seconds of mental break state becomes longer according to the number of mental breaks (Recover from mental break after a certain period of time and return with 50% of Me).
mlProduceKeyword_Description.19: 【Exclusive to CoMETIK】 Increases the number of removed cards by a specified number (the number of removed cards increased by this effect is not decreased)
mlProduceKeyword_Description.20: When the bundle of cards you use is less than the Max number of cards in your hand, the cards after use are added to the Deck, except for the removed cards that are subtracted from the Deck.

mlProduceKeyword_Name.19: Boost in number of cards removed

mlSpecialMission_Empty.1: It will be unlocked when {0} is cleared.

mlSpecialMission_Hint.1: Choose your favorite song and difficulty level from the Live's song selection. Any format of live performance will be counted as a live performance, including normal live performance, auto live performance, skip live performance, and manual play.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.2: Select one of the units from the Produce Episode selection and press the [Decide] button to start producing. Select a Lesson from the Schedule selection, and win the mini-game in the Lesson.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.3: Pull one Gacha of your choice. Consume a Gacha Ticket or Prism Jewel.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.4: P. Choose a P-idol from the Idol Training screen and raise its Awakening Lv. Awakening Book and Money are required. The required items can be obtained through live performances and producing.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.5: Select the S-character you wish to train from the Support Character building screen and train to increase the Support Characters Lv. Training tickets and Money are required. The required items can be acquired through live performances and productions.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.6: The number of remaining Skip Lives will be reset at midnight every day.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.7: You can start the auto-live by turning on the auto-live function in the unit confirmation after selecting a song. Auto Live is not recorded as a live performance, but you will be rewarded as ALL PERFECT. The number of remaining auto lives will be reset at 0:00 every day.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.8:
After selecting a song, press the LB consumption setting button in the unit confirmation to set the number of LB consumption x 2 or more to start the live performance.

The number of drawings for live rewards after the end of the event will increase according to the number of LBs consumed. Also, the number of plays will be counted together according to the number of LBs consumed.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.9:
After selecting a song, select one of the Idol members in the unit confirmation to change members.

You can also change the composition by clicking on the [Optional Formation] button on the unit checklist.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.10: Select one of the units from the Produce Episode selection screen and press the [Decide] button to start producing. Select an Audition that will be held in the last week of the month from the schedule selection screen, and win the mini-game in the Audition.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.11: Select one of the units from the Produce Episode selection screen, press the [Decide] button to start producing, and play to the end.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.12: Select one of the units from the Produce Episode selection screen, press the [Decide] button, select an Idol from the Produce Select Idol screen, select an Idol other than the one currently displayed as [Establishment], and press the [Decide] button in the lower right corner of the screen to organize the Idol. Press the decision button in the lower right corner of the screen to organize the unit.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.13: Exchange any item from the exchange. The items to be exchanged differ depending on the tab. Mainly, Money, Rainbow Rocks, Star Shards, and Season Medals are consumed.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.14: Select [Search Friends] from the [Friends] screen, select any friend and press the [Follow] button.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.15: Set the Birthday from Producer Information profile screen.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.16: Select the Friend Support Characters icon from Producer Information profile screen and set up any Friend Support Characters.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.17: From Producer Information profile screen, click on the Comments column and edit any comment you wish.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.18: Click the [Favorite Idol] button on the lower left of Producer Information profile screen, select the desired Produce Idol, and click the [Change] button.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.19: From Producer Information profile screen, click on the [Unset] column for the title, select any title, and change it.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.20: Select illumination STARS from the main tab of the story, then select Chapter 1 to read the story.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.21: Press the Idol tab of the story and select any Idol, then select Chapter 1 to read the story.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.22: Press the third icon from the upper right corner of the home screen, select the Idol you have set up, and then select any Idol from the Idol settings. The selected Idol will appear in front of the left side of the desk.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.23:
Stage's costumes can be changed from the's costume icon in the's costume tab of the live unit selection screen.

Stage's costume cannot be changed for P-idol before producing. F-Idol after produce can be changed in unit setup.

mlStore_ItemCaveat.9:
・Even if you have purchased a Season Pass, you will not be able to receive the Premium Rewards for any Season Rank that you have not yet achieved.
・Season Pass can be purchased until 23:59 11/28/2023, but the Season Pass effect will last until 23:59 11/30/2023.
・The Season Pass effect will be inherited even if the model is changed to another OS.
・The Season Pass effect is inherited when playing multi-session play with other devices.
・Season Pass is not available for payment at shop from the time of purchase until the payment is completed.
・Season Pass cannot be returned or exchanged at any time.
mlStore_ItemCaveat.10:
・This product may be purchased up to one time.
・Private can be worn in the story and on the home screen. It cannot be set as a Stage's costume and cannot be worn in a live performance.
・If you already own any of the's costumes, hairstyles or accessories included in this product, you will not be able to acquire those's costumes, hairstyles or accessories.
・【Costume 02】 Juri Saijo may be obtained at a later date at a different location. Please understand this in advance.
mlStore_ItemCaveat.11:
・Login Bonus Pass holders will receive 100 Prism Jewels once a day when they log in to the game.
・The opportunity to receive Prism Jewel is reset at 0:00 every day.
・If you have logged in for 25 days or more within 30 days of purchasing your Login Bonus Pass, you will receive a total of 2500 Prism Jewels.
・If you have not logged in for less than 24 days within 30 days of purchasing your Login Bonus Pass, you will lose the Prism Jewel you have not received.
・Prism Jewel will be sent to your Gift Box.
・If you change your device to another operating system, your Login Bonus Pass will be transferred to the new device.
・Login Bonus Pass will be inherited even when playing multi-session play with other devices.
・Prism Jewel obtained by Login Bonus Pass is free Prism Jewel. The free Prism Jewel cannot be used for the paid Prism Jewel service.
・The Login Bonus Pass will not be effective until the payment is completed after the purchase of the product.
・Login Bonus Pass cannot be returned or exchanged at any time.
