mlTips_Description.1: Enjoy the story and develop your Idol while strengthening your status and Produce Cards, and aim to pass the Auditions.
mlTips_Description.2: They are used in Lessons and Auditions. Collect Produce Cards that have various effects to give your idols an advantage.
mlTips_Description.3: By selecting a Produce Policy, the selected effect will be applied during the Season.
mlTips_Description.4: Depending on each schedule, you can increase your status and obtain Produce Cards. Stamina is consumed depending on the type of schedule.
mlTips_Description.5: The goal is to maximize Appeal Points within the time limit by making full use of Produce Cards.
mlTips_Description.6: The goal is to maximize Appeal Points before your Rival does within the time limit. By surpassing the time limit, you can advance to the next Season.
mlTips_Description.7: Tap the heart mark on the song jacket to register/unregister Favorite songs. Registering frequently played songs makes it easier to find songs.
mlTips_Description.8: By playing various songs, [Overall High Score Rate] and [Overall Technical Rate] will increase and rate frames and rewards will be earned.
mlTips_Description.9: This is the total High Score Rate of the top 20 songs recorded by manual play, and you can aim for a new High Score by increasing the Total Stats.
mlTips_Description.10: This is the average of the Technical Rate of the top 20 scores recorded in manual play. Technical score is calculated based on the judgment result only.
mlTips_Description.11: When there's a song that cannot be cleared, try to form units with Life Recovery or Invincibility and fans boosting skills when you want to increase fans.
mlTips_Description.12: Once you complete a produce run and acquire Fes Idols, you will get one Live Skill. P.idols who have not yet produced will not acquire any Live Skill.
mlTips_Description.13: Idols marked [CENTER] and [ONSTAGE] will appear on the stage. When multiple Idols of the same name are organized, other Idols will appear randomly.
mlTips_Description.14: When organized as the center of a live unit, the Live Skill can be activated up to twice, doubling the EXP gained and the No. of fans after the live performance.
mlTips_Description.15: If you set-up Idols with the same type mark as the song, the unit bonus will be added and the Total Stats will be increased. You can check the bonus in the Unit Set-up screen.
mlTips_Description.16: Each P-idol has a unique's costume. By training to 3★, Stage's costume will be unlocked, and the's costumes can be changed during live performances.
mlTips_Description.17: Money can be used to exchange items used for awakening and training at the exchange.
mlTips_Description.18: Expired exchange points become Star Shards. You can exchange Star Shards for other items at the exchange.
mlTips_Description.19: An item used for Idol Skill LvUp of Produce Idol.
mlTips_Description.20: The item used to awaken the Produce Idol. There are common awakening books and individual awakening books for each unit.
mlTips_Description.21: You can exchange Rainbow Rocks for pieces at the exchange.
mlTips_Description.22: Items that can be used to Recover ST (Stamina).
mlTips_Description.23: Items that can be used to Recover LB (Live Boost).
mlTips_Description.24: Items that can be acquired at various points in the game and may be used in gachas, stores, ST Recovery, LB Recovery, etc.
mlTips_Description.25: Items used for special training of Produce Idol and master training of Support Characters.
mlTips_Description.26: Items used for training of Support Characters.
mlTips_Description.27: The Season Mission is held for a certain period of time, and you can play the Season Mission and earn rewards for completing the Season Mission.
mlTips_Description.28: This is where you can exchange one item for another. You can exchange Money, Star Shards, Rainbow Rocks, Season Medals, etc. for another item.
mlTips_Description.29: You can change settings for the entire application from the menu in the upper right corner of the home screen.

mlTitle_ConsentModule.21:
The Service collects information necessary to analyze the provision of the Service and to improve its functions.

We ask for your consent to link and combine this information with other services and products of BNE and BNE's affiliates and with information provided by Chapter 3.

Types of data collected: online identifiers (including ad IDs and IP addresses), usage of this service (including play data and billing amounts), and registration information for this service (including name, address, telephone number, age, and e-mail address).

You may withdraw your consent at any time by accessing the settings screen within the Service.

mlTitle_DataTransfer.52:
To link data, you will need a Bandai Namco ID that is already Account Linked. Please be sure to read the following notes before linking data.

<sprite=3><color=#ff3300>Disclaimer</color>
・Only one Account can be linked to one Bandai Namco ID.<line-height=66%>
</line-height>
・Selecting[data linkage]will link the saved data you are using with the data in your DMM Account you are currently logged in to.<line-height=66%>
</line-height>
・Selecting[Data Linkage] will not result in the loss of saved data on your device or platform.<line-height=66%>
</line-height>
・When data linkage is performed, it is not possible to link to other DMM Accounts.<line-height=66%>
</line-height>
・Paid Prism Jewels cannot be linked to different platforms. They can only be used on the platform where they were purchased.<line-height=66%>
</line-height>
・Free prismatic jewels can be linked to different platforms.<line-height=66%>
</line-height>
・Login Bonus Pass and Season Pass effects can also be linked to different platforms. Achievement and earning status will also be linked.

From [Data Linkage] you will be redirected to a screen where you can log in to your Bandai Namco ID. Once you have logged in, the data linkage is complete.

By linking your account to your Bandai Namco ID, you can link the data associated with your account when you lose your device or change to a new device.
Do you want to do an Account Link?

<sprite=3><color=#ff3300>Disclaimer</color>
・Only one account can be linked to a single Bandai Namco ID. If you wish to link another account to your Bandai Namco ID, you will need to cancel the Account Link. Once linked, it cannot be unlinked for 30 days.<line-height=66%>
</line-height>
・Paid Prism Jewels cannot be linked to different platforms. They can only be used on the platform where they were purchased.<line-height=66%>
</line-height>
・Free prismatic jewels can be linked to different platforms。<line-height=66%>
</line-height>
・Login Bonus Pass and Season Pass can also be linked to different platforms. Achievement and earning status will also be linked.

Click 'Linkage' to go to the screen for logging in to your Bandai Namco ID. Account Link is completed when you log in to your Bandai Namco ID. If you have not created a Bandai Namco ID, please go to 'New Registration'.

mlVoiceResource_Text.200002: I hope I can bring you all the brilliance...
mlVoiceResource_Text.200005: ....i-it went by so fast, but it was fun
mlVoiceResource_Text.200006: Wow...everyone is smiling, I'm so happy...
mlVoiceResource_Text.200007: It looks like the practice paid off...
mlVoiceResource_Text.200008: It's all thanks to you Producer...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200009: I can't believe I could make such a Stage...
mlVoiceResource_Text.200011: I will do my best now
mlVoiceResource_Text.200013: Sorry, i'll be sure next time...
mlVoiceResource_Text.200014: Not yet. We can do much better....
mlVoiceResource_Text.200015: I think we were able to improve on the results of our practice.
mlVoiceResource_Text.200016: This is the best I've ever done...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200017: It's all because of you producer, thank you
mlVoiceResource_Text.200018: I was happy to be on the Stage...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200019: Okay, I'll give it my all!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200020: I'm having a great time, Producer!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200022: Let's think about the next thing after reflecting!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200023: Let's make sure the next one is even more enjoyable...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200025: Ehehe... I had a lot of fun too!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200029: I won't take my eyes off you!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200031: We won't be discouraged by setbacks!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200032: It seems like we can still aim higher!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200035: Ehehe~, this is the extent of our abilities!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200036: I... I'm so happy I could burst...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200039: Please keep an eye on us!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200043: It was quite exciting, wasn't it?
mlVoiceResource_Text.200049: I will definitely use this experience as nourishment.
mlVoiceResource_Text.200050: We still have... further heights to aim for, don't we?
mlVoiceResource_Text.200053: It seems like we delivered a good performance.
mlVoiceResource_Text.200055: Expect great things from Mitsumine's activities!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200060: Oh dear, it seems like I got serious.
mlVoiceResource_Text.200061: Was it thanks to Producer's support?
mlVoiceResource_Text.200063: Yeah, it's so... happy it's scary.
mlVoiceResource_Text.200066: Because I'm... part of L'Antica too...
mlVoiceResource_Text.200067: Next time, it will definitely be okay...
mlVoiceResource_Text.200068: It seems like we're progressing little by little...
mlVoiceResource_Text.200070: It feels like... I've caught the sound...
mlVoiceResource_Text.200075: Houkura always ends with a climax!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200079: I didn't make a single mistake!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200080: It means I'm getting stronger, right!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200081: It's incredibly, incredibly, incredibly amazing, isn't it!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200082: I promise to make it special, the best time!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200083: Please take the best memories home with you!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200084: Let's go all out from start to finish!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200085: Can we identify areas for improvement together...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.200086: I'll keep doing my best, Producer-san!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200087: It was fun...! It was so exciting!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200090: It seems like it's going to be an unforgettable live...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200092: Let's hype it up to the max!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200094: Yeah, let's move on to the next!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200096: Thank you, it's all thanks to you!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200099: Wow, I can't believe it. Seriously...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200103: We still have a long way to go...
mlVoiceResource_Text.200104: Did we live up to your expectations...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.200105: The cheers of everyone resonate in my heart...
mlVoiceResource_Text.200106: Fufu... it's the result of training...
mlVoiceResource_Text.200113: We still have a long way to go!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200114: The result of our daily efforts!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200115: It was a stage I'm satisfied with!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200116: It seems like we've created a stage that satisfies everyone!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200119: Let's make it the best stage ever☆
mlVoiceResource_Text.200120: Let's deliver happiness together as three!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200122: It felt quite good, didn't it?
mlVoiceResource_Text.200130: Ah... no, it didn't go well...
mlVoiceResource_Text.200131: Tenka... did I do it properly...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.200138: Let's make the flowers of smiles bloom!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200143: I... somehow feel warm in my chest...
mlVoiceResource_Text.200144: I'm glad I didn't give up on anything...
mlVoiceResource_Text.200145: The beginning of a fun time!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200149: I want to try more things!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200151: Eh~ I don't want it to end yet~
mlVoiceResource_Text.200152: I was able to do everything I wanted to!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200153: Amazing...! So this is what being an idol is like~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200154: I'll make you even more captivated, Producer
mlVoiceResource_Text.200156: Fuyu and I won't lose to anyone
mlVoiceResource_Text.200157: ...I'm going to cool my head for a bit
mlVoiceResource_Text.200158: Fuyu's impression is that we could have done more. How about you?
mlVoiceResource_Text.200159: ...The audience seemed really pleased, didn't they?
mlVoiceResource_Text.200160: This is the ideal, isn't it?
mlVoiceResource_Text.200162: How was it? Fuyu's perfect form
mlVoiceResource_Text.200167: It feels quite good, doesn't it?
mlVoiceResource_Text.200168: Phew, that was a great live!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200171: I feel like I can do anything now!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200172: I'll be back after it's over
mlVoiceResource_Text.200176: Was I able to do it? Not really?
mlVoiceResource_Text.200177: I did it, right? Quite well
mlVoiceResource_Text.200180: Did you see it? It was sparkling
mlVoiceResource_Text.200185: I'll do my best, in my own way
mlVoiceResource_Text.200187: For some reason, it's like this
mlVoiceResource_Text.200189: I don't get it... it's funny
mlVoiceResource_Text.200196: I was able to produce results...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200199: Ahaha~ I'm looking forward to it~
mlVoiceResource_Text.200201: I feel like I can do it~
mlVoiceResource_Text.200205: I had so much fun, Hinana♡
mlVoiceResource_Text.200208: I just did what I could
mlVoiceResource_Text.200209: I can do it, I can do it, I can do it...
mlVoiceResource_Text.200213: If I don't do this much...
mlVoiceResource_Text.200215: I did it... I did it!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200218: Let's make sure it's a success
mlVoiceResource_Text.200221: ...I need to make it more perfect
mlVoiceResource_Text.200223: I think it went really well
mlVoiceResource_Text.200224: I think I was able to produce good results
mlVoiceResource_Text.200228: Let's make it the best stage. Can't we do it?
mlVoiceResource_Text.200229: Can't end it like this, right...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.200231: I've been waiting for this kind of thing~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200232: We have to do it like this, right...?!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200240: Producer, will you praise me a lot?
mlVoiceResource_Text.200242: It was really good, wasn't it...?!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200243: I don't want to forget this feeling──!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200247: I feel like I can do more next time...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200251: Hehe...! I did it as I wanted!
mlVoiceResource_Text.200252: It feels like the world I see has changed...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.300005: I still have to do my best...
mlVoiceResource_Text.300010: Let's do our best next time too
mlVoiceResource_Text.300012: We were able to grow a little
mlVoiceResource_Text.300016: I want to keep doing my best like this
mlVoiceResource_Text.300023: Phew... I might be a little tired...
mlVoiceResource_Text.300024: What should I do next time...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.300029: Thank you for the break... I'll spend some quiet time with P-chan.
mlVoiceResource_Text.300030: Um... I'm sorry for taking up your time. Thank you, Producer.
mlVoiceResource_Text.300031: I somehow managed to make it this far...
mlVoiceResource_Text.300032: Next time, I'll work even harder!
mlVoiceResource_Text.300033: I still need to work hard in my lessons...
mlVoiceResource_Text.300034: Step by step, let's keep moving forward...
mlVoiceResource_Text.300035: I feel like I'm gradually growing.
mlVoiceResource_Text.300036: I want to keep working hard together from now on.
mlVoiceResource_Text.300037: As an idol, I've gained a little confidence.
mlVoiceResource_Text.300038: I want to deliver even more radiance to our fans!
mlVoiceResource_Text.300039: Hehe... I've been feeling really good lately...
mlVoiceResource_Text.300040: It's because you've been watching over me, Producer.
mlVoiceResource_Text.300041: Ah... my heart feels so full...
mlVoiceResource_Text.300045: Should we do a little more before ending?
mlVoiceResource_Text.300046: Let's not let our guard down and keep going...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.300048: I should still be able to catch up...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.300050: I fell short of my full potential...
mlVoiceResource_Text.300051: I don't think that last attempt was bad.
mlVoiceResource_Text.300052: Yeah. Let's pay more attention to the details next time.
mlVoiceResource_Text.300053: It feels like it's starting to take shape, right?
mlVoiceResource_Text.300054: Yeah, let's keep up this momentum.
mlVoiceResource_Text.300056: With this, we can aim even higher.
mlVoiceResource_Text.300057: I think I managed to overcome the challenges.
mlVoiceResource_Text.300059: I was able to fully demonstrate the results of my lessons.
mlVoiceResource_Text.300060: I'm glad I could produce good results.
mlVoiceResource_Text.300061: There are still many challenges ahead...
mlVoiceResource_Text.300064: I won't make the same mistake twice.
mlVoiceResource_Text.300065: I might have underestimated my physical Stamina...
mlVoiceResource_Text.300066: Producer, could you tell me about the next schedule?
mlVoiceResource_Text.300071: Having a whole day free... makes it hard to decide what to do, doesn't it?
mlVoiceResource_Text.300072: I'm sorry for taking up your time... I couldn't think of anything else...
mlVoiceResource_Text.300073: There are still many things I lack...
mlVoiceResource_Text.300074: First, I'll firmly retrain the basics.
mlVoiceResource_Text.300075: I want to think of more things I can do.
mlVoiceResource_Text.300076: I need to overcome the things I can't do...
mlVoiceResource_Text.300077: I feel like I'm finally getting the hang of the basics.
mlVoiceResource_Text.300078: From here on, I'll need even more effort.
mlVoiceResource_Text.300079: I feel like I can see some possibilities now.
mlVoiceResource_Text.300080: I feel like I'm actually growing.
mlVoiceResource_Text.300081: I'm glad I could achieve results I'm not embarrassed about.
mlVoiceResource_Text.300082: But I still feel like I can aim higher.
mlVoiceResource_Text.300083: I think I gave it my all with what I could do now.
mlVoiceResource_Text.300084: I made it this far thanks to you, Producer.
mlVoiceResource_Text.300087: Should I think a bit more?
mlVoiceResource_Text.300090: A pinch is a chance, right?
mlVoiceResource_Text.300093: I feel like I nailed it!
mlVoiceResource_Text.300094: See! Things seem to be going smoothly!
mlVoiceResource_Text.300096: Yeah yeah! It's the result of our hard work together!
mlVoiceResource_Text.300098: Yeah! With you, I feel like we can do anything!
mlVoiceResource_Text.300099: I feel like I've got the hang of it!
mlVoiceResource_Text.300100: Hehe, we've grown a lot in one go, haven't we?
mlVoiceResource_Text.300102: I'm glad we've been working hard together!
mlVoiceResource_Text.300104: Let's think about what went wrong!
mlVoiceResource_Text.300105: Sorry, I guess I messed up...
mlVoiceResource_Text.300106: Alright! Let's do our best for the next one!
mlVoiceResource_Text.300107: I'm sorry... I might be a bit worn out.
mlVoiceResource_Text.300108: Hey hey Producer! What's the next plan?
mlVoiceResource_Text.300113:
What should I do~?
Is it better to just go all out and have fun? What do you think?
mlVoiceResource_Text.300114:
Are you listening to me? Thank you!
Well then, please take care of me...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.300116: I want to stretch myself further!
mlVoiceResource_Text.300117: I want to increase the things I can do even more.
mlVoiceResource_Text.300118: Then, I'll be able to do the things I want to do.
mlVoiceResource_Text.300119: I feel like a real idol now!
mlVoiceResource_Text.300120: Let's aim to remove the 'like an idol' part next time!
mlVoiceResource_Text.300121: I feel like we're moving forward!
mlVoiceResource_Text.300124: I feel like we can go even further!
mlVoiceResource_Text.300125: I still don't feel it very much...
mlVoiceResource_Text.300126: Thank you so much for everything, Producer!
mlVoiceResource_Text.300132: I don't want to give up...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.300135: I feel like I did well!
mlVoiceResource_Text.300138: I feel like I've got the hang of it!
mlVoiceResource_Text.300140: With this, let's shine even more~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.300146: I'll have to start over and do my best again!
mlVoiceResource_Text.300147: Aw man... that didn't go well...
mlVoiceResource_Text.300149: Hmm... I need to get back into it and do my best...
mlVoiceResource_Text.300155:
Sometimes it's important to take it easy~
I'll rest well and do my best later!
mlVoiceResource_Text.300156:

mlVoiceResource_Text.301113: I'll do my best next time...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.301116: Producer, what are we doing next?
mlVoiceResource_Text.301121: Huh, a break? Thanks. Ahaha, what should I do now?
mlVoiceResource_Text.301122: Hehe, thank you~ I've been wanting to talk for a while.
mlVoiceResource_Text.301126: How about aiming for even higher?
mlVoiceResource_Text.301129: There's still more we can do, right?
mlVoiceResource_Text.301130: If we're together, we can still do our best.
mlVoiceResource_Text.301134: ...This is also thanks to Producer, you know?
mlVoiceResource_Text.301144: Let's keep going with this feeling!
mlVoiceResource_Text.301150: With us, it feels like we can go anywhere~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.301151: We did it~! Thanks to everyone
mlVoiceResource_Text.301154: Let's straighten our backs and try again~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.301155: We didn't make it, did we...
mlVoiceResource_Text.301157: ...Ah, I'm sorry... I was spacing out.
mlVoiceResource_Text.301158: I'm looking forward to what we'll do next!〜
mlVoiceResource_Text.301163: Is it okay if I take a break? There are so many things I want to do...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.301164: Thank you very much! Ah, where should I start... I'd like to take up a lot of your time, if that's okay...
mlVoiceResource_Text.301166: I want to do better next time.
mlVoiceResource_Text.301168: We need to fix any shortcomings!
mlVoiceResource_Text.301170: I'd be happy if you praised me~
mlVoiceResource_Text.301171: Hmm, I wonder if it's getting better~
mlVoiceResource_Text.301172: I want to aim even higher...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.301176: Sniff... thank you very much... It was a job well done!
mlVoiceResource_Text.400001: I'm starting to feel a bit more confident!
mlVoiceResource_Text.400002: We still have a long way to go.
mlVoiceResource_Text.400004: Taking a step forward towards our dreams!
mlVoiceResource_Text.400005: Hehe, with this, I might get praised~
mlVoiceResource_Text.400006: We need to keep polishing our performance at this pace.
mlVoiceResource_Text.400007: Mitsumine is greedy, so we're still not there yet.
mlVoiceResource_Text.400008: Hehe... I managed to do it properly.
mlVoiceResource_Text.400009: I feel like I've gotten a bit stronger!
mlVoiceResource_Text.400010: Today is a reward for me!
mlVoiceResource_Text.400011: Alright! I feel a sense of accomplishment!
mlVoiceResource_Text.400012: Hehe... I can see it now...
mlVoiceResource_Text.400013: It feels good. I'll keep going like this!
mlVoiceResource_Text.400015: I think I did my best...
mlVoiceResource_Text.400017: Alright! Next time, let's go even further~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.400018: This much is probably fine for now.
mlVoiceResource_Text.400020: Looks like I can go a bit further.
mlVoiceResource_Text.400022: Well, I still have a long way to go~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.400025: Hmm... Yeah, I managed it today too.
mlVoiceResource_Text.400026: Hmm... I feel like I'm getting better, right?
mlVoiceResource_Text.400027: From now on, I feel like I can show a different side of myself.
mlVoiceResource_Text.400028: I feel like I have become more free...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.500002: I can see the challenges ahead...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.500005: Now that I've gotten better, maybe I should slack off next time
mlVoiceResource_Text.500006: Of course, I still intend to keep growing
mlVoiceResource_Text.500008: I wonder if I did well in the lesson...
mlVoiceResource_Text.500010: The chocolate after the lesson is exceptional...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.500011: Practice is important for everything, right?
mlVoiceResource_Text.500013: The daily efforts shape the person you'll be tomorrow
mlVoiceResource_Text.500015: I'll do my best in the lessons, too!
mlVoiceResource_Text.500016: Hehe, looks like I can still keep going
mlVoiceResource_Text.500017: Hmm, something feels off. I wonder why...
mlVoiceResource_Text.500018: There's still a long way to go...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.500025: Every day, striving for perfection... the same way
mlVoiceResource_Text.500026: I feel like I'm making progress... Ahaha
mlVoiceResource_Text.500027: It would be great if I could keep going like this, right?
mlVoiceResource_Text.500028: I feel like I'm gaining strength...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.500029: Hehe, it seems like I'm improving~♪
mlVoiceResource_Text.600002: I feel like I can fly even higher...
mlVoiceResource_Text.600004: I guess I've reached a passing grade...
mlVoiceResource_Text.600006: I want to shine even more...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.600008: I feel like I can do anything right now~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.600009: It's not like I worked hard or anything...
mlVoiceResource_Text.600010: Should I be happy? Well, it can't be helped~
mlVoiceResource_Text.600011: Hehe. How do I look to you now?
mlVoiceResource_Text.600012: I feel so proud to have come this far
mlVoiceResource_Text.600013: I'll keep working hard like this!
mlVoiceResource_Text.600014: Hey hey, wanna say I did a good job?
mlVoiceResource_Text.600015: I managed to wrap the bandages well...
mlVoiceResource_Text.600016: It's alright... so please, watch me...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.600018: I might have gotten really strong!
mlVoiceResource_Text.600019: I did it! A little bit of growth!
mlVoiceResource_Text.600021: Am I starting to look more like an idol?
mlVoiceResource_Text.600022: I feel like I'm steadily making progress step by step
mlVoiceResource_Text.600026: It feels amazing... but this is just the starting point!
mlVoiceResource_Text.600027: I'll keep going~! Please keep watching me, Producer~☆
mlVoiceResource_Text.600028: I feel like I'm shining so brightly right now!
mlVoiceResource_Text.600029: I tried my best... Am I amazing...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.600030: Hehe... being an idol is fun... maybe...
mlVoiceResource_Text.600031: What do you think? Am I doing well?
mlVoiceResource_Text.600032: Wow, I feel like I'm not even myself!
mlVoiceResource_Text.600035: This is just a milestone for me
mlVoiceResource_Text.600036: Hehe, well, I did my best, right?
mlVoiceResource_Text.600038: Wow... right now, I'm feeling really amazing!
mlVoiceResource_Text.600039: Am I getting closer? To the top
mlVoiceResource_Text.600047: I can't afford not to be able to do this much...
mlVoiceResource_Text.600048: I can't stay still. Not at this point
mlVoiceResource_Text.600049: I want to pay attention to the details more
mlVoiceResource_Text.600050: Because I want to give a perfect performance
mlVoiceResource_Text.600051: Ahaha! I feel like I can do even more now...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.600054: I'll keep working harder, so please keep watching, okay?
mlVoiceResource_Text.600055: I feel like I can see more things expanding before me
mlVoiceResource_Text.600056: I want to see even further ahead...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.700001: What might the idols be like?
mlVoiceResource_Text.700002: Let's watch over the idols' growth together~
mlVoiceResource_Text.700003: Let's get ready with the idols~
mlVoiceResource_Text.700004: Do you have something for me~?
mlVoiceResource_Text.700005: Let's take a look back at past activities~
mlVoiceResource_Text.700006: Happy birthday!♪ Don't forget to visit the idols too~
mlVoiceResource_Text.700007: Um... On sunny days, I like to bask in the sun at the park...
mlVoiceResource_Text.700008: On my way to the office, I saw a big bird called an Onaga... Its tail feathers were so impressive...
mlVoiceResource_Text.700009: My lucky item is... a star-shaped charm~! Oh, no... It's based on a fortune telling result, so it's a bit...
mlVoiceResource_Text.700010: Are you eating properly? Make sure you have a main dish, side dish, and soup... It's important to be mindful of your daily diet~
mlVoiceResource_Text.700011: Producer! Hehe, I'll do my best, so please teach me lots of things~?
mlVoiceResource_Text.700012: I love moving my body! Basketball, volleyball... Oh, and I really, really love dancing too~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.700013: I ain't clumsy at all! Just 'cause I trip or forget things don't mean I ain't the strongest, perfect idol!
mlVoiceResource_Text.700014: If you're hungry, count on me~! My cooking is Japanese... No, it's the most delicious in the galaxy~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.700015: If I play a prank, please scold me properly, okay~? ...Well, I won't stop, though.
mlVoiceResource_Text.700016: Won't you tell me what Producer dislikes~? Hehe, just for reference~
mlVoiceResource_Text.700017: I love interacting with people. Meeting someone and having a conversation makes me feel like the world is expanding.
mlVoiceResource_Text.700018: I want to know all about you. Because I'm someone who's interested in you, that's me.
mlVoiceResource_Text.700019: I was born on January 16th── You already knew that? Hehe, I figured you would, right?
mlVoiceResource_Text.700020: I'm the type who falls for Producer... or rather, scouting! Haha!
mlVoiceResource_Text.700021: Um... hehe... Nice to meet you... I look forward to working with you...
mlVoiceResource_Text.700022: Hehe... Please... tell me... lots of... stories...
mlVoiceResource_Text.700023: Kaho Komiya, sixth grader! People often ask, 'Are you in high school?' I'm still in elementary school!
mlVoiceResource_Text.700024: I want to be an idol who can make everyone smile like a hero!
mlVoiceResource_Text.700025: I have to work hard as a chocolate idol...! I check out new products every day too!
mlVoiceResource_Text.700026: I had a good breakfast this morning! Breakfast is the source of energy...! Alright, let's do our best today~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.700027: I don't mind moving my body. Actually, I might feel uneasy if I don't do anything.
mlVoiceResource_Text.700028: Am I... kind...? Ahaha, I don't really know myself, but it doesn't feel bad to be called that.
mlVoiceResource_Text.700030: I'm still... halfway... Please... guide me...
mlVoiceResource_Text.700031: I aim for the top in everything! Because having high goals makes it more challenging, right?
mlVoiceResource_Text.700032: If you're going to produce me, please always give it your all! I'll respond with all my might too!
mlVoiceResource_Text.700033: Tenka-chan is~ Amana's beloved big sister! She's always cute, and I'm so proud of her~
mlVoiceResource_Text.700034: Amana~ loves talking about fashion☆ How about you, Producer-san?
mlVoiceResource_Text.700035: Na-chan is Tenka's little sister... She's always so kind and energetic... Tenka loves her... a lot~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.700036: I don't have any special skills... But I like playing games... and I also like taking naps~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.700037: I like making small things and sewing. If a button comes off or something, please let me know, okay?
mlVoiceResource_Text.700038: I took the plunge... So I'll work hard to become a wonderful idol!
mlVoiceResource_Text.700039: I'm not good at sitting still. If you don't need me for anything, shall we go outside?
mlVoiceResource_Text.700040: I like dancing! I come up with a lot of ideas like 'Let's do this' and 'Let's do that'!
mlVoiceResource_Text.700041: I want to become an idol that everyone recognizes. Then I can proudly say, 'This is Fuyu'!
mlVoiceResource_Text.700042: They're noisy, sometimes incomprehensible, and don't listen to a word I say── They're such a hassle, really.
mlVoiceResource_Text.700043: You say it's easy to understand what I'm thinking? Ah, I get that a lot~
mlVoiceResource_Text.700044: Ahaha, I may look like this, but I'm confident in my handwriting! I used to practice calligraphy, you know~
mlVoiceResource_Text.700045: Fwaa... Uh... Ugh... I'm... sleepy... Mostly...
mlVoiceResource_Text.700046: Ah... I... forgot something... Diary... Going home...
mlVoiceResource_Text.700047: Don't mind me... It's easier that way, isn't it? For both of us.
mlVoiceResource_Text.700048: Serious, sincere, heartfelt... You're truly an exceptional person. I definitely don't want to become like that.
mlVoiceResource_Text.700049: Well, I'm good at studying... But this is just average, okay?
mlVoiceResource_Text.700050: Uh, um... Teo-chan, Enka-chan, and Hinana-chan are childhood friends!
mlVoiceResource_Text.700051: Hmm... What does Hinana like? There are so many things~
mlVoiceResource_Text.700052: Hinana can do anything reasonably well! Is that considered a special skill~?
mlVoiceResource_Text.700053: Making fun of shop clerks who know a lot about idols? Moi? Absolutely not~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.700054: Huh, calling me Nana-san? I refer to my sister as...! This isn't home, you know~?
mlVoiceResource_Text.700055: I wonder what I'm good at... Probably singing and dancing. Other than that, I'm nothing special.
mlVoiceResource_Text.700056: I want to be an idol. The kind of idol I envision... I want to become that.
mlVoiceResource_Text.700057: Lipstick? Is it a problem if it's red? Hey, what are you staring at?
mlVoiceResource_Text.700058: Everyone's always in the way... Ugh... So annoying...
mlVoiceResource_Text.700059: The kanji for 'wings' contains the character for 'feathers', right? That's why I thought it might be destiny, hehe~
mlVoiceResource_Text.700060: The one who first approached me was Producer, and I'm really glad about that, you know?
mlVoiceResource_Text.700061: I might not be good at just sitting still. I want to try everything!
mlVoiceResource_Text.700062: I have so many hobbies and things I like... I don't even know where to start...
mlVoiceResource_Text.700063: Producer-san, good job today... Are you going to take a break now...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.700064: Are you taking a break too, Producer? I was just thinking of taking a break... I'll go get some drinks.
mlVoiceResource_Text.700065: Are you tired, Producer...? ...I know! Let's take a break for a bit!
mlVoiceResource_Text.700066: Are you taking a break too, Producer? Then let's have a snack together. I need to eat something because I'm hungry!
mlVoiceResource_Text.700067: Producer, you seem bored... Do you want to hear an interesting story?
mlVoiceResource_Text.700068: Oh, Producer... Planning a break? Excellent! Shall I prepare some drinks?
mlVoiceResource_Text.700069: I recommend taking a break to you, busy big brother over there~ Sometimes, it's better to relax!
mlVoiceResource_Text.700071: Heroes don't always fight! Let's take a break together!
mlVoiceResource_Text.700072: Oh, Producer-san... How about taking a little break? Ah... Let's take a short break!
mlVoiceResource_Text.700073: Hey, come over here for a bit... Wanna take a break and relax a bit?
mlVoiceResource_Text.700074: Um... Please wait... I'm not ready... to meet... yet...
mlVoiceResource_Text.700075: You seem a bit tired, Producer. Maybe you should take a short break. Taking a break is a legitimate job too, you know.
mlVoiceResource_Text.700076: Producer-san... Here! Have some coffee~ Hehe, let's take a little break, shall we?
mlVoiceResource_Text.700077: Producer-san... Would you like to take a break with me...? I could take a break alone too...
mlVoiceResource_Text.700078: Producer-san, if you'd like, you can use this cushion. It's handmade by me.
mlVoiceResource_Text.700079: Hmm...! You look like something interesting happened. I want to know too!
mlVoiceResource_Text.700080: If you're tired, how about taking a little break? ...What? Are you rejecting Fuyu's invitation?
mlVoiceResource_Text.700081: Oh! Producer, welcome back~! Wanna chat for a bit~?
mlVoiceResource_Text.700083: What? If you don't need anything, can you not talk to me?
mlVoiceResource_Text.700084: Ah, um, welcome... Producer-san...! Um, what's the matter...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.700085: Ahaha~ Producer, do you have something you want to talk to Hinana about~?
mlVoiceResource_Text.700086: Ugh, bed hair... Can you stop pretending to be busy? Can I help you?
mlVoiceResource_Text.700087: Do you have something to talk about? I'll listen, but... I have a bit of time now.
mlVoiceResource_Text.700088: Taking a break, huh... It's fine, isn't it? Well... It doesn't matter to me.
mlVoiceResource_Text.700089: Producer, sometimes you need to take a good break, you know?
mlVoiceResource_Text.700090: Producer-san, is it okay if I stay here? Just being with you makes me feel calm.
mlVoiceResource_Text.800001:
Producer-san,
here is today's login bonus~
mlVoiceResource_Text.800002: You can receive this tomorrow, so please look forward to it~
mlVoiceResource_Text.800003:
Producer-san,
here's today's login bonus for you~
mlVoiceResource_Text.800004:
I've prepared
a special login bonus for you~
mlVoiceResource_Text.800005: Today's login bonus is something special~
mlVoiceResource_Text.800009:
Let's do our best
and not be defeated by the heat~
mlVoiceResource_Text.800010:
It's hot every day,
isn't it? Let's take care of our health~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900001: Good morning! I'll do my best today too!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900002: Good job! Would you like to take a break together?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900003: Next time, I'm planning to have a sleepover with Hiori-chan and Meguru-chan.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900004: Did you hear the sound of birds just now...? They came to play, maybe?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900005: Talking with you always cheers me up...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900007: S-sorry... I got a little too relaxed...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900008: ...The sun is warm and it's perfect weather for a stroll...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900009: ...Since it's nice weather, eating outside seems pleasant...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900010: ...The sky looks like a pigeon... fluffy clouds look like pigeons curling up...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900011: ...The sound of rain is somehow calming...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900013: ...It's heavy rain... I wonder if the doves are able to take shelter...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900014: Wow... it's snowing... Can I go make a 'snow Pea-chan' later?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900015: ...Cherry blossom viewing and picnics... The warm spring weather makes me want to go out a lot...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900016: ...The wagtails were sucking nectar from the flowers... hehe... they were cute...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900019: ...The trees on the mountains have turned beautifully colored... Autumn is a fun season for walking too.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900020: Next time, the three of us are going hiking to see the autumn leaves! I'm really looking forward to it...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900021: ...I like taking walks even in the cold, silent winter air...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900022: ...It's a bit cold today, so the sparrows are all puffed up...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900023: I went to the shrine for the New Year with my family... I'll do my best with a fresh feeling this year too.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900026: I'm going to see the Christmas illuminations with Hiori-chan and Meguru-chan... hehe
mlVoiceResource_Text.900027: ...I found chocolates shaped like cute owls... um... I hope they taste good...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900028: ...T-thank you very much... I'll treasure it...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900031: ...When I was little, I used to pick Hina-arare for Pii-chan...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900034: Thank you for everything this year... I'll also work hard on cleaning the office...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900035: Wow... Thank you so much! I'll continue to do my best so you'll see me as having grown.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900036: Today is Hiori-chan's birthday, so I thought I'd bake some icing cookies for the celebration...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900038: Happy birthday! I hope you have a wonderful year ahead, Producer.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900039: Good morning, Producer! Let's have a great day today too!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900040: Good job! How are you feeling? No particular problems?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900041: Producer, can I ask you about our lesson?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900042: Are you hungry? Um... I made too much lunch, so...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900043: Another coffee? Be careful not to have too much, or you won't be able to sleep.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900045: If you relax too much, you'll be left behind.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900046: Nice weather, isn't it? The laundry will dry well too.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900047: Can I open the window? The wind seems nice.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900048: The forecast said it would be cloudy, but... just in case, I brought a folding umbrella.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900049: Producer, your shoulder is a little wet. Shall I get a towel?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900050: The sound of rain seems to calm the mood, contrary to the weather... It makes me want to listen closely.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900051: The rain is intense, isn't it? I hope it doesn't affect our schedule...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900052: So white... Sometimes, this kind of thing isn't so bad, I think.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900053: When I go for a walk with Mano, she teaches me a lot about birds and wildflowers.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900054: I want to build up my strength now for summer that's coming.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900057: Can we include idol activities in 'Art Autumn'? It'd be nice, right...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900058: It's the perfect season for a trip, isn't it? Since it's 'Autumn of Appetite', even researching is fun.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900059: Meguru often sticks close to me because she's cold... but she seems to be having fun.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900060: I tend to make hotpot dishes because they're easy... but I've made a variety already... Any suggestions?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900061: They say 'The plan for the year is made on New Year's Day', so I want to work hard with a fresh feeling.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900064: It was tough choosing within the budget for the gift exchange, but it was fun.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900065: I think I've already received a lot, but... Here, some chocolates for you.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900066: This is from a famous place, right? It seems to be more than triple the usual... but thank you...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900069: Hina-arare is something you only eat this time of year... but it tastes nostalgic.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900072: Are you able to finish up your work? It'd be nice to relax during the New Year's holidays...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900073: ...You remembered... Um... Thank you very much... I'm happy to be celebrated.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900074: I made a cake with a bird motif for Mano's birthday. I hope she'll be pleased with it.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900076: Is today your birthday...? Um, I chose this myself, so please... Congratulations.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900077: Good morning, Producer! Let's give it our all today too!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900078: Producer, are you tired? If it's tough, let me know...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900079: Wow, a treat!? Hehe, let's play rock-paper-scissors to decide who picks first!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900080: Ah, a chain! Um... my friend said they watched that show the other day...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900081: Why that face? Sometimes you need to move your body to refresh!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900082: Hey hey, Producer! Do you have time right now? Let's chat!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900083: Producer, are you awake...? Are you tired?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900084: Today's weather is really nice! I feel energized and ready to go!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900085: Mano and I went to the park! Sunbathing there makes my heart and body feel warm!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900086: The weather forecast says it's going to be cloudy! Not too hot or cold, just right!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900087: It's raining today, so I'll change my plans for jogging and do some stretching and muscle training instead!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900088: I forgot my umbrella! So I came here sharing an umbrella with Mano and Hiori!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900089: Hey hey, do you have any plans to go out later? Since it's raining heavily, I'm worried...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900090: Snow always gets me excited! I want to play in the snow!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900091: Spring is the season of encounters, so I'm excited! I wonder if I'll make new friends!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900092: Since it's warm, I talked with the two of them about going on a picnic! Would you like to join us?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900095: I'm definitely all for 'Autumn of Sports'! ...I thought, but I also want to eat delicious food!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900096: Since we have the chance, I want to try some new sports or something!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900097: It's cold, isn't it? Maybe I'll make some hot milk. Do you want some too, Producer?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900098: It's cold, huh? When I tried to huddle with Tōri, she said 'Oh, come on...'!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900099: Every year, I try my best to stay awake for the New Year's countdown! I quickly run out of energy though!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900102: Illuminations are special after all, right...? The reason is... pretty obvious, huh!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900103: Happy Valentine's Day! Thank you, Producer, as always!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900104: Being able to give and receive gifts is really nice. It makes me happy and excited!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900107: I think calling Hina Matsuri 'Peach Festival' is really cute! It has a fluffy image!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900110: Meguru, work has finished! Let's do our best next year too! though we'll see each other right away, hehe.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900112: Mano? Yeah, I already congratulated her directly! I went to see her first!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900113: Congrats! When I gave a hug, I received one back! That's supposed to be my line!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900114: Hiori, I'll sing with all my heart! ...Happy birthday to you♪
mlVoiceResource_Text.900115: Howdy, Producer! I'm in great spirits today too, y'all!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900116: Now, don't you go pushin' yourself too hard, okay? Takin' a proper rest is mighty important for work!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900117: Feelin' hungry? If y'all are, I'll whip somethin' up real quick!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900118: Ehehe~ Leave everythin' to me, darlin'!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900119: Nfufu It's lively and fun when everyone's 'round, ain't it~?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900120: Hey there, Producer, are you sleepin' properly? Your eyes look mighty tired...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900121: Well, howdy there, Producer! Nfufu~ I just wanted to see if y'all would respond~!!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900122: Hmm~! The weather's mighty nice, ain't it? Feelin' refreshed, so I reckon I can do my best today too!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900123: It's nice and warm out, so I went and aired out the futon. Lookin' forward to tonight~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900124: I wonder if it's gonna rain later~? ...Producer, are y'all carryin' your umbrella properly?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900125: It's been rainin' all day today... To avoid slippin' and fallin', we need to be mighty careful...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900126: Feh... Forgot to bring in the laundry... Oops...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900127: The rain is really intense...!! The wind is strong too, so our umbrellas might get blown away...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900128: Hey, Producer, look outside! It's snowin'!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900129: Did y'all go cherry blossom viewin'? Since I'm makin' delicious bento, do y'all wanna make plans?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900130: Warm weather feels mighty nice~, but make sure not to fall asleep accidentally!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900133: This time of year, there's a heap of delicious foods, so it's right fun to plan the menu!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900134: I seen a flyer for grape pickin'! I wanna go with everyone~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900135: It's gettin' right cold~! Producer, make sure to dress warmly too, y'hear?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900136: On chilly days, let's warm up our bellies with some hot champon!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900137: I went to the shrine for New Year's and drew a fortune! I kept drawin' until I got the best one, so my fortune for this year should be perfect!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900140: From my house... Thank y'all always... But, not just that...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900141: Feh, a return gift...!? Thank y'all, Producer, I'm right happy...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900142: It makes me remember... I made hina dolls outta origami and displayed 'em at my family's restaurant...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900145: Thanks for everything this year~! Countin' on y'all next year too! Of course, I'll do my best too~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900148: Thank y'all for all your help this year, I look forward to workin' with y'all again next year! Of course, I'll take care of y'all too!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900149: Y'all remembered, huh...! Nfufu~ Bein' celebrated makes today a right great day!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900152: I thought about what Kaho likes a lot~, so I chose carefully! I'd be happy if she likes it~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900154: Today's a special day, right? I'll grant any wish y'all have, Producer!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900155: Good morning~ Let's take it easy today too, okay~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900156: Good job~ Well then, time for a break~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900157: Hmm, still haven't noticed? Try to guess what I did~ Please figure it out quickly~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900158: Feeling a bit bored~ Oh, could you make a funny face for me~?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900159: I'm a naughty girl~ You better keep an eye on me~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900160: Producer, are you slacking off perhaps~? I'm working hard, you know~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900161: Hey~ ...Oh, are you waiting for me to play a prank~?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900162: Hmm, it's such nice weather~ ...So, maybe I'll take a nap~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900163: ...Are you the type of person who feels energized when it's sunny~?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900164: Is it going to rain~? ...If it does, how about we cancel lessons for the day~?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900165: I tried out a styling gel that can withstand the rain~ Hmm, looks good~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900166: Rainy weather... so gloomy~ ...So, today's activities as Tanaka Mirei have concluded~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900167: Wow, this rain is intense... I might catch a cold~ Can I go home, please~?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900168: Huh, snow~...? I thought it felt chilly... Looks like I won't be able to move much today~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900169: Spring makes everyone seem so lively, doesn't it~? As for me... Hmm, I'm feeling sleepy~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900170: Huh, flower petals in my hair...? ...Ah, don't trick me with jokes like that-- ...Oh, they were actually there~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900173: Um, there's talk about having a bonfire or something at the office~ ...Oh, and they're talking about having a sweet potato grilling contest at L'Antica...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900174: Not too hot, not too cold~ I want it to stay like this forever~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900175: It's so cold that the commute takes twice as long as usual~...That's why I hate winter~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900176: When I move in the cold, I end up falling into a thousand-year sleep~ It's because of the curse of Demon King.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900181: I want some delicious chocolate~ Right? Hehe~ Producer, are you looking forward to it?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900182: ......Umm, thank you~ ......Ah, umm~ Got some sweets~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900185: Since it's Hinamatsuri, sometimes wearing a traditional Japanese outfit might be nice~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900188: Thanks for all your hard work this year~ You've worked so hard, so I'm looking forward to my reward~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900190: Everything feels so lively and exciting today, doesn't it? Hehe~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900192: Mitsumine seems like she has everything... so it's hard to choose a present for her~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900194: ......That present might have something weird jump out of it~ So be careful, okay?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900195: Good morning, Producer Let's do our best today
mlVoiceResource_Text.900196: Good job, How are you feeling? You're not pushing yourself too hard, are you?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900197: Oh, your tie is crooked Hehe, it seems even you relax sometimes
mlVoiceResource_Text.900198: Hehe... Oh, sorry I just remembered something funny
mlVoiceResource_Text.900199: I wonder what you think about me as an idol, Producer?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900200: What are you obsessed with right now? Oh, I feel a bit envious
mlVoiceResource_Text.900201: I hope you'll start looking at me soon, Producer
mlVoiceResource_Text.900202: The weather is so nice Hehe, it seems like we might have a wonderful encounter today
mlVoiceResource_Text.900203: Invited by the cheerful sky── I feel like going out into the city
mlVoiceResource_Text.900204: Whether I'll cry or not... Only the gods know
mlVoiceResource_Text.900205: With the gentle sound of rain as BGM── Now, how shall we spend our time?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900206: I wonder if there'll be a rainbow after this rain? I'd be very happy if I could see it with you
mlVoiceResource_Text.900207: With this rain, there's no time to even gaze at the umbrella... I hope it clears up soon
mlVoiceResource_Text.900208: The snow dancing is so beautiful And── I wonder if it'll accumulate I'm a bit anxious
mlVoiceResource_Text.900209: Spring is generally considered the season of encounters── But I want that in summer, autumn, and winter too
mlVoiceResource_Text.900210: The roads and streets are so beautifully colorful Just gazing at them makes my heart dance
mlVoiceResource_Text.900213: Because autumn passes by in the blink of an eye, we have to actively create memories, don't we?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900214: Delicious food, reading, movies── It's hard to give up moving your body too I want to hear about your autumn, okay?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900215: It's going to get chilly for a while, so be careful not to catch a cold, okay? ...Hmm, maybe I'm meddling too much?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900216: During today's commute, let's have a rule where if you say 'It's cold', you lose. Shall we?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900217: Everyone at the dorm is getting excited talking about ozoni. Each of us is making our hometown's taste.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900220: Have you already decorated the tree? Hehe, of course, I'm all set~ The star at the top is sparkling too~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900221: I think you're getting a lot, but── is there room for my share...? I wonder...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900222: Even though it's okay not to give anything back── ...Ah, that's a lie~ Thank you, Producer
mlVoiceResource_Text.900225: I couldn't help but buy some hina-arare... How about you?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900228: Thanks for all your help this year, and next year, we already have plans to work together. I'm a lucky person.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900230: I've already secured a delicious cake for Koi-kun. Since I'm always being treated by you, you know.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900232: Well then, I have to go to Yuhiri's place. Today, I should be able to escort her without any worries.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900234: It's an irreplaceable day when you've gained connections to the world. I want to celebrate it too.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900235: Good morning~ Well then, shall we do our best today?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900236: P-tan, you're tired~ Hey, would you like to take a break here?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900237: You seem to be in good spirits today. You have a lot of energy, don't you?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900238: Hey, are you the type of producer who goes to karaoke? Oh, the other day──...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900239: Hey, could you take a look at this photo? Isn't it amazing? Such a beautiful cat, right~?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900240: Oh my, you're neglecting your assigned idol. You're a bad producer~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900241: Hello, are you awake~? It's not good to neglect things~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900242: The weather is on our side, so── Let's get excited and do our best at work!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900243: It's such a nice day, so instead of desk work all day, you should get some sunlight too, okay?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900244: It's okay if it rains, but── Oh. Did you bring your umbrella?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900245: ～～♪ Good mood? Of course it is~ Today's umbrella is my favorite, you know~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900246: It's pouring~ I hope the public transportation won't stop. Can you get home safely, P-tan?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900247: It's pouring like crazy~ I hope the public transportation won't stop. Can you get home safely, P-tan?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900248: If it accumulates, I'll definitely have you accompany me~! For what? Snow play, of course!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900249: Right now, it's the best time to just take a walk and snap some photos, don't you think?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900250: This time of year makes you sleepy, huh~... Are you going to sleep, P-tan? I'll wake Sanmyu up later, okay~?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900253: Producer, that book you recommended was so interesting! Thank you!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900254: Hey, that movie. It's a hot topic. Did you see it? ...Yay! So, how was it? I've been dying to tell someone!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900255: I want ice cream~ Oh yeah, because it's winter, you know. It's the one you enjoy while benefiting from the heating.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900256: Anyone need coffee~? ...Yuika? Yuika's more of a cocoa person~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900257: Special programs, countdowns, being busy during the New Year's holidays, it's all very much appreciated~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900260: The present I want from Yuika is── ...Ah, just kidding, okay? No need to actually take notes!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900261: Here you go, P-tan~ A gift of chocolates from Kogane-chan from a great store~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900262: Hehe, thank you! I've been looking forward to what I'd get in return~?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900265: I have a small hina doll set in my room~ Just the hina and the emperor dolls~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900268: Hey Producer, let's work together next year too, okay? ...Nnfufu, I plan to keep bothering you for a while~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900269: ...Ahaha, thank you. It's a bit embarrassing face to face, after all~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900270: There's something about surprises with Kogane that's worth it, right...? Like, it feels rewarding to be the one planning it...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900274: Happy birthday! Today, I'll be relatively more inclined to grant your wishes, Producer~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900275: Good morning... ...Today... seems like... something good... is going to... happen...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900276: Good work... ...Make sure to... drink... enough water...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900279: A letter... from my... school friends... is... going around...♪
mlVoiceResource_Text.900283:
Look...
...Even the sheets...
smell... like the sun...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900289:
Someone... seems to have come... Hehe...
Spring is here...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900293:
Someone... seems to have come... Shhh...
────Autumn is here...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900295:
Someone... seems to have come... Welcome...
Winter...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900296:
Let's meet again... ...When it gets warmer...
Cyclamen-san...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900300:
Merry Christmas...
...May warm lights...
shine in every window...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900301:
A day...
to hand over...
...many thanks...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900302:
Tha... thank you...
...Hehe...
Such... a sweet smell...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900305:
Every year...
...Grandma... celebrates...
'They've grown up,' she says...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900308:
Let's clean up... ...So that even the sun...
smiles at the new year...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900315:
Producer-san, listen up!
Something happened at
school the other day──
mlVoiceResource_Text.900316:
I can't drink milk,
but I like ice cream!
I like coffee milk too!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900317:
Will I be able to become like
Producer-san and everyone else when I grow up too?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900318:
Because I'm tall,
my friends can always find me easily!
I'm proud of it!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900319:
What do you think is
necessary to make everyone
smile like a hero...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900320:
Producer-san!
Is there anything I can
help you with?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900321:
Energy! Determination! I'm all set!
I, Kaho Komiya, am
ready for action anytime!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900322:
Today, I played in the park
with my friends before coming here!
It was so much fun!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900323:
Our hearts are burning
like the sun...!
 Hehe, what do you think...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900324:
My mom told me to bring an umbrella!
Even if it rains, I'll be safe!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900325:
Today, I wore rain boots!
Now I can jump into big
puddles with no problem!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900326:
Since it's raining, we played dodgeball
in the gym! It was a great match!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900327:
It's raining really heavily!
It's like 'the rain of frogs'!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900328:
If it snows a lot,
I want to make
snowmen or snow forts!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900329:
Mamemaru found some flowers
while on a walk! He's a 'genius of discovery'!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900330:
Producer-san! What events did
you participate in at sports day
when you were a child?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900333:
We did some sketching on a field trip!
The leaves were turning red and
it was so beautiful!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900334:
Look!
I found a really big pine cone!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900335:
Producer-san,
why does your breath
turn white on cold days?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900336:
Hehe, I played tag with everyone
so I'm all warm now!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900337:
During New Year's,
I played Karuta and Hanetsuki with my dad! Of course, it was a serious match!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900340:
I wrote a letter to Santa with
Mamemaru! I asked Mom for help~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900341:
We made it in home economics class!
Happy Valentine's, Producer-san!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900342:
A return gift...! I'm so, so happy!
Thank you very much~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900345:
Ta-da~! Look, paper cup hina dolls
I made! Aren't they cute~?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900348:
I want to work really, really hard
with you next year too, Producer-san!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900350:
When I gave Choco-senpai a present,
he said 'Let's eat together'...! So
I ended up eating some too...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900351:
It's Juri-chan's birthday~! As a
regular return gift, I'll be extra
gentle to Juri-chan!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900354:
Producer-san's birthday is a very
special day~! Congratulations~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900355:
Good work, Producer-san! Let's do
our best together at work today!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900356:
I bought some new chocolates!
Would you like to taste them later...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900357:
～～～～♪ Uhh, did you hear that...?!?
Please forget it~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900358:
Wow, a snack...!?
Thank you very much~!
Your concern means a lot~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900359:
It's such an honor to be able to work
with you, Producer-san!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900361:
At this rate, it might melt or...
something── Just kidding! Just about
chocolates!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900362:
It's sunny today, huh~! Ah, no, I
messed up! Uh, 'It's sunny today'~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900363:
It's such nice weather, so let's
work hard today too!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900364:
Producer-san, did you bring an
umbrella today...!? Or did you
forget it...!?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900365:
Producer-san...! There's a new
restaurant that offers services on
rainy days...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900366:
Isn't it just perfect timing that
it's raining only during commutes...?
No?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900367:
It's raining cats and dogs...!
...Is that the right expression
for this moment...!?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900368:
Even if I can't make a snowman,
at least a snow rabbit...!
I wonder if it'll snow enough for that...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900369:
Next time, we're going on a picnic
with everyone! I'm putting all my
energy into choosing snacks!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900370:
Spring makes me want to take
different routes than usual...!
It's perfect weather for a stroll!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900373:
The season of delicious food has
begun, hasn't it...! Well, it's
kind of like that all year round...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900374:
It's the season of appetite,
so of course I'll eat a lot!
And then I'll move a lot too!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900375:
Producer-san, how about having some
ice cream together later? In a room
with good heating!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900376:
It's so hard to get out of bed
in the winter that my mom often
scolds me...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900377:
For New Year's, there's crab and
sushi, sukiyaki or yakiniku, and
of course, osechi and mochi too!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900380:
Cake, presents, and chicken too!
I'm equally excited for all of them!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900381: This is a carefully selected chocolate idol product! The taste is guaranteed, so please enjoy it!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900382: Wow, thank you very much! If it's a choice by Producer-san, it must be definitely right...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900385: Every time I decorate the hina dolls, I look up the combinations of the three court ladies and tools... I want to remember them soon...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900388: Thank you very much for your hard work this year──Oops, not yet! Please continue to take care of the remaining work!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900389: I've already reserved a chocolate cake! I asked for a slightly luxurious plate, hehe...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900391: When I said it would be a double feature of presents and chocolates, Juri-chan laughed at the way I said it...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900394: Happy birthday! I hope the coming year will be filled with delicious and happy days for you!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900395: Producer, are you tired? If you are, make sure to take a proper rest.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900396: I'm feeling a bit hungry... How about you? Want to have a snack together?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900397: ...What? There's nothing to see even if you stare like that.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900398: Yeah, I'm feeling pretty good today. If there's anything, let me know. I feel like I can handle anything.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900399: I feel like I've been really fulfilled lately. It might be thanks to you, Producer.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900400: ...What's wrong? If you're spacing out like that, and if you're feeling unwell, you should say so.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900401: ...You seem busy. Oh, I'll be fine later. I'll be reading a magazine and waiting.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900402: I think I'll go for a light run outside... Hey, you shouldn't sit around all the time either, you know?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900403: The sun is strong today, so if you're going out, you should be careful.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900404: Oops... I forgot my umbrella at school... I hope it doesn't rain...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900405: On rainy days, your hair gets all frizzy and messy, huh? It's a hassle.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900406: If it rains too much, we won't be able to practice running... That's a bummer.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900407: Oh no... Even just going back to the dormitory will be quite a hassle with this rain.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900408: Kaho seems like she'd be eager to do a snowball fight, huh... Oh, Haru too, I guess.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900409: Everyone's good at taking pictures of flowers and stuff, right? Editing them too? That kind of stuff is amazing...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900410: The other day, I saw Choco dozing off so comfortably while we were on the move. Spring makes you want to sleep as much as you want, huh?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900413: Phew... I borrowed a manga from Ritsu, and it was so interesting that I ended up staying up late.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900414: It's about time to change into winter clothes, huh... I want some autumn clothes too, but I wonder where I should buy them...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900415: We're talking about having a hot pot party at the dormitory next time... Hot pot is definitely the way to go on cold days.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900416: It's canned corn soup, but do you want to drink it? They're having a campaign at the convenience store, so it's still warm.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900417: They were pounding mochi at the shopping street, so I got to try it, but surprisingly, it's quite a laborious task.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900420: The town starts to feel like Christmas, and I get all excited... For some reason.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900421: ...Um, I've been relying on you, so, well, it's obligatory...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900422: Is this for me!? I feel bad... Even though you didn't give me anything that great...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900425: I bought lots of traditional sweets for Hina Matsuri! You can choose your favorite.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900428: This feeling of being chased by busyness... Feels like the end of the year, huh... I actually quite like this atmosphere.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900429: You remembered my birthday...!? ...Thanks, I'm happy.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900431: When I went to buy limited edition items, it was so crowded... Well, I'm glad Choco was happy.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900434: Hmm... Is this... a birthday present...? Make sure to open it when you get home, okay!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900435: Good morning... Producer-sama... Let's spend today together with Rinze...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900436: If you're tired... Rinze will... massage your shoulders... and so on...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900437: I borrowed a comic from Chiyoko-san... It's a very deep world...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900438: Producer-sama... Please keep Rinze... by your side...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900439: Meeting everyone... makes Rinze... feel very calm...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900440: Producer-sama... Are you tired...? Are you here...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900442: Being able to meet Producer-sama... clears up Rinze's heart...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900443: Thanks to you... I'm spending today... pleasantly...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900444: The haze is... spreading... Please be careful... on your way back...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900445: Rain... Rain... falling... falling... Hehe... it's a nursery rhyme...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900446: After the rain... a rainbow... appears... If you think about it... this sky too...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900447: The sound of rain... is like... a rumble... I wonder if... Rinze's voice... reaches you...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900448: Snow... hail... falling... falling... Hehe... a nostalgic sound...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900449: The view of spring... is priceless... Rinze... treasures this time...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900450: Plum... peach... cherry blossoms... Each flower... is lovely...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900453: Along the way... maple leaves... have fallen...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900454: Autumn days are fleeting... Spending time with Producer-sama... is even more...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900455: Rinze... doesn't feel cold... because Producer-sama... is by my side...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900456: The sun is warm... the moon is clear... Welcoming winter here... is beautiful...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900457: Cold... pure... solemn... The smell of the beginning of the year...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900460: The night when sleds go through the sky... May happiness... visit Producer-sama's window too...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900461: What I give you... are Rinze's... feelings...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900462: Just your consideration... in choosing a return gift... is enough to make Rinze's heart...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900465: Today is Hinamatsuri... It feels somehow nostalgic and happy...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900468: The New Year's footsteps are getting closer...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900471: I've prepared a celebration gift... It's that, you know...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900472: Let's celebrate at the dorm... Until the end of today...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900474: Producer, celebrating this day with you makes me happy...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900475: Good morning! It seems like it will be a good day today!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900476: I hope you're not tired. Taking proper rest is important for work.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900477: Are you feeling hungry? Let's eat properly after all that activity!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900478: Who taught me, It's okay to be your usual self, Natsuha? I want to say the same thing to you.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900479: Next time, we're going to the gym with everyone! I'm really looking forward to it!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900480: Hey, Producer, there's no time for idling around.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900481: There's no urgent schedule, right? In that case, shall we do some training?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900482: The weather is nice. How about taking a walk as a break?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900483: Today, the wind feels very refreshing. Hehe, it makes me want to go for a drive.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900484: The clouds are spreading... It might rain, so it might be better to skip the run...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900485: It doesn't seem like it's going to stop raining soon... Today, let's focus on indoor training.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900486: I don't hate rain, but if I can't go for a walk, Cattleya will get bored...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900487: With this heavy rain, driving could be dangerous. Be sure to take care of yourself too.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900488: How about a snowball fight? It's three against three with us and Producer!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900489: Why don't you try some strength training too? It's always good to start something new!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900490: The wind feels so good that I ended up running too much. I have to be careful not to overdo it.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900493: There's art in autumn, and there's also sports. There are various types of autumn, but I'm going to enjoy them all!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900494: Autumn clothes have a wide range of coordination options, which is fun. I feel like trying out various things.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900495: Training in the cold season has a high fat-burning effect. I have to maintain my figure properly.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900496: When the temperature drops, it's easy to have bad posture. Come on, let's stretch, okay?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900497: Producer, are you feeling sluggish from the New Year? Let's start training!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900500: It's Christmas after all! How about having a party at the office?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900501: Producer, please accept this! I've put all my feelings into it.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900502: I really respect your sense of duty like this. And... thank you.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900505: Today is Hinamatsuri, right? Someday, I'd like to try decorating my house with Hina dolls too.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900508: The end of the year is when our true abilities are tested. Let's give it our all until the very last moment of this year!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900511: I brought training gear to celebrate Chiyoko's birthday!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900512: Today is Juri's birthday! Let's continue to strive together!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900514: You can expect a present! I chose it just for you, so there's no doubt it's perfect!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900515: Good morning, Producer! Let's do our best together today!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900516: Are you tired? If there's anything I can do to help, just let me know!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900517: Hey, hey, how's your day going, Producer?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900518: I was looking at Tenka-chan's pictures. Hehe, she's so cute~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900519: There's a style I want to try. I'd like to hear your opinion too, Producer~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900520: If there's anything you need help with, just tell me, okay?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900521: Producer, can we talk for a moment?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900522: It's so warm~ Makes me want to take a nap with Tenka-chan.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900523: It was nice weather, so I woke up early and went for a run. Feels great~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900524: Looks like it's going to rain...! Better not forget your umbrella when you go out.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900525: Fashionable umbrellas are nice~ But it feels like a waste to use them, right...?!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900526: Hehe... It's hard to manage your hair when it's humid~...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900527: You're going to work now, right, Producer...? Just be careful, okay...?!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900528: I wonder if it'll snow~ Hehe, I want to make a snowman with Tenka-chan and Chiyuki-san~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900529: Look, look~ I painted my nails cherry blossom pink~☆ Thinking of adding some petal decorations~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900530: Producer, there were some beautiful flowers blooming nearby! Want to go see them...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900533: Autumn is comfortable, so you can try various outfits~☆ Hehe~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900534: There are so many delicious things, I might end up eating too much! Need to be careful...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900535: Winter has beautiful stars~ When you look up at the sky at night, they sparkle~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900536: It's the season for layering clothes~☆ You can create lots of variations, it's super fun~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900537: During New Year's, it's easy to loosen the purse strings, so we have to be careful, right?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900540: Illuminations are nice, right~ It's incredibly romantic.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900541:
Happy Valentine's☆
Here! Chocolates for you,
Producer!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900542: Thanks for the wonderful return gift! Hehe, it's too precious to eat~...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900545: Huh? This hina-mochi, even the bottom layer is pink~! Hehe, it's like an ALSTROEMERIA flower~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900548: Producer! You're busy at the end of the year, right? I'll help with anything you need!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900549: Hehe, getting congratulations from you, Producer, makes me super happy!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900550: Today's a really happy day! Because I get to say congratulations to Tenka-chan☆
mlVoiceResource_Text.900551:
I made a cake
with Tenka-chan☆
Hehe, I hope she'll be happy.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900552: Happy birthday! I hope you have a wonderful day!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900553: ──Ah... Good morning... Producer... ...Guess I'll... go back to sleep...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900554: Producer... If you get sleepy... let me know, okay...? I have a blanket...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900555: I set a new high score in the game! So... Tenka's feeling great today...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900556: Producer... since you're working hard... I'll give you some Tenka points...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900557: How about a nap time...? ...No...? Then... how about snack time...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900559: Um, are you off today...? Can I come home...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900560: The sofa... with the sun shining... is warm and cozy... Perfect for a nap spot...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900561: Since the weather's nice... I went for a walk with Nachi... Just for a bit...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900562: Hehe... I brought a foldable umbrella... just in case...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900563: The sound of rain... If you listen to it for a while... it makes you sleepy...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900564: Aah, it's raining... Until it stops... let's play some games...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900565: Eek...! There's a really loud... rumbling sound...! Gotta hide my belly button...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900566: It's dangerous on snowy roads...! The trick to walking without slipping is... like a penguin...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900567: Since it's spring... feeling sleepy is... inevitable, right...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900568: Sakura mochi and... dango... Spring is... the season for Japanese sweets, isn't it...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900571: Autumn for Tenka is... the season of naps... The best... right...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900572: Autumn...── It's nice being in between hot and cold, isn't it...?
