mlVoiceResource_Text.900573: This morning... Tenka managed to... get out of bed after a lot of effort... ...Tenka's amazing...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900574: Producer... How about putting a kotatsu in the office...? There are good ones online...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900575: It's New Year's... So instead of just lazing around, I'll... laze around even more...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900578: Hehe... Having a birthday... on Christmas...! It's like... double the celebration...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900579: I tried my best... to melt and solidify it...! So... technically, it's homemade...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900580: Oh...! White Day...? Thanks...! Then... watch as Tenka eats it...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900583: Hehe... Naa-chi has hina dolls... and Tenka also... has hina dolls...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900586: Producer...! Once work's done, Tenka will... laze around so much...!!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900587: Tenka leveled up...! Hehe... Let's keep leveling up together from now on...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900588: At the moment the date changed... I said 'Congratulations!' in unison with Nachi-chan...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900589:
Hehe...
Today, I'm going to celebrate
Chiyuki-san a lot...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900590: Happy birthday, Producer...! Let's have some cake to celebrate...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900591: Good morning. Let's do our best today too, okay, Producer-san♪
mlVoiceResource_Text.900592: Hehe, good work. How about a tea time once we're done with this?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900593: Light, sound, color, smell... Regardless of the weather outside the window, there's something I like about it.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900594: Ah, Producer-san. I have a message from Hazuki-san for you...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900595: When I meet everyone at the office, it makes me want to work harder too.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900597: I'll be here for a while... If you need anything, just let me know.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900598: It's a perfect day for a stroll. Shall we go to that shop we've been curious about...♪
mlVoiceResource_Text.900599: S-Sorry...! The sun feels so nice that I got a bit drowsy.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900600: Even on cloudy days, UV rays still come through... So we shouldn't let our guard down.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900601: I was making teru teru bozu. How about making one together, Producer-san?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900602: It's a strap for your umbrella. Please take it if you'd like. It makes it easier to find.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900603: With this rain, umbrellas seem pointless... But... hehe, I won't give up.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900604: Wow, it's snowing...! Hehe, I hope we can make a snow rabbit and a snowman♪
mlVoiceResource_Text.900605: I made a bookmark with cherry blossom petals. I wanted to preserve a bit of their fleeting beauty.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900606: What's your choice for a picnic bento? Sandwiches or rice balls?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900609: I'm collecting pinecones... I might make a wreath using acorns too.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900610: Autumn is so delicious... Um, is it okay if I eat this much, Producer-san...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900611: I'm knitting a scarf and gloves. They have matching patterns, hehe.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900612: Good job in the cold. I'll make some warm coffee, so please wait a bit.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900613: I didn't have the courage to ask for just one mochi for the new year... I need to exercise properly, huh.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900616: Seeing Christmas decorations at various stores makes me want to try making some myself.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900617: Um... Sorry... Could you accept this chocolate?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900618: Hehe, I'm happy. It seems I was looking forward to it... Thank you for the return gift.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900621: Chirashi sushi, clam soup, and rice cakes... Hehe... The party preparations are all set♪
mlVoiceResource_Text.900624: It seems the year-end special programs will be broadcasted locally too... My family is looking forward to it♪
mlVoiceResource_Text.900625:
特別な日を、大切な人たちと
一緒に過ごせて……
とっても幸せです、私
mlVoiceResource_Text.900626: Naa-chan's and Tenka-chan's birthdays... are very special days for me too.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900627: I bought two kinds of cake for the celebration. Today, let's not hold back~♪
mlVoiceResource_Text.900628: Happy birthday! I'll do my best so we can continue to smile together!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900629:
Good morning!
I wonder if anything good will happen today~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900630:
What are you spacing out for?
Let's look for something fun!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900631:
Producer-san, I'm bored.
Don't you have anything interesting?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900632:
I found an interesting book!
Do you want to read it, Producer-san?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900633: Being an idol lets you do interesting things, right? It's exciting!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900634:
Mm... I'm bored.
Don't you have anything?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900635: What have you been doing since earlier? I'm curious! Please tell me~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900636:
It's super sunny!
I want to go play outside!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900637: The wind feels great, doesn't it? I know! Let's go fly some paper airplanes!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900638:
Producer-san!
Look, isn't there something flying beyond the clouds!?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900639: Even with all this rain, it's sunny above the clouds, right? I want to see it~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900640: They say the shape of umbrellas hasn't changed for a long time. Can't we make something cooler?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900641: There's a really loud sound outside... Do you want to go check it out!?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900642: It's snowing! Let's go make footprints first! Producer-san!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900643: I saw a flower I've never seen before! I want you to see it too, Producer-san!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900644: I caught a big butterfly! What should we feed it? I'll look it up~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900647: I heard there are days when the moon looks really big! I want to see it~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900648: Producer-san, I found a fruit I've never seen before! Will it sprout if we plant it?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900649: Winter makes the stars look really pretty, huh? I want to see them more clearly. Don't we have a telescope?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900650: It's cold, huh? How about putting a kotatsu in the office?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900651: How does God listen to everyone's wishes? It seems like it would be tough to handle all of them.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900654: How can we catch Santa Claus? Let's come up with a strategy together!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900655: Why do we give chocolates on Valentine's Day? Can't we give something else?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900656: I see, we have to give chocolates on Valentine's Day first, or else we won't get any sweets on White Day~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900659: Are we really not allowed to eat more than our age in hina-arare? Then we have no choice but to eat hishimochi!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900662: Everyone seems busy. It's boring when no one wants to hang out.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900663: It was my birthday today~ Everyone wished me happy birthday, and I remembered!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900664: I found something really interesting! I'm going to use it as Fuyuko-chan's birthday present~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900666:
Producer-san!
Happy birthday~
Did you eat cake?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900667: Good morning, Producer-san! ♡ Please take care of me today too.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900668: Are you tired? Remember, it's important not to push yourself too hard for Mei and the others.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900669: Um... would you like to go out to eat sometime? There's a new super spicy menu!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900670: What kind of snacks would make you happy, Producer-san? I'll prepare them for you ♡
mlVoiceResource_Text.900671: Um... I wanted to talk to you about Asahi-chan and Mei-chan for a bit...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900672: Um... Producer-san, are you busy right now? ...Ehe, sorry...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900673: I'd be really happy if you paid more attention to Mei... Just saying.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900674: Nice weather makes me happy! ♡ It seems like it's going to be a wonderful day.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900675: Um... are you feeling sleepy? Since it's such nice weather, it's okay, I'll keep it a secret.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900676: I hope it doesn't rain... Um, I have a folding umbrella just in case...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900677: On rainy days, I give myself a little present so my mood doesn't get gloomy.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900678: Are you going out today...? Don't forget a towel so you don't catch a cold ♡
mlVoiceResource_Text.900679: I'm a little worried about the rain... Will you be able to get home safely, Producer-san...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900680: Snow is so beautiful, isn't it? I love it. The pure white snow before it touches the ground.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900681: Spring feels like such a cute season. There are so many flowers blooming, and it's warm and relaxing ♡
mlVoiceResource_Text.900682: At this time of year, every store has strawberry sweets... They all look so delicious, it's hard to choose.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900685: Doesn't it feel like autumn is being encroached upon by summer and winter more and more each year...? Oh, is that not the case?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900686: Do you already have something in mind for 'autumn's specialty,' Producer-san? I'm curious, you know~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900687: Is it like a joke if I say I like winter...!? N-No, that's not it~...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900688: When I see Christmas illuminations, I'm like, 'Yay!' They're so sparkly and beautiful ♡
mlVoiceResource_Text.900689: Please keep it a secret that Mei and Producer-san ate a lot of mochi...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900692: Did you make a wish for Santa Claus?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900693: Um... since you always... take care of me... could you... accept this from me...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900694: Wow, I'm so happy ♡ Thank you for the return gift, Producer-san.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900697: We have a seven-tier display at home. Yes, it's our pride and joy. We carefully display it every year.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900700: You're always running around all year... Take care of your body a little. ...Thank you for your hard work this year too.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900701: The 'congratulations' from Producer-san is the most wonderful.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900702: I hope Asahi-chan remembers that today is her birthday...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900704: Happy birthday! Spend a wonderful day today and make it a wonderful year!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900705: Good morning, Producer! Let's go full throttle today too~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900706: You look tired, huh? How about taking a break? I'll keep you company to pass the time.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900707: Your selfies are looking great! You're seriously killing it!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900708: Oh no... I forgot about my school assignment...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900709: Mmm... I feel like going to karaoke! Wanna go together?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900710: Hey Producer, got any interesting stories? Even if they're not that funny, it's fine?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900711: Producer, how about taking a break? Want to grab something to drink?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900712: Ahaha~ The weather's so nice! My mood is getting higher~♪
mlVoiceResource_Text.900713: Producer! Since the weather's nice, let's go somewhere~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900714: Whoa, it's raining so hard...! Hey, I don't have an umbrella today!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900715: Whoa... my hair is getting all curly from the humidity...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900716:
In the rice field~♪
The frogs~♪
Go croak croak~♪
mlVoiceResource_Text.900717: Whoa...! It's gonna be soaking wet on the way back for sure!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900718:
Wow, it's snowing!
If it piles up, let's play together~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900719: Spring makes you feel so laid-back, doesn't it...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900720: You can see the cherry blossoms from my room's window~ Isn't it nice~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900723: Got some sweet potatoes from the neighbor's house~ Wanna join, Producer?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900724: Autumn feels really nice, doesn't it? It's comfortable to spend time in.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900725:
It's cold!
Producer, can I turn up the room temperature?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900726: Hey Producer, which do you prefer, cold or hot weather?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900727: Hey look, Producer~! This is my New Year's calligraphy for this year~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900730: Lately, my little brother and sister have been asking, 'Have you been a good kid?'
mlVoiceResource_Text.900731: Here, have some chocolate~! It was really delicious, so I'm giving some to you too~♪
mlVoiceResource_Text.900732: Oh, a return gift? Awesome~! I'll open it now~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900735: Isn't it hard to set up the Hina dolls? Except for my sister, nobody else in the house can do it properly!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900738: The end of the year is so busy, right? Huh, are we okay? ... We're also in a lot of trouble!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900740: Asahi-chan was really happy with the present! Ahaha, I'm happy too~♪
mlVoiceResource_Text.900741: Choosing a present for Fuyuko-chan was fun! We went to shops we don't usually go to.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900742: Happy birthday, Producer~♪ Today's a special day, so feel free to tell me anything~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900743:
Yawn...
Ah, sorry.
Good morning, Producer.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900745: Here, here, the diary. Wait for it.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900746: Hehe, a yawn? ...Yawwn. Uh-oh, it's contagious.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900747: Hey, can I eat this? Hey.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900748: Hey, can you hear me? Hey.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900750: I bet 100 yen it'll clear up like this. Hehe, what do you think?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900762: Autumn? Huh, when did autumn start?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900763: Is it cold? Making snowmen normal? Hot?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900764: Brrr, it's cold. Chilly chilly chilly chilly...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900765: New Year's gift? Got it. Let's live it up.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900768: Huh, it's a holiday, right? Christmas.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900777:
Birthday, huh?
Feels like a birthday, huh~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900780: It's Hinana's birthday, right? You mentioned it. Happy Birthday, Yeah~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900782:
Good morning.
...Look forward to working with you.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900783:
You don't have to mind me.
Let's keep it business-like.
...It's easier for both of us, isn't it?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900784:
Oh, small talk is fine.
Don't mind me.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900785:
...What is it? If you have something to say, say it.
It's annoying if you plead with your eyes.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900786:
Do you need to burn passion to get anything done?
High efficiency, impressive.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900787: If there's nothing to do, I'll go home.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900788: Please don't worry about me. Focus on your work. It's annoying to be bothered.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900789:
I'll open the window.
The air is stagnant.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900790:
Yes,
today's weather is sunny.
So what?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900791: Even if the sun hides, the stuffiness remains the same. Whose fault is it?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900793: Looks like rain. Any changes to the schedule? Please inform me if there are.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900794: Were you out in this rain? ...Drenched.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900795: Playing in the snow? I'm not interested. Feel free to enjoy it on your own.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900796:
You got this flower?
...Thoughtful of you.
Well done.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900800: There are a lot of fallen leaves in front of the office... Just reporting.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900801: Fruit jelly? Thank you. ...Any flavor is fine.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900802: Oh, it's okay. That blanket... It's your personal item, right?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900803: When you come in from outside? Yes. Gargle, wash your hands... If you know, then go ahead.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900804: Happy New Year. Looking forward to working with you this year.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900807: Yes, it's Christmas. So, what's the point?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900808: I'll distribute Valentine's Day sweets to my colleagues as a token of appreciation.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900809: What's this? White Day, perhaps? Thank you very much.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900815: Thank you for your support this year. Whether I'll be here next year... I don't know.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900817: It's Asakura's birthday, so what? It's none of your business, right?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900819: A present for Hinana? Just give her some snacks or something. I don't know.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900820: It's your birthday? Congratulations. ...Well, there you go.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900821: G-Good morning...! Please take care of me today too.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900822: G-Good job...! Would you like some candy, Producer-san...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900823: Um, is it okay if I use this desk...? I want to finish my homework early...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900824: Eek...! ...S-Sorry. You suddenly made noise, so...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900825: I-I'll inform everyone if there's any contact...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900828: I-It's nice weather, isn't it...? ...Th-That's all...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900829: Uh, hehe... T-Today, the sunlight feels really nice.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900830: Um, d-do you think it's going to rain...? I-I forgot my umbrella today...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900831: Eeek...! Oh, is that the sound of rain...? It startled me...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900832: Um, d-do you know the forecast...? I-I hope it clears up by the time we go home...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900833: T-This rain is really something... I-It's not that I'm scared or anything...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900835: Uh, this is a new spring product... I saw it at the convenience store... D-Do you want it...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900836: T-Translucent-chan... you were asleep earlier... Maybe it's because it's spring...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900839: Autumn of art, autumn of sports... autumn of reading... I guess I'm in the autumn of studying...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900840: Th-This time of year, I sometimes don't know what to wear... Suits look good, don't they...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900841: T-Today is cold, isn't it...? I-I wore gloves, but my fingers are still cold...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900842: Hinana-chan and I were talking about going to the convenience store to buy something warm...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900843: L-Look, please...! When I drew a fortune, it was Daikichi (great luck)...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900846: Ch-Christmas...! If we didn't have work, it would be nice to gather with everyone...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900847: Um, today is Valentine's Day, so... I wanted to express my gratitude for all your help...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900848: Eeek...! Is this candy... for White Day...? Thank you very much...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900851: Hinana-arare...? Y-You're giving it to me...? Thank you very much.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900854: Th-Thank you for your hard work this year...! If there's anything I can help with, please let me know...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900856: I told Toru-chan, Congratulations, but... she said, [What are you talking about?]...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900858: Hinana-chan tells me what she wants, so I don't have to worry!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900859: Ahaha~ Producer-san...! T-Today is your birthday, right...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900860: Ahaha~ It's nice to see Hinana in the morning, isn't it~?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900861: Ahaha~ They say if you sigh, happiness runs away~?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900862: Hey, Producer, can you tell if today's Hinana is different from usual~?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900863: Isn't this strap cute~? It matches with Toru-senpai~♡
mlVoiceResource_Text.900864: Hey, Producer, tell us an interesting story~ Hinana is listening!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900865: Hey, haven't you forgotten about Hinana~?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900866: Hey, Producer, what are you doing now~?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900867: Aha~ It looks like the weather will bring something good today too~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900868: I'm starting to feel sleepy... Can I use the sofa?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900869: It's getting cloudy, huh? Hinana will go home before it rains, okay?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900870: Hmm, it's still raining, so maybe we should postpone going out until next time?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900871: Hinana wore cute rain boots today.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900872: It's pouring rain... Producer, will you give me a ride?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900873: Ahaha~ Snow~! Producer, want to have a snowball fight~?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900874: I bought a lot of spring cosmetics! I want to use them soon~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900875: Spring is warm and relaxing, it feels so happy~ doesn't it?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900878: Autumn is full of delicious fruits like sweet potatoes and chestnuts~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900879: Autumn clothes are cute, but it gets cold so quickly that you can only wear them for a short time~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900880: I bought YourKuma-chan's scarf, so I want to use it soon~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900881: Producer, you look cold~ Shall we have a lesson together with Hinana?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900882: Ahaha~ Being together with Hinana again this year makes me happy~ don't you think?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900885: Ahaha~ Christmas... I have too many things I want, but how many can I ask for?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900886: Producer, you're here! Hey, do you want chocolate from Hinana?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900887: Ahaha~ I was looking forward to the return gift from Producer~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900890: Hinamatsuri... it feels like Hinana's festival, doesn't it? ...Huh? Why are you laughing?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900893: Thank you for your hard work this year~ Hinana had a fun and happy year again~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900894: Today, Hinana's wishes will be granted, right? Right, Producer?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900895: Let's celebrate together in Toru-senpai's room~ Aha~, looking forward to it~♡
mlVoiceResource_Text.900898: Producer, are you happy to be celebrated by Hinana? That's good then~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900900: ...Are you tired? How are you feeling?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900902: ...Huh? Hmm? Your stomach seems a bit bloated, doesn't it?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900904: ...Wow, isn't it unacceptable to neglect your assigned idol like that?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900905: ...What do you think about that kind of busy impression?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900906: Producer-san, you seem like the type to say, 'It's nice weather, so let's do our best,' right?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900907: Oh, talking about the weather and small talk is okay~
mlVoiceResource_Text.900908: ...Isn't this the one that predicts rain? My laundry...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900909: Low pressure idiot... Ouch, my head hurts.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900910: Did I borrow the umbrella from the office? It wasn't raining when I came...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900911: Why don't you go check the outside for a bit? I'm rooting for you!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900912: Can I put snow on your back? ... Can I put snow on your back?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900913: Which spring drama are you watching? The one I'm hooked on seems to have few viewers...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900914: During spring, trains get crowded, don't they? If someone doesn't follow proper manners, I'll curse them!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900917: I'm on a diet, so I don't want to hear about autumn flavors or anything like that.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900918: Do you like mushrooms? I got a lot, but they don't last long.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900919: I want warm treats! Warm treats!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900920: That's why you're hunching over, making it even colder.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900921: I won't call it New Year's money, but there's a live performance I want to check out...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900924: If you have plans or something, feel free to go home early. If you have any, that is.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900925: If you want something, just say so clearly. I have to go buy it, you know.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900926: Oh, thanks for the return gift. Um... it's about three times as much, naturally.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900929: Isn't the attire of people from the past amazing? Like the juni-hitoe. If Mikoto-san wore it, it would be absolutely amazing!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900932: ...Ah... uh... um... Thank you for your hard work this year.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900935: It's my birthday, but there's nothing special about today...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900936: Good morning, Producer. Can I check today's schedule?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900937: Are you not tired? It's better to rest when you can.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900938: Thanks for the treats, as always... I'll enjoy them.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900939: I'm not pushing myself too hard... Effort is just something that comes naturally.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900940: Can I use the TV? There's a program I want to watch.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900941: There isn't much time to relax, is there?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900942: Producer, if there's nothing else, can I go to the practice room?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900943: The practice room seems to be full... I might go for a run outside.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900944: Can I open the window a bit? It seems like there's a nice breeze today.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900945: It seems to have gotten quite cloudy while we were practicing.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900946: It's raining... I didn't notice because I was listening to music.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900947: We can still practice even if it's raining, so it's fine.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900948: Don't worry about me, I'll keep practicing.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900949: Snow... it's starting to fall. It's getting cold, isn't it?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900950: It's a comfortable time of year, so it's important to build up your Stamina.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900951: Seasonal flowers? Sorry, I'm not very familiar with them.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900954: Managing your health is also part of the job, so you have to be careful of temperature changes.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900955: Autumn is comfortable, so it's easy to practice.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900956: It was cold today, so maybe I should extend the stretching session.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900957: It's getting colder, so I have to be careful not to get injured.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900958: I don't really need a break. More importantly, when can I schedule the next practice?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900961: Christmas? If there's no work scheduled, I'll arrange a lesson...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900962: I always receive treats, so here's my thanks too.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900963: ...I meant to express my gratitude, but it seems like I received something again.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900966: Did you buy some hina arare? ...Hmm, it looks delicious.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900969: I'll be in the practice room on New Year's Eve. We don't stop practicing.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900972: Congratulations, Producer. You can be happy on a day like this, can't you?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900973: Huh...? What's up? Stop staring at me like that.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900974:
What...?
I'm not angry...
I said I'm not angry, right?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900975:
Those snacks over there?
I don't know...
You probably put them somewhere, right?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900976:
I always feel like something...
is missing...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900977:
Oh, that package over there?
It's mine, so...
Don't touch it, okay?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900978: Oh, what's with this time? If there's nothing to do... What the hell... Hurry up and finish...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900979: Hey... hey... Tch. Hey! Are you listening? What are you waiting for...?!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900980:
Good weather?
So what...
Are you going to pick flowers or something?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900981:
Mmm...
Haa...
Damn, I'm getting sleepy...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900982:
It's cloudy...
This much is just right.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900983: Damn, rain... And I don't have an umbrella...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900984: Rain... it's been falling continuously... It won't stop...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900985: Wow... it's pouring rain! ...Huh? Who looks happy? Hmph...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900986:
When it snows...
it feels like the background noise disappears...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900987:
Everyone keeps talking about cherry blossoms...
It's annoying.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900988:
Ugh...
what's this...
I'm tired... sleepy...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900991: Sometimes, I feel like disappearing... Is this all there is?
mlVoiceResource_Text.900992: Everywhere you look, there's just events... I don't need weird jobs like that.
mlVoiceResource_Text.900993: It's cold... Is the air conditioning even on? It's cold...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900994: Agh...! Static electricity... What's up with that...?!
mlVoiceResource_Text.900995: Fukuwarai... Hmm... It's kind of funny, isn't it...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900998: I heard bells and the sound of sleighs in the town... Must be Christmas...
mlVoiceResource_Text.900999: Haha... Are you expecting something? Well, do your best.
mlVoiceResource_Text.901003: I'm not interested in those kinds of events. Do them somewhere else.
mlVoiceResource_Text.901006: The last one this year? So what... We're back to work right away.
mlVoiceResource_Text.901007: My birthday? It's got nothing to do with you, does it?
mlVoiceResource_Text.901010: Is it your birthday today? Huh... and?
mlVoiceResource_Text.901011: Good morning, Producer. Let's do our best together today too.
mlVoiceResource_Text.901012: Producer, when are you coming to Okayama again? I'll guide you properly next time.
mlVoiceResource_Text.901013: Hey, don't stare at me like that! ...Geez, I'm embarrassed.
mlVoiceResource_Text.901014: Good job, Producer. Want to rest together? ...Okay, then sit next to me?
mlVoiceResource_Text.901015: Hey, can you talk about something? Like what you ate today, recent news, I want to hear it.
mlVoiceResource_Text.901016: Producer...? ...Geez, you're not listening, are you?
mlVoiceResource_Text.901017: Hey... being left alone is lonely...
mlVoiceResource_Text.901018: It's nice weather, isn't it? Want to take a walk around here together and refresh our minds?
mlVoiceResource_Text.901019: Since it's nice weather, want to have a picnic? I'll try my best to make sandwiches.
mlVoiceResource_Text.901020: On days like this, my mood darkens for some reason... I wish it would clear up...
mlVoiceResource_Text.901021: Producer, I forgot my umbrella today... even though it's raining.
mlVoiceResource_Text.901022: Producer, you always look so put together even on rainy days. I should learn from you...
mlVoiceResource_Text.901023: Wow, the weather is terrible... I'm scared, so Producer, will you walk home with me...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.901024: I took a beautiful picture of the snow this morning. I'll send it to you, Producer.
mlVoiceResource_Text.901025: Yawn... Oh, it's not that... I'm not sleepy, I'm just warm...
mlVoiceResource_Text.901026: Today, I tried a new eyeshadow that's only available in spring. Want to take a closer look?
mlVoiceResource_Text.901029: Speaking of autumn... hehe, it's my birthday, isn't it?
mlVoiceResource_Text.901030: Producer, which do you like best, sweet potatoes, chestnuts, or pumpkins? As for me... Ahaha, I can't decide!
mlVoiceResource_Text.901031: Hey, can I snuggle up close to you, Producer? ...Hehe, it's because it's cold!
mlVoiceResource_Text.901032: The illuminations near the station are so beautiful! ...Hehe, I'm inviting you, you know?
mlVoiceResource_Text.901033: Happy New Year, Producer! Will this year be Luca's year?
mlVoiceResource_Text.901036: Wasn't I a good girl? I want a present from you, Producer...
mlVoiceResource_Text.901037: I bought special chocolates for you, Producer. ...How is it? Are you happy?
mlVoiceResource_Text.901038: You chose it with me in mind? ...Geez... ...Hehe, I'm 100 times happier than I imagined!
mlVoiceResource_Text.901041: Shall we toast with juice now? I bought cute cherry blossom paper cups!
mlVoiceResource_Text.901044: So, the year is ending, huh... Let's do our best together until the end, Producer!
mlVoiceResource_Text.901046: Hey, it's Luca's birthday today. What are you going to do, Producer? As for me... Ahaha, it's a secret...
mlVoiceResource_Text.901047: Today is Haruki-chan's birthday. We've been in touch since the date changed.
mlVoiceResource_Text.901048: Happy birthday! Hey, what do you want to do? ...Hehe, I'll do anything for you!
mlVoiceResource_Text.901049: Good morning, Producer-san. I hope today will be a fun day too.
mlVoiceResource_Text.901050: When your concentration suddenly drops, let's do something else~ Like having a snack...
mlVoiceResource_Text.901051: Um... Can I tidy up here? Oh, it's okay. I'll do it quickly.
mlVoiceResource_Text.901052: Producer-san~ I want to do something~ I don't know what though~
mlVoiceResource_Text.901053: The office is so cozy... It somehow feels calming.
mlVoiceResource_Text.901054: I'm not good at sitting still... Feel free to talk to me anytime, okay?
mlVoiceResource_Text.901055: Hmm... It smells nice...? Do you have some special sweets hidden away, Producer-san?
mlVoiceResource_Text.901056: It's such nice weather~ On days like this, I feel like going out far away.
mlVoiceResource_Text.901057: Just the sunshine alone makes me feel so good, you know?
mlVoiceResource_Text.901058: The clouds look gloomy... But it's kind of comfortable, isn't it~
mlVoiceResource_Text.901059: Hehe~ Maybe I should try out my new rain gear.
mlVoiceResource_Text.901060: The smell of rain is somehow calming, isn't it...
mlVoiceResource_Text.901061: Wow... It's pouring rain! So heavy!
mlVoiceResource_Text.901062: It's rare around here, isn't it, snow? But I wonder if it'll accumulate...
mlVoiceResource_Text.901063: It's getting warmer, isn't it? Soon it'll be time to put away the coats and go for lots of walks.
mlVoiceResource_Text.901064: ...Ah-choo! Oh, it's not hay fever...! Probably... No, definitely...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.901067: Autumn is the season of harvest! I'm so happy to have lots of fruits to pick.
mlVoiceResource_Text.901068: When will the leaves start changing color? I want to take lots of photos.
mlVoiceResource_Text.901069: I end up buying several scarves and gloves... They're so cute!
mlVoiceResource_Text.901070: It's so cold, isn't it... Oh, maybe I should look up some of the latest warming gadgets.
mlVoiceResource_Text.901071: Rice cakes are only for New Year's, right? It'd be a hassle later if we didn't prepare them...
mlVoiceResource_Text.901074: I look forward to buying Christmas ornaments little by little every year! It's so much fun!
mlVoiceResource_Text.901075: Producer-san, um, well... There's something I want to receive...
mlVoiceResource_Text.901076: Wow, did you prepare this for me? I'm so happy! Can I open it?
mlVoiceResource_Text.901079: Since it's Peach Blossom Festival, I bought peach tea. How about having it with some sweets~
mlVoiceResource_Text.901082: The year is ending soon, huh... Thanks to you, Producer-san, it's been such a good year...
mlVoiceResource_Text.901083: Ah... Thank you so much. Hehe, I've grown a little older. Please continue to take care of me.
mlVoiceResource_Text.901084: It's Luca-chan's birthday today, right? Let's celebrate together and surprise her~
mlVoiceResource_Text.901086: Happy birthday! Actually, I've been waiting for this moment. I'm glad I could say it while looking at your face.
mlVoiceResource_Text.1000001:
On sunny days, I sometimes end up
falling asleep on a bench
in the park...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1000002:
Oh, welcome back.
It'd be nice if it's sunny
on your next day off.
mlVoiceResource_Text.1000003:
Now then, how many cats
are here? Hmm, too easy, you say?
mlVoiceResource_Text.1000004:
Producer, want to come over
to the dorm next time? Hehe,
I could even show you around my room.
mlVoiceResource_Text.1000005:
Today, let's give it our all, Kaho...!
...But first, maybe...
a little nap...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1000006: This outfit? Well, I like it...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1000007:
Producer, feeling peckish?
Picked up some croquette bread!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1000008:
Producer, want to hang out?
If you're worried, I'll come along.
mlVoiceResource_Text.1000009:
Let's go, somewhere...
to have fun.
mlVoiceResource_Text.1000010:
What's it to you? Whether I wear this
or that, it's my choice.
Don't bother me with trivial stuff.
mlVoiceResource_Text.1000011:
Hehe, a bit chic, don't you think?
How about we go out together?
mlVoiceResource_Text.1000012:
My hood and hair accessory
are my pride and joy!
They feel amazing to touch, you know...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1000013:
Oh? Producer,
you seem to be in high spirits.
Hehe, that makes me happy too.
mlVoiceResource_Text.1000014:
I have some delicious snacks.
Producer, would you like
to join me?
mlVoiceResource_Text.1000015:
Thinking of making something light...
Any preferences?
mlVoiceResource_Text.1000016:
Huh, was I smiling?
Not like anything special happened,
but... hehe~
mlVoiceResource_Text.1000017:
Worried if my stomach's cold?
Heh, didn't expect
you'd be concerned about that.
mlVoiceResource_Text.1000018:
Work's done, right?
Any further engagements
will require a special bonus.
mlVoiceResource_Text.1000019:
Hey, want to go out?
If you have time to admire the snow,
why not come with me?
mlVoiceResource_Text.1000020:
Huh... clothes?
If I like something, I'll buy it.
Brand doesn't matter.
mlVoiceResource_Text.1000021:
Today, we meet again...
Rinze feels... warm...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1000022:
I iron my blouses myself...
Hehe... they come out...
all crisp...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1000024:
Producer, are you busy?
If... if you have time,
I'd like to chat!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1000025:
Good morning! Saying it
in the morning, afternoon, or evening
is funny!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1000026:
Producer,
Are you free today~?
Let's do something~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100002: When you hear chirping... let's sing!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100003: The design of this's costume, the lace on the right arm, is so cute...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100006: Towards the sky of song with everyone...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100008: Wrapped in spring colors... to that sky...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100009: It seems I can still flap my wings...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100010: To this sky, with all my might...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100012: Hehe, let's do our best today too, Producer...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100013: I'll show you the bonds with everyone...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100014: I feel relieved when Tsukasa-chan and Meguru-chan are around.
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100015: I'll do my best to keep up with the two of them.
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100016: As long as we're together, I'm not afraid...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100020: Somehow... it feels like my strength is welling up...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100021: With the three of us... we'll shine even more...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100023: I'll do my best... with all my might...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100028: I feel like I could even fly in the sky...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100030: I'll keep doing my best... Mmm...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100031: If it's us, we can definitely do it...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100032: I want us to grow more as a unit too.
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100033: Since I'm not alone anymore, I feel like I've noticed more things.
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100034: It's okay... because I'm not alone...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100036: If it's the three of us...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100041: I spare no effort to become my ideal self.
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100042: Your fortune today, Producer, seems very good.
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100043: I won't let my guard down...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100044: There's still a long way to go...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100045: I don't want to embarrass this's costume...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100047: Little by little, I'm starting to understand...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100050: Becoming an idol and making more friends... makes me incredibly happy every day!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100051: I can't wait to stand on stage with the three of us soon!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100053: Let's make our song resound wherever we go!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100054: Just wearing it makes me feel energetic!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100057: If it's the three of us together...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100059: I want to know more about you, Producer!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100060: I want to try challenging various things!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100064: I want to work even harder at dancing!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100065: To the other side of the blue sky...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100066: I feel like I could even fly in the sky...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100068: Hehehe, L'Antica is so much fun!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100069: Thanks to everyone, I feel like I can grow even more!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100071: We'll carve out our own fate...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100073: The most reliable leader in the world? That's me!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100074: Isn't it a cool L'Antica-like feeling?
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100076: My smile is the best in the universe!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100077: With you and Producer, becoming top idols isn't just a dream!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100078: I want to try various things!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100079: I'll show you my full power!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100081: I'll be careful not to trip!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100082: Hehehe, even if there's twice as much fluttering, it's okay~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100083: In this sky-like outfit, I'm like a goddess, right~?
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100084: I'll warm you up with the power of a goddess~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100085: Shall I show you my true power?
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100086: It's not bad to be lively, you know~
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100087: I can't let you slack off, so I'm troubled~
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100090: I might be able to show a better way~
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100091: Shall I teach you this step~?
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100092: Right~? This suits me, doesn't it~?
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100095: Hehe~ What kind of mischief do you want today~?
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100096: I don't dislike the atmosphere of the office~
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100099: I feel like I'm getting along well~?
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100100: Well, wearing it with everyone isn't bad either, I guess~
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100102: Thanks to you, Producer, I've gotten used to it~
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100103: Let's aim for greater heights together!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100105: As L'Antica... we must aim higher.
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100107: Now is the time to open the door!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100109: Am I becoming someone who can support L'Antica?
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100110: It all started with this's costume.
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100111: I hope that my presence as a gear can bring joy to someone.
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100113: Every day shines because of you.
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100114: Is it fun to produce me?
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100117: Let's not forget our original intentions and work hard.
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100118: It seems like I can continue to fly higher.
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100119: I want to be as elegant as a swan.
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100122: I feel motivated when I'm with everyone.
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100123: Please look forward to what Mitsumine and the others will do...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100125: Can you see my true form...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100126: Am I becoming unable to see anyone other than Mitsumine...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100127: I feel like I've been entrusted with the key to destiny.
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100129: Are you ready to have your heart stolen by Mitsumine...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100131: Mitsumine will do her best today too~
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100132: It feels weird to be an idol as Mitsumine.
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100133: I have to live up to expectations!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100134: This is Mitsumine's ace up her sleeve!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100135: You do frog kick under the water, okay? Understand?
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100136: Make sure to watch where I jump, okay?
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100138: Could I become a pride of Producer?
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100153: It feels like... I can feel the wind...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100154: My body... feels like it's turned into feathers...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100155: Do you like... the blue sky...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100156: I want to stand on a stage above the clouds... someday...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100157: Just like snow, effort will become strength if accumulated...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100158: It's like stalactites, or rather, like the reflection of crystals...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100159: It would be amazing if we could share the same image.
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100160: If we keep going like this...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100161: Because everyone is here, I feel like I have to do my best...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100163: This suits the me who wears it...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100164: I'll give it my all with everything I have...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100168: I'm watching... everything that's happening here...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100169: I can hear... so many sounds...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100170: It's time to wake up... and become a flower...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100172: So that I can... shine on someone... someday...
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100176: As if floating... as if flying...!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100177: Don't push yourself too hard, okay~?
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100178: If you ever have any trouble, just tell me, okay...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100180: With the smile of an angel~ Take this~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100181: I wonder what a heavenly Sweet Flower would look like~
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100182: Take this~! You've been healed by the power of Tenka~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100183: I'll do my best to cheer everyone up~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100184: What do you want me to do...?
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100185: I'll make it even more beautiful~!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100186: Let's do our best in today's lesson!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100187: Can I ask you to take a look at my dance moves?
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100191: Alrighty! Let's turn the stage into a flower garden with the three of us!
mlVoiceResource_Text.1100193: Don't miss it, okay? When Sweet Flower blooms...!
